WEBVTT FILE

1
00:00:06.423 --> 00:00:09.426
等一下，別射
Okay, hold on, don't shoot.

2
00:00:10.176 --> 00:00:11.928
-看到目標了嗎？ -嗯
- You see where you're going? - Mm-hmm.

3
00:00:12.095 --> 00:00:13.096
好
Okay.

4
00:00:13.263 --> 00:00:15.181
現在想想怎麼射中
Now, let's worry about how you get there.

5
00:00:16.057 --> 00:00:17.434
腳得移過來
Gotta move your foot here.

6
00:00:17.767 --> 00:00:19.352
腳尖向這邊
Point your toe this way.

7
00:00:19.728 --> 00:00:21.271
屁股，挺胸
Your hips here.

8
00:00:21.479 --> 00:00:22.814
好了嗎？
Okay?

9
00:00:23.606 --> 00:00:24.941
-看得見嗎？ -可以
- Can you see? - Yeah.

10
00:00:25.108 --> 00:00:26.109
-確定？ -嗯
- Are you sure? - Mm-hmm.

11
00:00:26.317 --> 00:00:27.652
現在呢？看得見嗎？
How about now? Can you see now?

12
00:00:27.736 --> 00:00:29.070
-看不見 -這樣呢？
- No. - How about now?

13
00:00:31.239 --> 00:00:32.323
好
All right.

14
00:00:32.991 --> 00:00:34.993
準備，用三根手指頭
Ready? Three fingers.

15
00:00:35.660 --> 00:00:36.870
漂亮
Nice!

16
00:00:38.371 --> 00:00:39.956
投得真棒，孩子
Nice throw, kiddo.

17
00:00:40.123 --> 00:00:41.207
接住
Here you go.

18
00:00:41.583 --> 00:00:43.626
你們要美乃滋還是芥末醬？
Hey, you guys want mayo? Or mustard?

19
00:00:43.793 --> 00:00:45.253
還是都要？
Or both?

20
00:00:45.545 --> 00:00:47.505
哪有人熱狗加美乃滋？
Who puts mayo on a hot dog?

21
00:00:47.672 --> 00:00:48.631
妳弟弟吧
Probably your brothers.

22
00:00:48.798 --> 00:00:50.967
兩份加芥末醬，謝了，媽媽
Uh, two mustard, please! Thanks, Mama.

23
00:00:51.134 --> 00:00:51.968
知道了
Got it!

24
00:00:52.427 --> 00:00:54.054
奈特，美乃滋還是芥末醬？
Nate, mayo or mustard?

25
00:00:54.679 --> 00:00:55.889
番茄醬呢？
How about ketchup?

26
00:00:56.306 --> 00:00:58.266
好，也有番茄醬
Or ketchup. I got ketchup, too.

27
00:00:58.558 --> 00:00:59.642
注意手肘
Mind your elbow.

28
00:01:02.645 --> 00:01:03.688
好眼力
Good job, hawk-eye.

29
00:01:03.855 --> 00:01:05.482
去拔箭
Go get your arrow.

30
00:01:08.693 --> 00:01:09.694
大家過來
Hey, guys!

31
00:01:09.861 --> 00:01:12.072
練習夠了，吃東西
Enough practice. Soup's on!

32
00:01:12.238 --> 00:01:13.281
好
All right.

33
00:01:13.448 --> 00:01:14.824
馬上來，我們餓了
We're coming. We're hungry.

34
00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:17.369
萊拉，走吧
Lila, let's go.

35
00:01:20.413 --> 00:01:21.664
萊拉？
Lila?

36
00:01:24.584 --> 00:01:25.585
親愛的？
Honey?

37
00:01:29.464 --> 00:01:30.632
老婆？
Hey, babe?

38
00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:38.074
-= www.OpenSubtitles.org =-

39
00:01:40.141 --> 00:01:41.518
老婆？
Babe?

40
00:01:43.478 --> 00:01:44.771
老婆？
Babe?

41
00:01:46.398 --> 00:01:47.649
兒子！
Boys!

42
00:01:49.567 --> 00:01:50.402
兒子！
Boys!

43
00:01:52.696 --> 00:01:53.905
蘿拉！
Laura!

44
00:02:37.907 --> 00:02:38.950
妳不必這樣
You don't need to do that.

45
00:02:39.492 --> 00:02:42.162
只要保持不動就好
Because, uh, you're just holding the position.

46
00:02:43.204 --> 00:02:44.372
對
Oh, yeah.

47
00:02:44.664 --> 00:02:45.665
差一點
That was close.

48
00:02:47.542 --> 00:02:49.294
得分，現在一比一
That's a goal. We are now one a piece.

49
00:02:49.461 --> 00:02:50.837
我想再試試看
I would like to try again.

50
00:02:53.298 --> 00:02:55.550
我們平手，緊張嗎？
We're tied up. Feel the tension?

51
00:02:55.717 --> 00:02:57.260
好玩
It's fun.

52
00:02:57.427 --> 00:02:59.429
爛死了，現在妳有機會贏
That was terrible. Now you have a chance to win.

53
00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:01.681
妳贏了
And you've won.

54
00:03:02.766 --> 00:03:03.933
恭喜
Congratulations.

55
00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.226
公平競爭
Fair game.

56
00:03:06.644 --> 00:03:07.937
可敬的對手
Good sport.

57
00:03:08.938 --> 00:03:10.315
開心嗎？
You have fun?

58
00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:14.069
很好玩
It was fun.

59
00:03:36.675 --> 00:03:38.218
啟動了嗎？
This thing on?

60
00:03:40.387 --> 00:03:42.389
波茲小姐，小辣椒
Hey, Miss Potts. Pep.

61
00:03:44.349 --> 00:03:46.434
如果妳找到這段錄影
If you find this recording...

62
00:03:46.601 --> 00:03:49.270
別放到社群媒體上
don't post it on social media.

63
00:03:49.437 --> 00:03:51.147
它會讓人大飆淚
It's gonna be a real tearjerker.

64
00:03:51.815 --> 00:03:54.234
不知道妳會不會看到這些影片
I don't know if you're ever gonna see these.

65
00:03:54.401 --> 00:03:56.444
不知道妳是否還…
I don't even know if you're still...

66
00:03:56.986 --> 00:03:58.863
天啊，希望如此
Oh, God, I hope so.

67
00:03:59.698 --> 00:04:01.950
今天是第21天
Today's day 21.

68
00:04:02.117 --> 00:04:04.369
不，第22天
No, uh, 22.

69
00:04:05.036 --> 00:04:07.580
要不是因為盯著無垠太空
You know, if it wasn't for the existential terror...

70
00:04:07.747 --> 00:04:12.210
產生存在恐懼，我今天會好過點
of staring into the literal void of space, I'd say I'm feeling a little better today.

71
00:04:12.377 --> 00:04:15.422
感染快好了，多虧裡面那個藍臉魔王
Infection's run its course, thanks to the Blue Meanie back there.

72
00:04:16.256 --> 00:04:17.590
妳會很喜歡她的
Oh, you'd love her.

73
00:04:17.757 --> 00:04:19.175
非常務實
Very practical.

74
00:04:19.634 --> 00:04:21.720
只有一點虐待狂
Only a tiny bit sadistic.

75
00:04:26.725 --> 00:04:28.810
燃料電池在戰役中受損
So, the fuel cells were cracked during battle...

76
00:04:28.977 --> 00:04:31.146
我們設法反轉離子電荷
and we figured out a way to reverse the ion charge...

77
00:04:31.312 --> 00:04:34.024
多爭取了48小時飛行時間
and bought ourselves about 48 hours of flight time.

78
00:04:37.569 --> 00:04:39.154
但現在陷入絕境
Uh, but it's now dead in the water.

79
00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:42.824
最近的7-11在一千光年以外
Thousand light years from the nearest 7-Eleven.

80
00:04:44.325 --> 00:04:46.703
氧氣明早會用完
Oxygen will run out tomorrow morning...

81
00:04:48.204 --> 00:04:49.873
就這樣了
and that'll be it.

82
00:04:53.168 --> 00:04:56.254
小辣椒，我說過不再有驚人之舉
Pep, I know I said no more surprises...

83
00:04:56.421 --> 00:05:00.008
但我真的希望再做最後一次
but I gotta say I was really hoping to pull off one last one.

84
00:05:00.175 --> 00:05:02.135
可是看起來…
But it looks like...

85
00:05:02.302 --> 00:05:04.095
妳也知道現在的情況
Well, you know what it looks like.

86
00:05:05.513 --> 00:05:07.349
不要難過
Don't feel bad about this.

87
00:05:07.515 --> 00:05:10.310
如果妳悲痛個幾星期
I mean, actually, if you grovel for a couple weeks...

88
00:05:11.061 --> 00:05:14.189
然後帶著強烈罪惡感過日子…
and then move on with enormous guilt...

89
00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:23.365
我應該躺一下，閉目養神
I should probably lie down for a minute. Go rest my eyes.

90
00:05:26.368 --> 00:05:27.911
請妳瞭解
Please know...

91
00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:32.707
等我慢慢睡著，就會像最近的每個夜晚
when I drift off, it'll be like every night lately.

92
00:05:32.916 --> 00:05:35.877
我很好，好得不得了
I'm fine. Totally fine.

93
00:05:36.544 --> 00:05:37.837
我常夢見妳
I dream about you.

94
00:05:39.422 --> 00:05:41.007
自始至終都是妳
Because it's always you.

95
00:09:03.752 --> 00:09:04.753
我阻止不了他
Couldn't stop him.

96
00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:05.920
我也沒辦法
Neither could I.

97
00:09:06.087 --> 00:09:07.255
等一下
Hang on.

98
00:09:09.674 --> 00:09:11.259
我失去了那小子
I lost the kid.

99
00:09:13.803 --> 00:09:15.388
東尼，我們輸了
Tony, we lost.

100
00:09:17.682 --> 00:09:18.683
是不是…
Is, uh...?

101
00:09:19.684 --> 00:09:21.311
我的天啊
- Oh, good. - Oh, my God!

102
00:09:22.312 --> 00:09:23.355
我的天啊
Oh, my God!

103
00:09:28.777 --> 00:09:30.487
沒事
It's okay.

104
00:09:36.868 --> 00:09:39.204
薩諾斯來到地球已經23天
It's been 23 days since Thanos came to Earth.

105
00:09:39.371 --> 00:09:40.372
（史蒂芬史傳奇，失蹤）

106
00:09:40.538 --> 00:09:41.539
（山姆威爾森，失蹤）

107
00:09:41.706 --> 00:09:42.957
各國政府分崩離析
World governments are

108
00:09:43.124 --> 00:09:44.125
（汪達麥西莫夫，失蹤）
in pieces.

109
00:09:44.292 --> 00:09:45.460
還在運作的政府
The parts that are still working...

110
00:09:45.460 --> 00:09:46.294
（史考特朗恩，失蹤）
The parts that are still working...

111
00:09:46.461 --> 00:09:49.964
正試圖統計人數，看來他…
...are trying to take a census and it looks like he did...

112
00:09:52.717 --> 00:09:54.302
他說到做到
He did exactly what he said he was gonna do.

113
00:09:54.469 --> 00:09:55.470
薩諾斯殲滅了…
Thanos wiped out...

114
00:09:55.637 --> 00:09:57.639
（尼克福瑞，失蹤）

115
00:09:58.056 --> 00:10:01.142
世上一半的生物
...50% of all living creatures.

116
00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:07.399
他現在在哪裡？
Where is he now? Where?

117
00:10:07.565 --> 00:10:09.275
不知道
We don't know.

118
00:10:09.442 --> 00:10:12.529
他打開一個入口，走了進去
He just opened a portal and walked through.

119
00:10:15.156 --> 00:10:16.199
他怎麼了？
What's wrong with him?

120
00:10:17.283 --> 00:10:19.244
他很火大
Oh, he's pissed.

121
00:10:19.411 --> 00:10:20.745
覺得自己失敗了
He thinks he failed.

122
00:10:22.205 --> 00:10:23.206
當然是那樣沒錯
Which, of course, he did...

123
00:10:23.373 --> 00:10:25.500
但大家不都如此嗎？
but there's a lot of that going around, ain't there?

124
00:10:25.667 --> 00:10:28.211
說真的，我剛剛還以為你是填充玩具
Honestly, until this exact second I thought you were a Build-A-Bear.

125
00:10:28.378 --> 00:10:29.000
也許我是
Maybe I am.

126
00:10:29.100 --> 00:10:31.339
我們找了薩諾斯三星期
We've been hunting Thanos for three weeks now.

127
00:10:31.506 --> 00:10:33.508
深度太空掃描
Deep space scans...

128
00:10:33.758 --> 00:10:35.719
還有衛星，一無所獲
and satellites, and we got nothing.

129
00:10:37.512 --> 00:10:38.513
東尼，你對抗過他
Tony, you fought him.

130
00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:39.597
誰告訴你的？
Who told you that?

131
00:10:40.265 --> 00:10:41.307
我沒有
I didn't fight him.

132
00:10:41.474 --> 00:10:43.059
他徹底擊垮我
No, he wiped my face with a planet...

133
00:10:43.226 --> 00:10:45.645
那個紐約魔術師奉上寶石
while the Bleecker Street magician gave away the store.

134
00:10:45.812 --> 00:10:48.148
沒有對抗，他根本打不垮
That's what happened. There was no fight, 'cause he's not beatable.

135
00:10:48.314 --> 00:10:51.026
他有給你線索或座標嗎？
Did he give you any clues, any coordinates, anything?

136
00:10:51.748 --> 00:10:53.281
Uh...

137
00:10:54.029 --> 00:10:55.530
幾年前我就料到了
I saw this coming a few years back.

138
00:10:55.697 --> 00:10:57.323
我看到一個景象，卻不願相信
I had a vision. I didn't wanna believe it.

139
00:10:57.824 --> 00:10:59.284
以為自己在作夢
Thought I was dreaming.

140
00:10:59.451 --> 00:11:00.452
東尼，我需要你專注點
Tony, I'm gonna need you to focus.

141
00:11:00.618 --> 00:11:02.370
當時我需要你
And I needed you.

142
00:11:02.537 --> 00:11:03.580
過去式
As in, past tense.

143
00:11:03.747 --> 00:11:07.000
那比你需要的更重要，太遲了
That trumps what you need. It's too late, buddy.

144
00:11:07.167 --> 00:11:08.293
抱歉
Sorry.

145
00:11:09.252 --> 00:11:11.963
我需要什麼呢？刮鬍子
You know what I need? I need a shave.

146
00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:15.133
我記得告訴你們…
And I believe I remember telling all youse...

147
00:11:15.300 --> 00:11:16.176
東尼…
Tony, Tony!

148
00:11:16.343 --> 00:11:21.639
無論死活，我們需要一套全球防衛機制
...alive and otherwise, that what we needed was a suit of armour around the world.

149
00:11:21.806 --> 00:11:25.435
記得嗎？無論它是否影響我們寶貴的自由
Remember that? Whether it impacted our precious freedoms or not.

150
00:11:25.602 --> 00:11:26.811
那才是我們需要的
That's what we needed.

151
00:11:26.978 --> 00:11:28.063
結果無效，是吧？
Well, that didn't work out, did it?

152
00:11:28.229 --> 00:11:29.647
我說我們會輸
I said we'd lose.

153
00:11:29.814 --> 00:11:31.983
你說要輸也是一起輸
You said, "We'll do that together, too."

154
00:11:32.525 --> 00:11:33.610
結果呢，隊長？
And guess what, Cap?

155
00:11:33.777 --> 00:11:35.070
我們輸了
We lost.

156
00:11:35.528 --> 00:11:36.529
你卻不在場
And you weren't there.

157
00:11:38.114 --> 00:11:39.282
我們就是這德行
But that's what we do, right?

158
00:11:39.449 --> 00:11:42.202
事後只會說我們是復仇者聯盟
Our best work after the fact? We're the "Avengers."

159
00:11:42.369 --> 00:11:44.329
我們是復仇者聯盟，不是預防者聯盟
We're the "Avengers," not the "Pre-vengers."

160
00:11:44.496 --> 00:11:45.497
-好啦 -對吧？
- Okay. - Right?

161
00:11:45.663 --> 00:11:46.873
你表達得很清楚了，坐下
You made your point. Just sit down, okay?

162
00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:47.999
不，我要講重點了
Okay. No, no, here's my point. You know what?

163
00:11:48.166 --> 00:11:49.542
-她很厲害 -你病了，坐下
- She's great by the way. - Tony, you're sick. Sit down.

164
00:11:49.709 --> 00:11:51.336
我們需要妳，妳是新血
We need you. You're new blood.

165
00:11:51.503 --> 00:11:54.339
我們都是老屁股，我沒東西給你，隊長
Bunch of tired old mules. I got nothing for you, Cap.

166
00:11:54.506 --> 00:11:55.799
我沒有座標
I got no coordinates...

167
00:11:55.965 --> 00:11:58.718
沒線索，沒策略，沒選擇
no clues, no strategies, no options.

168
00:11:58.885 --> 00:12:00.595
零，鴨蛋，屁都沒有
Zero. Zip. Nada.

169
00:12:00.762 --> 00:12:02.514
沒有信任，騙子
No trust, liar.

170
00:12:07.060 --> 00:12:08.311
拿去
Here, take this.

171
00:12:08.478 --> 00:12:10.605
找到他，戴上去
You find him, you put that on...

172
00:12:11.064 --> 00:12:12.607
躲起來
you hide.

173
00:12:13.900 --> 00:12:15.610
-東尼 -我很好
- Tony! - I'm fine.

174
00:12:15.777 --> 00:12:17.487
讓我…
Let me...

175
00:12:23.993 --> 00:12:25.286
布魯斯幫他打了鎮靜劑
Bruce gave him a sedative.

176
00:12:25.453 --> 00:12:27.163
他應該今天都不會醒
He's gonna probably be out for the rest of the day.

177
00:12:28.248 --> 00:12:29.708
你們照顧他
You guys take care of him...

178
00:12:29.874 --> 00:12:31.418
我再帶梭爾人的仙丹回來
and I'll bring him a Xorrian elixir when I come back.

179
00:12:32.002 --> 00:12:33.003
妳要去哪？
Where are you going?

180
00:12:33.169 --> 00:12:34.838
幹掉薩諾斯
To kill Thanos.

181
00:12:37.882 --> 00:12:39.009
喂
Hey.

182
00:12:39.175 --> 00:12:41.302
我們通常集體行動
You know, we usually work as a team here...

183
00:12:41.469 --> 00:12:43.138
其實現在士氣低落
and, uh, between you and I, morale's a little fragile.

184
00:12:43.304 --> 00:12:46.891
太空固然是妳的戰場，但這也是我們的戰役
We realize up there is more your territory, but this is our fight, too.

185
00:12:47.058 --> 00:12:48.226
妳知道他的下落嗎？
You even know where he is?

186
00:12:48.393 --> 00:12:49.561
我認識的人可能知道
I know people who might.

187
00:12:49.728 --> 00:12:51.062
不必麻煩了
Don't bother.

188
00:12:52.022 --> 00:12:53.773
我能告訴你們薩諾斯在哪
I can tell you where Thanos is.

189
00:12:56.317 --> 00:12:59.279
薩諾斯花了很長時間使我更趨完美
Thanos spent a long time trying to perfect me.

190
00:12:59.904 --> 00:13:03.950
他常提到他的遠大計劃
And when he worked, he talked about his Great Plan.

191
00:13:04.117 --> 00:13:07.203
我就算支離破碎，也想討好他
Even disassembled, I wanted to please him.

192
00:13:07.370 --> 00:13:08.788
我會問他
I'd ask...

193
00:13:09.330 --> 00:13:12.000
他計畫完成後，我們會去哪裡？
where would we go once his plan was complete?

194
00:13:12.500 --> 00:13:14.502
他的答案始終如一
And his answer was always the same.

195
00:13:18.715 --> 00:13:19.716
去花園
"To the Garden."

196
00:13:20.383 --> 00:13:23.094
真可愛，薩諾斯有養老計畫
That's cute. Thanos has a retirement plan.

197
00:13:23.261 --> 00:13:24.804
所以他在哪裡？
So, where is he?

198
00:13:25.096 --> 00:13:27.223
薩諾斯一彈指
When Thanos snapped his fingers...

199
00:13:27.390 --> 00:13:31.269
地球成了一股超強電力突波的中心點
Earth became ground zero for a power surge of ridiculously cosmic proportions.

200
00:13:31.436 --> 00:13:33.646
沒人見過那樣的奇景
No one's ever seen anything like it.

201
00:13:33.813 --> 00:13:35.148
直到兩天前
Until two days ago...

202
00:13:36.983 --> 00:13:38.568
在這個星球上
on this planet.

203
00:13:39.277 --> 00:13:40.779
薩諾斯在那裡
Thanos is there.

204
00:13:42.489 --> 00:13:44.199
他又運用了無限寶石
He used the stones again.

205
00:13:44.449 --> 00:13:45.867
喂…
Hey, hey, hey.

206
00:13:46.284 --> 00:13:48.244
我們人手不足
We'd be going in shorthanded, you know?

207
00:13:48.411 --> 00:13:49.788
無限寶石還在他手上
Look, he's still got the stones, so...

208
00:13:49.954 --> 00:13:51.498
我們去拿
So, let's get 'em.

209
00:13:51.664 --> 00:13:53.041
用它們把所有人救回來
Use them to bring everyone back.

210
00:13:53.208 --> 00:13:54.292
就那樣？
Just like that?

211
00:13:54.459 --> 00:13:56.044
對，就那樣
Yeah. Just like that.

212
00:13:56.211 --> 00:13:59.381
即便逆轉的機會微乎其微
Even if there's a small chance that we can undo this...

213
00:13:59.547 --> 00:14:02.258
為了其他人，我們也該放手一搏
I mean, we owe it to everyone who's not in this room to try.

214
00:14:02.425 --> 00:14:06.388
如果這麼做，如何知道結果會有所不同？
If we do this, how do we know it's gonna end any differently than it did before?

215
00:14:06.554 --> 00:14:08.181
因為以前你們沒有我
Because before you didn't have me.

216
00:14:09.057 --> 00:14:10.225
嘿，新來的妹
Hey, new girl?

217
00:14:10.392 --> 00:14:13.103
這裡每個人都是超級英雄
Everybody in this room is about that superhero life.

218
00:14:13.895 --> 00:14:15.897
我直接問，這段時間妳在哪裡？
And if you don't mind my asking, where the hell have you been all this time?

219
00:14:16.064 --> 00:14:18.483
宇宙中還有其他許多星球
There are a lot of other planets in the universe.

220
00:14:18.650 --> 00:14:21.528
可惜它們沒有你們
And unfortunately, they didn't have you guys.

221
00:14:41.172 --> 00:14:43.258
這個我喜歡
I like this one.

222
00:14:47.804 --> 00:14:50.265
我們去找那個王八蛋
Let's go get this son of a bitch.

223
00:14:50.432 --> 00:14:57.397
復仇者聯盟：終局之戰

224
00:15:12.037 --> 00:15:13.038
好
Okay.

225
00:15:13.455 --> 00:15:15.832
這裡誰沒上過太空？
Who here hasn't been to space?

226
00:15:17.208 --> 00:15:18.335
幹嘛？
Why?

227
00:15:18.501 --> 00:15:20.170
最好別吐在我船上
You better not throw up on my ship.

228
00:15:20.337 --> 00:15:21.629
接近跳躍點，三…
Approaching jump in three...

229
00:15:22.047 --> 00:15:23.882
二，一
two, one.

230
00:15:37.437 --> 00:15:39.147
我去前面偵察情況
I'll head down for recon.

231
00:15:57.665 --> 00:15:58.875
會成功的，史帝夫
This is gonna work, Steve.

232
00:15:59.250 --> 00:16:00.835
我知道
I know it will.

233
00:16:04.673 --> 00:16:06.966
否則我也束手無策了
'Cause I don't know what I'm gonna do if it doesn't.

234
00:16:07.550 --> 00:16:11.054
沒衛星，沒船艦，沒軍隊
No satellites. No ships. No armies.

235
00:16:11.221 --> 00:16:12.722
沒有任何地面防禦機制
No ground defenses of any kind.

236
00:16:14.808 --> 00:16:16.476
只有他
It's just him.

237
00:16:17.102 --> 00:16:18.853
那就夠了
And that's enough.

238
00:17:48.109 --> 00:17:49.319
糟糕
Oh, no.

239
00:17:59.204 --> 00:18:00.538
它們在哪裡？
Where are they?

240
00:18:00.872 --> 00:18:02.374
回答問題
Answer the question.

241
00:18:04.793 --> 00:18:07.212
宇宙需要修正
The universe required correction.

242
00:18:07.379 --> 00:18:11.174
修正後，寶石就沒有用途
After that, the stones served no purpose...

243
00:18:11.341 --> 00:18:12.967
只是誘惑
beyond temptation.

244
00:18:13.134 --> 00:18:15.095
你謀殺了數十億人
You murdered trillions!

245
00:18:16.054 --> 00:18:17.639
你們應該心懷感激
You should be grateful.

246
00:18:21.851 --> 00:18:23.770
寶石在哪裡？
Where are the stones?

247
00:18:23.937 --> 00:18:25.313
灰飛煙滅
Gone.

248
00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:26.564
縮小成原子
Reduced to atoms.

249
00:18:27.232 --> 00:18:28.733
兩天前你才用過它們
You used them two days ago!

250
00:18:28.900 --> 00:18:32.112
我用寶石來摧毀寶石
I used the stones to destroy the stones.

251
00:18:32.862 --> 00:18:34.489
差點害我沒命
It nearly killed me.

252
00:18:35.907 --> 00:18:37.659
但任務完成了
But the work is done.

253
00:18:38.076 --> 00:18:40.745
總是會完成的
It always will be.

254
00:18:42.330 --> 00:18:45.709
我是無可匹敵的
I am inevitable.

255
00:18:48.003 --> 00:18:50.380
我們徹底搜索這裡，他一定在說謊
We have to tear this place apart. He has to be lying!

256
00:18:50.547 --> 00:18:51.756
我父親有很多面向
My father is many things.

257
00:18:52.632 --> 00:18:54.718
卻不會說謊
A liar is not one of them.

258
00:18:58.722 --> 00:19:00.056
謝謝妳，女兒
Ah. Thank you, daughter.

259
00:19:02.934 --> 00:19:04.853
或許我對妳太嚴厲了
Perhaps I treated you too harshly.

260
00:19:11.359 --> 00:19:12.360
什麼？
What?

261
00:19:13.028 --> 00:19:14.779
你做了什麼？
What did you do?

262
00:19:16.322 --> 00:19:18.116
這次我對準了頭
I went for the head.

263
00:20:02.035 --> 00:20:09.000
（五年後）

264
00:20:29.020 --> 00:20:31.189
所以…
So......I, uh,

265
00:20:31.356 --> 00:20:32.357
（他們不在了，我們何去何從？）

266
00:20:32.524 --> 00:20:34.984
前幾天我有約會
went on a date the other day.

267
00:20:35.151 --> 00:20:36.820
五年來頭一遭
It's the first time in five years.

268
00:20:36.986 --> 00:20:39.322
我坐在那裡吃晚餐
You know? I'm sitting there at dinner.

269
00:20:40.532 --> 00:20:42.534
根本不知道該聊什麼
I didn't even know what to talk about.

270
00:20:43.868 --> 00:20:45.078
結果你們聊什麼？
What did you talk about?

271
00:20:45.578 --> 00:20:48.915
老掉牙的話題…今非昔比
Eh, same old crap. You know, how things have changed.

272
00:20:49.541 --> 00:20:51.167
我的工作，他的工作
My job, his job.

273
00:20:52.168 --> 00:20:54.045
我們多懷念大都會隊
How much we miss the Mets.

274
00:20:56.464 --> 00:20:58.008
接著兩人靜了下來
And then things got quiet...

275
00:21:00.218 --> 00:21:03.722
上沙拉時他哭了出來
then he cried as they were serving the salads.

276
00:21:03.888 --> 00:21:05.390
你呢？
What about you?

277
00:21:06.474 --> 00:21:09.728
我在上甜點前飆淚
I cried just before dessert.

278
00:21:13.481 --> 00:21:15.608
我明天還會見他，所以…
But I'm seeing him again tomorrow, so...

279
00:21:16.276 --> 00:21:17.527
那很棒
That's great.

280
00:21:17.694 --> 00:21:19.279
踏出第一步最難
You did the hardest part. You took the jump.

281
00:21:19.446 --> 00:21:21.573
你不知道結果如何
You didn't know where you were gonna come down.

282
00:21:22.198 --> 00:21:26.494
我們就是得踏出那些小小的步伐
And that's it. That's those little brave baby steps we gotta take...

283
00:21:26.661 --> 00:21:30.373
努力再認真生活，尋找目標
to try and become whole again, try and find purpose.

284
00:21:32.208 --> 00:21:36.212
1945年我遇見摯愛後，立刻被冷凍
I went in the ice in '45, right after I met the love of my life.

285
00:21:37.088 --> 00:21:38.840
70年後才醒來
Woke up 70 years later.

286
00:21:41.968 --> 00:21:44.012
日子總得過下去
You gotta move on.

287
00:21:46.723 --> 00:21:48.350
就是得過下去
Gotta move on.

288
00:21:53.188 --> 00:21:55.607
世界掌握在我們手中
The world is in our hands.

289
00:21:55.774 --> 00:21:57.859
交到了我們手上，各位
It's left to us, guys.

290
00:21:58.026 --> 00:22:00.236
我們必須善加利用
And we gotta do something with it.

291
00:22:00.945 --> 00:22:02.364
否則…
Otherwise...

292
00:22:03.656 --> 00:22:05.992
薩諾斯該殺光我們才對
Thanos should've killed all of us.

293
00:22:10.413 --> 00:22:13.500
（舊金山）

294
00:22:16.961 --> 00:22:20.965
（任你放自助倉庫）

295
00:23:07.929 --> 00:23:09.264
搞什麼？
What the hell?

296
00:23:21.526 --> 00:23:22.902
荷普？
Hope?

297
00:23:24.487 --> 00:23:25.488
（保全）

298
00:23:32.537 --> 00:23:35.040
（救命！）

299
00:23:44.841 --> 00:23:47.385
（失蹤）

300
00:23:56.102 --> 00:23:57.103
小朋友！
Kid!

301
00:23:57.270 --> 00:23:58.313
喂，小朋友
Hey, kid!

302
00:24:02.650 --> 00:24:04.861
這裡發生什麼事？
What the hell happened here?

303
00:24:25.507 --> 00:24:27.717
（消逝者）

304
00:24:36.518 --> 00:24:38.311
天啊
Oh, my God!

305
00:24:41.147 --> 00:24:42.607
拜託
Oh, please!

306
00:24:42.774 --> 00:24:44.317
拜託…
Please, please!

307
00:24:44.484 --> 00:24:46.486
不…
No, no, no. No.

308
00:24:47.946 --> 00:24:49.322
不
No.

309
00:24:51.658 --> 00:24:52.659
抱歉
Excuse me. Sorry.

310
00:24:52.826 --> 00:24:54.119
凱西，不
Oh, Cassie, no.

311
00:24:54.285 --> 00:24:55.745
不…
No, no, no.

312
00:24:57.122 --> 00:24:58.832
不
No, no.

313
00:24:59.749 --> 00:25:02.669
拜託…不要有凱西
Please, please, please. No, Cassie.

314
00:25:04.921 --> 00:25:08.091
（史考特朗恩）

315
00:25:09.884 --> 00:25:11.052
什麼？
What?

316
00:25:41.124 --> 00:25:42.459
凱西？
Cassie?

317
00:25:43.626 --> 00:25:45.003
爸
Dad?

318
00:26:11.029 --> 00:26:12.781
妳長這麼大了
You're so big!

319
00:26:14.616 --> 00:26:17.660
（管制區，請勿進入）

320
00:26:26.753 --> 00:26:31.257
我們登上丹佛斯發現的可疑戰艦
Yeah. We boarded that highly-suspect warship Danvers pinged.

321
00:26:31.424 --> 00:26:33.134
那是艘髒亂不堪的垃圾船
It was an infectious garbage scow.

322
00:26:33.301 --> 00:26:34.761
感謝提供珍貴情報
So, thanks for the hot tip.

323
00:26:34.928 --> 00:26:36.262
你們比較接近嘛
Well, you were closer.

324
00:26:36.429 --> 00:26:37.722
現在我們渾身垃圾味
Yeah. And now we smell like garbage.

325
00:26:37.889 --> 00:26:39.224
有那些震動的讀數嗎？
You get a reading on those tremors?

326
00:26:39.391 --> 00:26:41.976
那是非洲板塊底下的輕微隱沒作用
'Twas a mild subduction under the African plate.

327
00:26:42.143 --> 00:26:44.187
有影像嗎？如何處理？
Do we have a visual? How are we handling it?

328
00:26:44.354 --> 00:26:45.522
小娜
Nat.

329
00:26:45.980 --> 00:26:47.941
那是海底的地震
It's an earthquake under the ocean.

330
00:26:48.108 --> 00:26:50.944
不需要處理
We handle it by not handling it.

331
00:26:51.695 --> 00:26:53.822
卡蘿，下個月妳會來嗎？
Carol, are we seeing you here next month?

332
00:26:54.280 --> 00:26:56.991
-應該不會 -妳又要去剪頭髮嗎？
Not likely. What? You gonna get another haircut?

333
00:26:57.158 --> 00:26:58.493
聽好，毛毛臉
Listen, fur face.

334
00:26:58.660 --> 00:27:00.453
我負責的區域非常大
I'm covering a lot of territory.

335
00:27:00.620 --> 00:27:03.748
其他地方都跟地球發生同樣的情形
The things that are happening on Earth are happening everywhere.

336
00:27:04.082 --> 00:27:05.917
幾千顆星球
On thousands of planets.

337
00:27:06.084 --> 00:27:08.753
好啦，有道理
All right, all right. That's a good point.

338
00:27:08.920 --> 00:27:11.006
你們應該很久都見不到我
That's a good point. So, you might not see me for a long time.

339
00:27:11.840 --> 00:27:13.508
好吧
All right. Uh, well...

340
00:27:14.384 --> 00:27:16.511
這個頻道隨時暢通
This channel's always active.

341
00:27:16.678 --> 00:27:18.763
只要出了問題
So, if anything goes sideways...

342
00:27:18.930 --> 00:27:21.349
有人無故製造麻煩
anyone's making trouble where they shouldn't...

343
00:27:21.516 --> 00:27:22.684
請通知我
comes through me.

344
00:27:23.476 --> 00:27:24.310
好
Okay.

345
00:27:24.477 --> 00:27:25.937
好吧
All right.

346
00:27:26.688 --> 00:27:27.772
祝你好運
Good luck.

347
00:27:36.364 --> 00:27:37.365
你在哪？
Where are you?

348
00:27:37.532 --> 00:27:38.533
墨西哥
Mexico.

349
00:27:38.700 --> 00:27:41.327
聯邦人員發現一個滿是屍體的房間
The Federales found a room full of bodies.

350
00:27:41.494 --> 00:27:43.121
看來是販毒集團
Looks like a bunch of cartel guys...

351
00:27:43.288 --> 00:27:45.248
連開槍的機會都沒有
never even had a chance to get their guns off.

352
00:27:45.415 --> 00:27:47.125
應該是敵對幫派幹的
It's probably a rival gang.

353
00:27:47.292 --> 00:27:48.501
並不是
Except it isn't.

354
00:27:48.752 --> 00:27:50.837
絕對是巴頓
It's definitely Barton.

355
00:27:51.421 --> 00:27:53.006
他在這裡的所作所為
What he's done here...

356
00:27:53.173 --> 00:27:56.343
過去幾年來幹的好事
what he's been doing for the last few years...

357
00:27:57.177 --> 00:27:58.970
他造成的後果…
I mean, the scene that he left...

358
00:27:59.971 --> 00:28:03.516
其實我並不是那麼想找到他
I gotta tell you, there's a part of me that doesn't even wanna find him.

359
00:28:09.105 --> 00:28:11.358
你能發現他接下來的去處嗎？
Will you find out where he's going next?

360
00:28:15.278 --> 00:28:16.404
小娜？
Nat?

361
00:28:18.198 --> 00:28:19.908
求求你
Please?

362
00:28:21.659 --> 00:28:22.827
好吧
Okay.

363
00:28:31.628 --> 00:28:33.463
我想幫妳煮晚餐
You know, I'd offer to cook you dinner...

364
00:28:33.797 --> 00:28:35.382
不過妳已經夠慘了
but you seem pretty miserable already.

365
00:28:39.469 --> 00:28:40.887
你來洗衣服嗎？
You here to do your laundry?

366
00:28:41.054 --> 00:28:42.639
還有看朋友
And to see a friend.

367
00:28:43.723 --> 00:28:46.393
你朋友明明好得很
Clearly, your friend is fine.

368
00:28:49.145 --> 00:28:51.648
我過橋時看到一群鯨魚
You know, I saw a pod of whales when I was coming over the bridge.

369
00:28:51.815 --> 00:28:53.650
-哈德遜河？ -船變少了…
- In the Hudson? - There's fewer ships...

370
00:28:53.817 --> 00:28:55.068
水變乾淨了
cleaner water.

371
00:28:55.235 --> 00:28:59.155
如果你想叫我看開點
You know, if you're about to tell me to look on the bright side...

372
00:29:01.533 --> 00:29:05.120
我就用花生醬三明治丟你的頭
Um... I'm about to hit you in the head with a peanut butter sandwich.

373
00:29:07.080 --> 00:29:08.248
抱歉
Hmm. Sorry.

374
00:29:08.415 --> 00:29:09.582
老毛病
Force of habit.

375
00:29:23.847 --> 00:29:26.975
我不斷告訴別人應該放下過去
You know, I keep telling everybody they should move on...

376
00:29:27.308 --> 00:29:28.810
成長
and grow.

377
00:29:30.020 --> 00:29:31.312
有的人可以
Some do.

378
00:29:34.774 --> 00:29:36.276
我們辦不到
But not us.

379
00:29:37.027 --> 00:29:39.070
如果我放下過去，誰來扛？
If I move on, who does this?

380
00:29:39.446 --> 00:29:41.573
也許不需要有人扛
Maybe it doesn't need to be done.

381
00:29:45.785 --> 00:29:48.038
從前我一無所有
I used to have nothing.

382
00:29:49.039 --> 00:29:51.124
後來有了這個
And then I got this.

383
00:29:53.293 --> 00:29:55.128
這個任務
This job.

384
00:29:57.505 --> 00:29:59.257
這個家庭
This family.

385
00:30:03.055 --> 00:30:06.931
我因此變得更好
And I was better because of it.

386
00:30:13.188 --> 00:30:16.733
即使他們走了
And even though they're gone...

387
00:30:20.695 --> 00:30:23.114
我還是想變得更好
I'm still trying to be better.

388
00:30:26.159 --> 00:30:28.578
我們都應該好好過日子
I think we both need to get a life.

389
00:30:30.997 --> 00:30:32.415
你先
You first.

390
00:30:37.962 --> 00:30:40.423
嗨，有人在嗎？
Oh, hi, hi! Uh, is anyone home?

391
00:30:40.590 --> 00:30:42.300
我是史考特朗恩
This is, uh, Scott Lang.

392
00:30:42.467 --> 00:30:45.303
我們幾年前在德國的機場
We met a few years ago at the airport...

393
00:30:45.470 --> 00:30:47.138
見過面
in Germany?

394
00:30:47.305 --> 00:30:49.599
我變成巨人，戴著頭盔
I was the guy that got really big. I had a mask on.

395
00:30:49.766 --> 00:30:51.267
-你們認不出我 -這是舊訊息嗎？
- You wouldn't recognize me. - Is this an old message?

396
00:30:51.434 --> 00:30:54.396
蟻人，我知道你們曉得
Ant-Man? I know you know that.

397
00:30:54.562 --> 00:30:57.148
-他在前門 -我真的需要跟你們談
It's the front gate. I really need to talk to you guys.

398
00:31:03.321 --> 00:31:04.489
史考特
Scott.

399
00:31:05.448 --> 00:31:06.449
你還好嗎？
Are you okay?

400
00:31:06.616 --> 00:31:07.617
嗯
Yeah.

401
00:31:09.411 --> 00:31:11.788
你們念過量子物理學嗎？
Have either of you guys ever studied quantum physics?

402
00:31:12.205 --> 00:31:13.707
只拿來聊天打屁
Only to make conversation.

403
00:31:14.791 --> 00:31:16.418
好
All right, so...

404
00:31:16.793 --> 00:31:19.504
五年前，就在…
five years ago, right before...

405
00:31:20.088 --> 00:31:21.214
薩諾斯之前
Thanos...

406
00:31:21.589 --> 00:31:23.675
我到了量子領域裡
I was in a place called the quantum realm.

407
00:31:23.842 --> 00:31:26.344
量子領域自成一個微型宇宙
The quantum realm is like its own microscopic universe.

408
00:31:26.511 --> 00:31:28.638
你必須變得極小才能進去
To get in there, you have to be incredibly small.

409
00:31:28.805 --> 00:31:30.348
荷普，她是我的…
Hope. She's my, um...

410
00:31:32.434 --> 00:31:34.144
她是我的…
She was my...

411
00:31:35.854 --> 00:31:37.063
她應該讓我出去
She was supposed to pull me out.

412
00:31:37.230 --> 00:31:38.815
後來發生了薩諾斯事件
And then Thanos happened...

413
00:31:38.982 --> 00:31:40.650
我因而困在裡面
and I got stuck in there.

414
00:31:41.109 --> 00:31:43.069
很遺憾，那五年想必很漫長
I'm sorry, that must have been a very long five years.

415
00:31:43.236 --> 00:31:44.571
重點就在這裡
Yeah, but that's just it.

416
00:31:44.738 --> 00:31:45.905
並不是
It wasn't.

417
00:31:46.072 --> 00:31:47.282
對我來說只是五小時
For me, it was five hours.

418
00:31:47.449 --> 00:31:49.868
量子領域毫無規則可言
See, the rules of the quantum realm aren't like they are up here.

419
00:31:50.035 --> 00:31:51.578
一切都無法預測
Everything is unpredictable.

420
00:31:51.745 --> 00:31:52.954
那是誰的三明治？
Is that anybody's sandwich?

421
00:31:53.121 --> 00:31:54.372
我餓扁了
I'm starving.

422
00:31:54.706 --> 00:31:55.832
史考特
Scott.

423
00:31:55.999 --> 00:31:57.292
你在說什麼？
What are you talking about?

424
00:31:58.293 --> 00:31:59.544
所以…
So...

425
00:32:00.503 --> 00:32:02.088
我想說的是…
what I'm saying is...

426
00:32:02.964 --> 00:32:05.383
量子領域裡的時間不一樣
time works differently in the quantum realm.

427
00:32:05.550 --> 00:32:08.845
唯一的問題是我們在裡面找不到方向
The only problem is right now we don't have a way to navigate it.

428
00:32:09.012 --> 00:32:10.013
要是可以呢？
But what if we did?

429
00:32:10.764 --> 00:32:13.975
我忍不住想，要是我們能控制混亂局面
I can't stop thinking about it. What if we could somehow control the chaos...

430
00:32:14.142 --> 00:32:15.268
在裡面找到方向呢？
and we could navigate it?

431
00:32:15.435 --> 00:32:16.936
要是有辦法…
What if there was a way...

432
00:32:17.103 --> 00:32:19.898
在某個時間點進入量子領域
that we could enter the quantum realm at a certain point in time...

433
00:32:20.065 --> 00:32:22.776
又在另一個時間點離開量子領域呢？
but then exit the quantum realm at another point in time?

434
00:32:22.942 --> 00:32:24.277
譬如…
Like...

435
00:32:25.028 --> 00:32:27.113
-譬如薩諾斯事件之前 -等等
- Like before Thanos. - Wait.

436
00:32:27.280 --> 00:32:28.865
你說的是時間機器嗎？
Are you talking about a time machine?

437
00:32:29.032 --> 00:32:31.785
當然不是，不是時間機器
No. No, of course not. No, not a time machine.

438
00:32:31.951 --> 00:32:32.994
這比較像…
This is more like a...

439
00:32:35.205 --> 00:32:36.956
對，像時間機器
Yeah. Like a time machine.

440
00:32:37.123 --> 00:32:38.917
我知道很誇張，很誇張
I know, it's crazy. It's crazy.

441
00:32:39.668 --> 00:32:42.462
但我忍不住一直想，應該…
But I can't stop thinking about it. There's gotta be...

442
00:32:43.213 --> 00:32:44.506
有辦法
some way...

443
00:32:44.673 --> 00:32:46.466
-太誇張了 -史考特
- It's crazy. - Scott.

444
00:32:46.633 --> 00:32:47.926
我會收到浣熊寄來的電郵
I get emails from a raccoon...

445
00:32:48.093 --> 00:32:50.095
已經沒什麼叫太誇張了
so nothing sounds crazy anymore.

446
00:32:50.845 --> 00:32:52.931
那我們必須找誰談？
So, who do we talk to about this?

447
00:33:11.032 --> 00:33:12.117
吃飯了
Chow time!

448
00:33:14.577 --> 00:33:15.620
小摩
Maguna.

449
00:33:20.041 --> 00:33:21.418
摩根史塔克，想吃午餐嗎？
Morgan H. Stark, you want some lunch?

450
00:33:22.585 --> 00:33:24.796
解釋午餐，不然死翹翹 -好啦
Define "lunch" or be disintegrated. - Okay.

451
00:33:26.172 --> 00:33:27.632
妳不應該戴這個
You should not be wearing that, okay?

452
00:33:27.799 --> 00:33:30.343
這是我做給媽媽的週年紀念禮物
That is part of a special anniversary gift I'm making for Mom.

453
00:33:34.097 --> 00:33:36.683
拿起來，想吃午餐嗎？
There you go. You thinking about lunch?

454
00:33:36.850 --> 00:33:38.768
我弄蟋蟀配生菜給妳吃
I can give you a handful of crickets on a bed of lettuce.

455
00:33:38.935 --> 00:33:40.645
-不要 -那是妳想吃的啊
- No. - That's what you want.

456
00:33:40.812 --> 00:33:42.939
妳怎麼發現這個的？
How did you find this?

457
00:33:43.106 --> 00:33:44.941
-車庫 -真的嗎？
- Garage. - Really?

458
00:33:45.108 --> 00:33:47.110
-妳去找這個嗎？ -沒有
- Were you looking for it? - No.

459
00:33:47.986 --> 00:33:49.863
不過是我發現的
- I found it, though. - Hmm.

460
00:33:50.030 --> 00:33:51.781
妳喜歡去車庫喔？
You like going in the garage, huh?

461
00:33:51.948 --> 00:33:53.199
把拔也是
So does Daddy.

462
00:33:53.950 --> 00:33:56.786
沒關係，媽不戴我買給她的東西
It's fine, actually. Mom never wears anything I buy her.

463
00:33:59.497 --> 00:34:00.749
那我就…
So, I'm gonna...

464
00:34:18.266 --> 00:34:20.810
不，我們知道聽起來很扯
No. We know what it sounds like.

465
00:34:20.977 --> 00:34:22.645
東尼，以你的經驗，真的有可能嗎？
Tony, after everything you've seen, is anything really impossible?

466
00:34:22.812 --> 00:34:25.315
量子漲落破壞普朗克尺度
Quantum fluctuation messes with the Planck scale...

467
00:34:25.482 --> 00:34:28.276
接著引發德意志命題，這我們同意吧？
which then triggers the Deutsch Proposition. Can we agree on that?

468
00:34:28.443 --> 00:34:29.527
謝謝
Thank you.

469
00:34:29.694 --> 00:34:31.821
講白話，這表示回不了家
In layman's terms, it means you're not coming home.

470
00:34:32.155 --> 00:34:33.406
-我回來了 -不對
- I did. - No.

471
00:34:33.573 --> 00:34:34.991
你是意外活下來
You accidentally survived.

472
00:34:35.533 --> 00:34:37.702
十億分之一的僥倖
It's a billion-to-one cosmic fluke.

473
00:34:37.869 --> 00:34:40.955
現在你想…那叫什麼？
And now you wanna pull a... What do you call it?

474
00:34:42.999 --> 00:34:44.334
時間攔劫？
A time heist?

475
00:34:44.501 --> 00:34:47.837
對，時間攔劫，以前怎麼沒想到？
Yeah, a time heist. Of course. Why didn't we think of this before?

476
00:34:48.004 --> 00:34:50.465
因為很可笑，癡人說夢
Oh, because it's laughable. Because it's a pipe dream.

477
00:34:50.632 --> 00:34:54.219
無限寶石在過去，我們能回去搶過來
The stones are in the past. We could go back, we could get them.

478
00:34:54.386 --> 00:34:56.680
我們一彈指就能救回所有人
We can snap our own fingers. We can bring everybody back.

479
00:34:56.846 --> 00:34:58.765
或者火上加油
Or screw it up worse than he already has, right?

480
00:34:58.932 --> 00:34:59.933
我認為不會
I don't believe we would.

481
00:35:00.517 --> 00:35:03.061
有時好懷念這種天真的樂觀態度
Gotta say it. I sometimes miss that giddy optimism.

482
00:35:03.937 --> 00:35:05.647
寄予厚望並沒有幫助
However, high hopes won't help...

483
00:35:05.814 --> 00:35:11.319
如果缺少安全執行時間攔劫的具體方法
if there's no logical, tangible way for me to safely execute said time heist.

484
00:35:11.486 --> 00:35:14.322
我想最可能的結果是我們集體死亡
I believe the most likely outcome will be our collective demise.

485
00:35:14.489 --> 00:35:17.367
嚴格遵守時間旅行的規則就不會
Not if we strictly follow the rules of time travel.

486
00:35:17.534 --> 00:35:20.120
也就是不跟過去的自己對話
All right? It means no talking to our past selves...

487
00:35:20.286 --> 00:35:21.830
不賭運動比賽
no betting on sporting events.

488
00:35:21.996 --> 00:35:23.748
我要請你住嘴，史考特
I'm gonna stop you right there, Scott.

489
00:35:24.666 --> 00:35:27.919
你意思是說你拯救宇宙的計畫
Are you seriously telling me that your plan to save the universe...

490
00:35:28.086 --> 00:35:29.754
是根據《回到未來》？
is based on Back to the Future?

491
00:35:30.880 --> 00:35:32.632
-是嗎？ -不是
- Is it? - No.

492
00:35:32.799 --> 00:35:34.968
你害我擔心了一下，那根本狗屁不通
Good. You had me worried there. 'Cause that would be horseshit.

493
00:35:35.135 --> 00:35:37.429
量子物理學不是那樣運作的
That's not how quantum physics works.

494
00:35:37.595 --> 00:35:38.763
東尼
Tony.

495
00:35:40.724 --> 00:35:42.183
我們必須堅定立場
We have to take a stand.

496
00:35:42.851 --> 00:35:44.728
我們有，卻落得如此下場
We did stand. And yet, here we are.

497
00:35:47.063 --> 00:35:48.356
我知道你得冒很大的風險
I know you got a lot on the line.

498
00:35:48.857 --> 00:35:51.401
你有老婆，女兒
You got a wife, a daughter.

499
00:35:51.568 --> 00:35:54.070
但我失去了一個非常重要的人
But I lost someone very important to me.

500
00:35:54.237 --> 00:35:55.822
很多人也一樣
A lotta people did.

501
00:35:55.989 --> 00:35:58.992
現在我們有機會把她救回來
And now, now we have a chance to bring her back...

502
00:35:59.159 --> 00:36:01.828
把所有人救回來，你卻說你根本不…
to bring everyone back, and you're telling me that you won't even...

503
00:36:01.995 --> 00:36:03.788
沒錯，我根本不願意
That's right, Scott. I won't even.

504
00:36:05.498 --> 00:36:06.833
我不能
I can't.

505
00:36:09.002 --> 00:36:11.254
媽咪叫我來救你
Mommy told me to come and save you.

506
00:36:11.421 --> 00:36:13.840
很好，我得救了
Good job. I'm saved.

507
00:36:14.591 --> 00:36:17.761
真希望你們是來問別的事，什麼都好
I wish you were coming here to ask me something else. Anything else.

508
00:36:17.927 --> 00:36:19.721
很高興見到你們
I'm honestly happy to see you guys, I just...

509
00:36:19.888 --> 00:36:21.514
-午餐準備了六人份 -東尼
Oh, look, the table's set for six.

510
00:36:21.681 --> 00:36:22.766
我懂
Tony. I get it.

511
00:36:22.932 --> 00:36:25.226
我替你高興，真的
And I'm happy for you. I really am.

512
00:36:26.019 --> 00:36:27.520
但這是第二次機會
But this is a second chance.

513
00:36:28.229 --> 00:36:30.648
我的第二次機會在這裡，隊長
I got my second chance right here, Cap.

514
00:36:30.815 --> 00:36:32.359
不能冒險
Can't roll the dice on it.

515
00:36:34.444 --> 00:36:36.363
不聊工作的話請留下來吃飯
If you don't talk shop, you can stay for lunch.

516
00:36:39.616 --> 00:36:40.825
他怕了
Well, he's scared.

517
00:36:41.493 --> 00:36:42.535
他也沒錯
He's not wrong.

518
00:36:42.702 --> 00:36:44.704
那我們怎麼辦？
Yeah, but, I mean, what are we gonna do?

519
00:36:44.871 --> 00:36:46.164
我們需要他，難道就此收手嗎？
We need him. What, are we gonna stop?

520
00:36:47.082 --> 00:36:49.084
不，我想妥善規劃
No, I wanna do it right.

521
00:36:52.295 --> 00:36:53.963
我們需要一個非常聰明的人
We're gonna need a really big brain.

522
00:36:55.048 --> 00:36:56.466
比他還聰明？
Bigger than his?

523
00:36:56.925 --> 00:36:59.552
好像只有我在吃，嚐嚐看嘛
Come on, I feel like I'm the only one eating here.

524
00:36:59.719 --> 00:37:00.720
吃點蛋
Try some of that. Have some eggs.

525
00:37:01.221 --> 00:37:02.472
我搞糊塗了
I'm so confused.

526
00:37:02.639 --> 00:37:04.307
這年頭是很讓人困惑
These are confusing times.

527
00:37:04.474 --> 00:37:06.393
我不是那意思
Right, no, no. That's not what I meant.

528
00:37:06.559 --> 00:37:09.062
我瞭，開玩笑的
Nah, I get it. I'm kidding!

529
00:37:09.646 --> 00:37:11.439
我知道很扯
I know, it's crazy.

530
00:37:11.606 --> 00:37:12.816
我竟然穿衣服
I'm wearing shirts now.

531
00:37:12.982 --> 00:37:15.819
對啊，怎麼會？為什麼？
Yeah. What? How? Why?

532
00:37:16.277 --> 00:37:18.613
五年前，我們吃了敗仗
Five years ago, we got our asses beat.

533
00:37:19.239 --> 00:37:20.865
只是我更慘
Except it was worse for me...

534
00:37:21.032 --> 00:37:22.242
我輸了兩次
'cause I lost twice.

535
00:37:22.409 --> 00:37:24.202
首先浩克輸了，班納又輸
First, Hulk lost, then Banner lost...

536
00:37:25.078 --> 00:37:26.329
然後我們全都輸了
and then, we all lost.

537
00:37:26.496 --> 00:37:27.747
沒人怪你，布魯斯
No one blamed you, Bruce.

538
00:37:27.914 --> 00:37:29.290
我怪我自己
I did.

539
00:37:31.042 --> 00:37:33.420
多年來我把浩克當成一種病
For years, I've been treating the Hulk like he's some kind

540
00:37:33.586 --> 00:37:35.046
想去之而後快
of disease... something to get rid of.

541
00:37:35.797 --> 00:37:38.466
後來我開始將他視為解藥
But then, I start looking at him as the cure.

542
00:37:39.050 --> 00:37:41.177
在伽瑪實驗室研究了18個月
Eighteen months in the gamma lab.

543
00:37:41.344 --> 00:37:43.930
將智慧與體力結合起來
I put the brains and the brawn together...

544
00:37:44.097 --> 00:37:45.348
現在看看我
and now, look at me.

545
00:37:46.391 --> 00:37:47.726
頭腦和四肢同樣發達
Best of both worlds.

546
00:37:48.476 --> 00:37:49.811
-對不起，浩克先生？ -是
- Excuse me, Mr. Hulk? - Yes.

547
00:37:49.978 --> 00:37:51.312
我們能跟你合照嗎？
Can we get a photo?

548
00:37:51.730 --> 00:37:53.732
沒問題，小朋友
100%, little person.

549
00:37:53.898 --> 00:37:55.942
過來…幫我們拍？
Come on, step on up. Do you mind?

550
00:37:56.651 --> 00:37:58.319
-好啊 -謝謝
- Oh, yeah, yeah. - Thanks.

551
00:37:58.486 --> 00:38:00.071
說七
Say "green."

552
00:38:00.238 --> 00:38:02.490
-七 -七
- Green. - Green.

553
00:38:02.657 --> 00:38:03.575
拍到了嗎？
Did you get that?

554
00:38:03.742 --> 00:38:04.993
很好看
That's a good one.

555
00:38:05.785 --> 00:38:08.038
想跟我合照嗎？我是蟻人
Did you want to grab one with me? I'm Ant-Man.

556
00:38:11.708 --> 00:38:13.626
他們是浩克粉絲，不認識蟻人
They're Hulk fans. They don't know Ant-Man.

557
00:38:13.793 --> 00:38:14.878
沒人認識我
Nobody does.

558
00:38:15.045 --> 00:38:16.588
-他要你跟他合照 -我不想拍
- No, he wants you to take a picture with him. - I don't want a picture.

559
00:38:16.755 --> 00:38:17.756
小心怪叔叔
Stranger danger.

560
00:38:17.922 --> 00:38:19.466
他竟然拒絕
Yeah, look, he's even saying no, he doesn't.

561
00:38:19.632 --> 00:38:21.676
-我懂了，我也不想拍 -別這樣
I get it. I don't want it, either.

562
00:38:21.843 --> 00:38:23.261
我不想跟他們合照
But come on. The kid... I don't want a picture with them.

563
00:38:23.428 --> 00:38:24.429
-他會很難過 -抱歉
- He's gonna feel bad. - Sorry.

564
00:38:24.596 --> 00:38:25.764
他們很樂意合照
They're happy to do it. They said they'll do it.

565
00:38:25.930 --> 00:38:27.390
-我不想拍 -我們可以
- I don't want to do it. - We can do it.

566
00:38:27.557 --> 00:38:29.559
-你不爽了 -手機拿去
- No, you feel bad. - Take the goddamn phone.

567
00:38:29.726 --> 00:38:30.894
好
Okay.

568
00:38:31.311 --> 00:38:33.730
-謝謝你，浩克先生 -很棒，謝謝你們
Thank you, Mr. Hulk. No, it was great, kids. Thank you very much.

569
00:38:34.189 --> 00:38:35.565
浩克萬歲
Hulk out!

570
00:38:35.732 --> 00:38:36.608
布魯斯
Bruce.

571
00:38:37.192 --> 00:38:38.193
帥
Dab.

572
00:38:38.526 --> 00:38:40.153
-布魯斯 -要聽媽媽的話
- Bruce. - Listen to your mom.

573
00:38:40.528 --> 00:38:41.529
她懂比較多
She knows better.

574
00:38:41.696 --> 00:38:43.365
關於我們說的事
About what we were saying.

575
00:38:43.531 --> 00:38:44.741
對
Right.

576
00:38:46.701 --> 00:38:49.371
靠時間旅行來逆轉？
The whole time travel do-over?

577
00:38:50.663 --> 00:38:54.417
那超出我的專業領域
Eh, guys, it's outside of my area of expertise.

578
00:38:54.876 --> 00:38:56.127
你成功轉型了啊
Well, you pulled this off.

579
00:38:57.170 --> 00:39:00.965
以前這也是不可能的任務
I remember a time when that seemed pretty impossible, too.

580
00:39:34.249 --> 00:39:37.085
我有一點靈感，想看看是否正確
I've got a mild inspiration. I'd like to see if it checks out.

581
00:39:37.252 --> 00:39:41.006
睡前我想做最後一次模擬
So, I'd like to run one last sim before we pack it in for the night.

582
00:39:41.172 --> 00:39:45.552
這次用反轉的莫比烏斯帶形狀
This time, in the shape of a Möbius strip, inverted, please.

583
00:39:45.719 --> 00:39:46.803
處理中
Processing.

584
00:39:50.265 --> 00:39:52.767
給我那個粒子的特徵值
Right, give me the eigenvalue of that particle...

585
00:39:52.934 --> 00:39:54.936
並考慮頻譜分解
factoring in spectral decomp.

586
00:39:55.103 --> 00:39:57.063
-這需要一段時間 -請稍候
- That'll take a second. - Just a moment.

587
00:39:58.106 --> 00:40:00.984
不順利的話也別擔心，我…
And don't worry if it doesn't pan out. I'm just kinda...

588
00:40:02.527 --> 00:40:04.029
模型成形
Model rendered.

589
00:40:06.406 --> 00:40:07.323
（模型成功）

590
00:40:15.832 --> 00:40:16.666
靠！
Shit!

591
00:40:17.167 --> 00:40:18.043
靠！
Shit!

592
00:40:22.464 --> 00:40:24.174
妳怎麼起來了，小姐？
What are you doing up, little miss?

593
00:40:24.341 --> 00:40:26.051
-靠 -不能說這個字
- Shit. - Nope. We don't say that.

594
00:40:26.217 --> 00:40:27.427
只有媽咪才能說
Only Mommy says that word.

595
00:40:27.594 --> 00:40:29.012
她發明的，媽咪專用
She coined it. It belongs to her.

596
00:40:29.179 --> 00:40:30.138
你怎麼起來了？
Why are you up?

597
00:40:30.305 --> 00:40:31.681
因為我有重要的事要做
'Cause I've got some important shit going on here!

598
00:40:31.848 --> 00:40:33.016
妳覺得呢？
Why do you think?

599
00:40:33.183 --> 00:40:36.144
不，我在想事情…
No, I got something on my mind.

600
00:40:36.311 --> 00:40:37.854
你在想果汁冰棒嗎？
I got something on my mind. Was it juice pops?

601
00:40:39.397 --> 00:40:40.607
當然
Sure was.

602
00:40:42.025 --> 00:40:43.777
妳勒索我
That's extortion. That's a word.

603
00:40:43.943 --> 00:40:45.111
妳要哪一種？
What kind you want?

604
00:40:45.278 --> 00:40:46.279
英雄所見略同
Great minds think alike.

605
00:40:46.446 --> 00:40:48.281
果汁冰棒就是…
Juice pops exactly...

606
00:40:48.300 --> 00:40:51.576
我腦袋在想的
was on my mind.

607
00:40:52.994 --> 00:40:54.120
吃完了嗎？
You done? Yeah?

608
00:40:54.662 --> 00:40:55.872
吃完了
Now you are.

609
00:40:56.456 --> 00:40:57.624
擦擦
Here. Wipe.

610
00:41:00.335 --> 00:41:03.004
好，躺下去
Good. That face goes there.

611
00:41:03.171 --> 00:41:04.422
說故事給我聽
Tell me a story.

612
00:41:04.589 --> 00:41:06.174
故事
A story.

613
00:41:06.341 --> 00:41:08.468
很久以前，小摩上床睡覺，完
Once upon a time, Maguna went to bed. The end.

614
00:41:08.843 --> 00:41:10.220
好爛的故事
That is a horrible story.

615
00:41:10.387 --> 00:41:12.138
這是妳最喜歡的故事
Come on, that's your favourite story.

616
00:41:12.847 --> 00:41:14.015
愛妳喔
Love you tons.

617
00:41:16.017 --> 00:41:17.852
我愛你三千次
I love you 3,000.

618
00:41:19.104 --> 00:41:20.105
哇
Wow.

619
00:41:27.445 --> 00:41:30.323
三千次，超多的
3,000. That's crazy.

620
00:41:31.533 --> 00:41:33.326
睡覺，不然賣掉妳的玩具
Go to bed or I'll sell all your toys.

621
00:41:34.536 --> 00:41:35.870
晚安
Night night.

622
00:41:36.037 --> 00:41:37.247
這不是比賽
Not that it's a competition...

623
00:41:37.747 --> 00:41:39.666
不過她愛我三千次
but she loves me 3,000.

624
00:41:39.833 --> 00:41:40.917
是喔？
Does she, now?

625
00:41:41.084 --> 00:41:44.129
妳只有六百到九百次
You were somewhere in the low 6 to 900 range.

626
00:41:50.176 --> 00:41:51.678
在看什麼？
Whatcha reading?

627
00:41:52.303 --> 00:41:53.763
製作堆肥的書
Just a book on composting.

628
00:41:53.930 --> 00:41:56.016
堆肥有什麼新發展？
What's new with composting?

629
00:41:57.475 --> 00:41:59.519
-有趣的科學… -我想通了
- Interesting science... - I figured it out.

630
00:42:00.603 --> 00:42:01.604
順便說一聲
By the way.

631
00:42:02.480 --> 00:42:05.859
我們講的是同一件事…
And, you know, just so we're talking about the same thing...

632
00:42:06.026 --> 00:42:07.485
時間旅行
Time travel.

633
00:42:08.153 --> 00:42:08.987
什麼？
What?

634
00:42:13.199 --> 00:42:14.200
哇
Wow.

635
00:42:16.288 --> 00:42:19.000
好驚人
That's amazing...

636
00:42:19.000  --> 00:42:21.916
也好可怕
and terrifying.

637
00:42:22.083 --> 00:42:23.543
沒錯
That's right.

638
00:42:30.842 --> 00:42:32.552
我們真的很幸運
We got really lucky.

639
00:42:32.719 --> 00:42:33.720
嗯
Yeah.

640
00:42:33.887 --> 00:42:35.013
我知道
I know.

641
00:42:35.180 --> 00:42:36.306
很多人沒這麼好運
A lot of people didn't.

642
00:42:36.473 --> 00:42:38.099
對，我救不了所有人
Nope. And I can't help everybody.

643
00:42:39.851 --> 00:42:41.186
感覺好像你可以
Sorta seems like you can.

644
00:42:41.353 --> 00:42:42.979
我停止的話就不能
Not if I stop.

645
00:42:44.147 --> 00:42:47.025
我能馬上煞車，停止
I can put a pin in it right now and stop.

646
00:42:47.817 --> 00:42:48.818
東尼
Tony...

647
00:42:49.527 --> 00:42:51.071
設法阻止你
trying to get you to stop...

648
00:42:51.237 --> 00:42:53.865
是我這輩子最大的敗筆之一
has been one of the few failures of my entire life.

649
00:42:58.161 --> 00:42:59.829
我有種感覺
Something tells me...

650
00:43:01.122 --> 00:43:03.792
我應該把它鎖進箱子，丟到湖底
I should put it in a lockbox and drop it to the bottom of the lake...

651
00:43:05.001 --> 00:43:06.211
上床睡覺
and go to bed.

652
00:43:12.592 --> 00:43:14.636
但你睡得著嗎？
But would you be able to rest?

653
00:43:19.349 --> 00:43:22.686
開始，時間旅行第一次測試
Okay, here we go. Time travel test number one.

654
00:43:22.852 --> 00:43:25.021
史考特，發動…
Scott, fire up...

655
00:43:25.939 --> 00:43:27.107
廂型車
the, uh, van thing.

656
00:43:29.401 --> 00:43:30.443
斷路器準備
Breakers are set.

657
00:43:30.610 --> 00:43:32.445
緊急發電機就緒
Emergency generators are on standby.

658
00:43:32.612 --> 00:43:37.534
要是斷電，我可不想在50年代失去奈米哥
Good, because if we blow the grid, I don't want to lose, uh, Tiny here in the 1950s.

659
00:43:37.701 --> 00:43:38.535
你說什麼？
- Excuse me?

660
00:43:38.702 --> 00:43:40.662
他開玩笑的
- He's kidding.

661
00:43:40.829 --> 00:43:42.789
你不能說這種話
You can't say things like that.

662
00:43:42.956 --> 00:43:44.457
冷笑話
It was a bad joke.

663
00:43:46.459 --> 00:43:47.419
你開玩笑的吧？
You were kidding, right?

664
00:43:47.585 --> 00:43:50.714
我不知道，這可是時間旅行
I have no idea. We're talking about time travel here.

665
00:43:50.880 --> 00:43:53.133
可能全是笑話，也可能都不是
Either it's all a joke, or none of it is.

666
00:43:53.299 --> 00:43:54.968
搞定了
We're good!

667
00:43:55.135 --> 00:43:56.469
戴上頭盔
Get your helmet on.

668
00:43:57.095 --> 00:43:58.888
史考特，我送你回到一週前
Scott, I'm gonna send you back a week...

669
00:43:59.055 --> 00:44:02.267
讓你待一小時，十秒後帶你回來
let you walk around for an hour, then bring you back in 10 seconds.

670
00:44:02.434 --> 00:44:03.435
有道理嗎？
Make sense?

671
00:44:04.102 --> 00:44:05.353
十分清楚
Perfectly not confusing.

672
00:44:05.520 --> 00:44:07.480
祝你好運，史考特，你沒問題的
Good luck, Scott. You got this.

673
00:44:09.024 --> 00:44:12.068
對，我沒問題，美國隊長…
You're right. I do, Captain America.

674
00:44:14.237 --> 00:44:15.572
倒數三秒
On a count of three...

675
00:44:15.739 --> 00:44:19.617
三，二，一
Three, two, one.

676
00:44:23.705 --> 00:44:24.539
大夥
Uh... Guys?

677
00:44:25.081 --> 00:44:26.875
感覺不對勁
This doesn't feel right.

678
00:44:27.042 --> 00:44:27.876
怎麼了？
What is this?

679
00:44:28.043 --> 00:44:28.877
-怎麼搞的？ -他是誰？
- What's going on? - Who is that?

680
00:44:29.044 --> 00:44:29.878
-等等 -那是史考特嗎？
- Hold on. - Is that Scott?

681
00:44:30.045 --> 00:44:30.920
我是史考特
Yes, it's Scott.

682
00:44:33.798 --> 00:44:36.343
-怎麼了，布魯斯？ -我的背！
- What's going on, Bruce? - Oh, my back!

683
00:44:36.509 --> 00:44:37.469
-怎麼搞的？ -等一下
- What is this? - Hold on a second.

684
00:44:37.635 --> 00:44:38.887
-給我一點空間 -好
Could I get a little space here? Yeah, yeah, yeah.

685
00:44:39.054 --> 00:44:40.930
-你能帶他回來嗎？ -正在想辦法
Can you bring him back? I'm working on it.

686
00:44:47.979 --> 00:44:48.980
一個嬰兒
It's a baby.

687
00:44:49.147 --> 00:44:50.690
-是史考特 -變成嬰兒
- It's Scott. - As a baby.

688
00:44:50.857 --> 00:44:52.233
-他會長大 -帶史考特回來
- He'll grow. - Bring Scott back.

689
00:44:52.400 --> 00:44:53.777
我說關掉就關掉
When I say kill the power, kill the power.

690
00:44:53.943 --> 00:44:55.195
天啊
Oh, my God.

691
00:44:55.904 --> 00:44:57.280
關掉
And... kill it!

692
00:45:01.701 --> 00:45:03.495
有人尿在我褲子上
Somebody peed my pants.

693
00:45:03.661 --> 00:45:04.621
謝天謝地
Oh, thank God.

694
00:45:04.788 --> 00:45:07.999
不知是嬰兒期的我還是老年的我
But I don't know if it was baby me or old me.

695
00:45:11.336 --> 00:45:13.296
或者現在的我
Or just me me.

696
00:45:13.713 --> 00:45:14.923
時間旅行
Time travel!

697
00:45:18.677 --> 00:45:19.678
怎樣？
What?

698
00:45:21.346 --> 00:45:23.598
我覺得非常成功
I see this as an absolute win.

699
00:46:09.269 --> 00:46:10.562
幹嘛苦瓜臉？
Why the long face?

700
00:46:10.729 --> 00:46:12.480
我猜，他變成嬰兒
Let me guess, he turned into a baby.

701
00:46:13.732 --> 00:46:15.734
是有那麼一回事，你來幹嘛？
Among other things, yeah. What are you doing here?

702
00:46:15.900 --> 00:46:17.318
這是EPR弔詭
It's the EPR Paradox.

703
00:46:18.111 --> 00:46:20.155
與其讓朗恩穿越時間，不如…
Instead of pushing Lang through time,

704
00:46:20.321 --> 00:46:21.740
讓時間穿越朗恩
you might've wound up... pushing time through Lang.

705
00:46:21.906 --> 00:46:24.576
那樣困難又危險，該有人警告你們的
It's tricky, dangerous. Somebody could have cautioned you against it.

706
00:46:24.743 --> 00:46:25.702
你警告過了
You did.

707
00:46:25.869 --> 00:46:27.078
是嗎？
Oh, did I?

708
00:46:27.245 --> 00:46:28.913
幸好我來了
Well, thank God I'm here.

709
00:46:29.706 --> 00:46:31.332
反正，我修好了
Regardless, I fixed it.

710
00:46:32.417 --> 00:46:34.711
運作正常的時空GPS
A fully functioning time-space GPS.

711
00:46:36.796 --> 00:46:38.048
我只要和解
I just want peace.

712
00:46:39.674 --> 00:46:42.385
怨恨有害身心，我不喜歡
Turns out resentment is corrosive, and I hate it.

713
00:46:43.261 --> 00:46:44.637
我也是
Me, too.

714
00:46:45.889 --> 00:46:49.351
有機會拿到寶石，但先說我的優先順序
We got a shot at getting these stones, but I gotta tell you my priorities.

715
00:46:49.517 --> 00:46:51.853
我希望救回失去的
Bring back what we lost, I hope, yes.

716
00:46:52.020 --> 00:46:54.856
不計代價留下我發現的
Keep what I found, I have to, at all costs.

717
00:46:56.107 --> 00:46:58.693
但願不必至死方休
And maybe not die trying.

718
00:46:58.860 --> 00:46:59.903
那樣就好
Would be nice.

719
00:47:02.364 --> 00:47:03.448
聽起來可行
Sounds like a deal.

720
00:47:27.055 --> 00:47:28.056
東尼，我不知道
Tony, I don't know.

721
00:47:28.223 --> 00:47:29.849
為什麼？
Why?

722
00:47:30.016 --> 00:47:31.810
他為你做的
He made it for you.

723
00:47:31.976 --> 00:47:35.563
我特地從垃圾堆挖出來，免得摩根當雪橇
Plus, honestly, I have to get it out of the garage before Morgan takes it sledding.

724
00:47:41.111 --> 00:47:42.237
謝謝你，東尼
Thank you, Tony.

725
00:47:43.238 --> 00:47:44.781
可以別聲張嗎？
Will you keep that a little quiet?

726
00:47:45.490 --> 00:47:46.866
不是每個人都有
Didn't bring one for the whole team.

727
00:47:48.618 --> 00:47:51.913
我們會集結整個團隊吧？
We are getting the whole team, yeah?

728
00:47:52.080 --> 00:47:53.832
正在努力
We're working on that right now.

729
00:48:11.933 --> 00:48:12.976
人類哥
Hey, Humie.

730
00:48:13.518 --> 00:48:15.311
綠巨人呢？
Where's Big Green?

731
00:48:15.645 --> 00:48:17.689
在廚房吧
The kitchen, I think.

732
00:48:18.940 --> 00:48:20.150
帥呆了
That's awesome.

733
00:48:21.359 --> 00:48:23.445
羅德，重新進入時小心
Rhodey, careful on re-entry.

734
00:48:23.611 --> 00:48:25.321
降落區有個白癡
There's an idiot in the landing zone.

735
00:48:26.489 --> 00:48:27.615
天啊
Oh, God.

736
00:48:28.199 --> 00:48:30.243
你好，正常尺寸蟻人
What's up, Regular-Sized Man?

737
00:48:59.981 --> 00:49:03.985
（歡迎蒞臨新阿斯嘉，請慢速行駛）

738
00:49:21.086 --> 00:49:25.423
這比黃金宮殿和魔力神鎚掉漆多了
Kind of a step down from the golden palaces and the magic hammers and what not.

739
00:49:25.507 --> 00:49:26.883
有點同情心
Hey, have a little compassion, pal.

740
00:49:27.050 --> 00:49:29.010
他們先失去阿斯嘉，又少了一半人口
First, they lost Asgard, then half their people.

741
00:49:29.177 --> 00:49:30.720
有個家就偷笑了
They're probably just happy to have a home.

742
00:49:30.887 --> 00:49:32.597
你們不該來的
You shouldn't have come.

743
00:49:32.683 --> 00:49:35.684
瓦爾基麗
Ah! Valkyrie!

744
00:49:35.850 --> 00:49:38.561
真高興見到妳，憤怒姊
Great to see you, angry girl!

745
00:49:38.728 --> 00:49:40.939
我比較喜歡你原來那兩個版本
I think I liked you better either of the other ways.

746
00:49:42.190 --> 00:49:43.983
-這是火箭 -妳好嗎？
This is Rocket. How ya doing?

747
00:49:46.403 --> 00:49:47.404
他不會見你們的
He won't see you.

748
00:49:47.737 --> 00:49:48.780
那麼慘？
It's that bad, huh?

749
00:49:48.947 --> 00:49:51.658
我們一個月只見他一次…他來補貨時
We only see him once a month

750
00:49:51.825 --> 00:49:53.576
（阿斯嘉麥芽啤酒，黑啤酒）
when he comes in for "supplies."

751
00:49:54.661 --> 00:49:55.787
慘到爆
It's that bad.

752
00:49:55.954 --> 00:49:56.955
是啊
Yeah.

753
00:50:09.467 --> 00:50:10.510
怎麼…
What the...?

754
00:50:13.972 --> 00:50:15.640
有東西死在裡面
Whew! Something died in here!

755
00:50:16.725 --> 00:50:18.977
哈囉？索爾
Hello? Thor!

756
00:50:19.519 --> 00:50:21.187
你是來修第四台嗎？
Are you here about the cable?

757
00:50:21.938 --> 00:50:24.024
電影台兩週前就不能看
The Cinemax went out two weeks ago...

758
00:50:24.607 --> 00:50:27.360
體育台有雜訊
and the sports are all kinda fuzzy and whatnot.

759
00:50:28.111 --> 00:50:29.112
索爾？
Thor?

760
00:50:37.037 --> 00:50:39.622
兄弟們，歐買尬！
Boys! Oh, my God!

761
00:50:40.248 --> 00:50:43.001
見到你們真好
Oh, my God, it's so good to see you!

762
00:50:44.461 --> 00:50:45.754
過來抱抱，小痞子
Come here, cuddly little rascal.

763
00:50:45.920 --> 00:50:47.505
我很好…
Yeah, no, I'm good. I'm good.

764
00:50:48.548 --> 00:50:49.632
沒必要這樣
That's not necessary.

765
00:50:50.091 --> 00:50:52.761
浩克，認識我朋友米克和寇格吧？
Hulk, you know my friends Miek and Korg, right?

766
00:50:52.927 --> 00:50:54.054
-你們好 -嗨
- Hey, boys! - Hey, guys.

767
00:50:54.220 --> 00:50:55.472
好久不見
Long time no see.

768
00:50:55.638 --> 00:50:57.891
桶子裡有啤酒，無線網路儘管用
Beer's in the bucket. Feel free to log on to the Wi-Fi.

769
00:50:58.058 --> 00:50:59.768
不用密碼
No password, obviously.

770
00:51:00.852 --> 00:51:02.354
索爾，他回來了
Thor, he's back.

771
00:51:02.520 --> 00:51:05.190
電視上那小子又叫我豬頭
That kid on the TV just called me a dickhead again.

772
00:51:05.732 --> 00:51:06.775
菜鳥大師
Noobmaster.

773
