菜鳥大師69叫我豬頭
Yeah, NoobMaster69 called me a dickhead.

774
00:51:09.569 --> 00:51:10.737
你好遜
I am sick of this.

775
00:51:11.654 --> 00:51:14.574
菜鳥大師，又是我，雷神索爾
Noobmaster, hey, it's Thor again. You know, the God of Thunder.

776
00:51:14.741 --> 00:51:16.910
聽好，你要是不馬上登出這遊戲
Listen, bud, if you don't log off this game immediately...

777
00:51:17.077 --> 00:51:20.205
我就飛去你家，闖進你躲的地下室
I am gonna fly over to your house, come down to that basement you're hiding in...

778
00:51:20.372 --> 00:51:22.999
扯斷你手臂，再塞進你屁眼
rip off your arms, and shove them up your butt!

779
00:51:23.375 --> 00:51:26.419
沒錯，哭給你老北聽，賤胚
Oh, that's right, yes! Go cry to your father, you little weasel.

780
00:51:27.128 --> 00:51:28.129
謝謝你，索爾
Thank you, Thor.

781
00:51:28.296 --> 00:51:29.631
他再煩你就告訴我
Let me know if he bothers you again, okay?

782
00:51:29.798 --> 00:51:31.007
感恩，我會的
Thank you very much. I will.

783
00:51:31.800 --> 00:51:33.301
你們想喝什麼嗎？
So, you guys want a drink? What are we drinking?

784
00:51:33.468 --> 00:51:35.887
我有啤酒、龍舌蘭，應有盡有
I've got beer, tequila, all sorts of things.

785
00:51:38.765 --> 00:51:40.183
兄弟
Buddy.

786
00:51:40.350 --> 00:51:41.309
你還好嗎？
- You all right?

787
00:51:41.476 --> 00:51:42.811
我很好，怎樣？
- Yes, I'm fine. Why?

788
00:51:42.977 --> 00:51:44.020
我看起來不好嗎？
Why, don't I look all right?

789
00:51:44.437 --> 00:51:45.855
你活像彌勒佛
You look like melted ice cream.

790
00:51:47.857 --> 00:51:49.943
怎樣？過來聊天打屁嗎？
So, what's up? You just here for a hang, or what?

791
00:51:50.110 --> 00:51:51.403
我們需要你幫忙
- We need your help. - Mm.

792
00:51:52.320 --> 00:51:54.614
我們有機會逆轉局勢
There might be a chance we could fix everything.

793
00:51:54.781 --> 00:51:56.116
修第四台嗎？
What, like the cable?

794
00:51:56.282 --> 00:51:58.493
它害我抓狂好幾星期了
'Cause that's been driving me bananas for weeks.

795
00:51:58.660 --> 00:51:59.661
薩諾斯
Like Thanos.

796
00:52:18.847 --> 00:52:21.683
別提起這名字
Don't say that name.

797
00:52:22.851 --> 00:52:25.520
這裡不准說到那個髒東西
Um, yeah, we don't actually say that name in here.

798
00:52:30.358 --> 00:52:32.235
請把手拿開
Please take your hand off me.

799
00:52:35.655 --> 00:52:38.700
我知道那個傢伙…
Now, I know that guy...

800
00:52:39.617 --> 00:52:40.744
可能嚇到你
might scare you.

801
00:52:40.910 --> 00:52:42.287
怎麼會？
Why would I be...?

802
00:52:42.454 --> 00:52:45.623
我怎麼會被那傢伙嚇到？
Why would I be scared of that guy?

803
00:52:45.790 --> 00:52:47.625
那傢伙是我殺的，記得嗎？
I'm the one who killed that guy, remember?

804
00:52:48.960 --> 00:52:50.837
這裡有別人殺了他嗎？
Hmm. Anyone else here kill that guy?

805
00:52:54.257 --> 00:52:55.342
沒有
Nope.

806
00:52:55.884 --> 00:52:56.885
應該沒有
Didn't think so.

807
00:52:57.969 --> 00:53:02.223
寇格，告訴大家誰砍掉薩諾斯的頭？
Korg, why don't you, uh, tell everybody who chopped Thanos' big head off?

808
00:53:02.766 --> 00:53:03.808
風暴破壞者？
Um, Stormbreaker?

809
00:53:03.975 --> 00:53:05.602
誰揮舞風暴破壞者？
Who was swinging Stormbreaker?

810
00:53:09.689 --> 00:53:11.900
我瞭解，你很不好受
I get it. You're in a rough spot, okay?

811
00:53:12.067 --> 00:53:13.068
我感同身受
I've been there myself.

812
00:53:13.234 --> 00:53:15.528
想知道誰幫我走出來嗎？
And you want to know who helped me out of it?

813
00:53:15.695 --> 00:53:18.031
是娜塔莎嗎？
Was it Natasha?

814
00:53:18.490 --> 00:53:20.367
是你
It was you.

815
00:53:20.533 --> 00:53:22.494
你幫助我
You helped me.

816
00:53:23.703 --> 00:53:25.163
你怎麼不問問…
So, why don't you ask...

817
00:53:26.247 --> 00:53:28.583
下面那些阿斯嘉人
the Asgardians down there...

818
00:53:28.750 --> 00:53:30.460
我的幫助值多少？
how much my help is worth?

819
00:53:36.132 --> 00:53:37.592
剩下的那些人
The ones that are left, anyway.

820
00:53:38.134 --> 00:53:39.719
我想我們能救他們回來
I think we could bring them back.

821
00:53:40.637 --> 00:53:41.638
別講了
Stop.

822
00:53:42.764 --> 00:53:43.848
別講了好嗎？
Stop, okay?

823
00:53:44.599 --> 00:53:47.519
你以為我在這裡自艾自憐
I know you think I'm down here wallowing in my own self-pity...

824
00:53:47.686 --> 00:53:50.230
等著被人拯救
waiting to be rescued and saved...

825
00:53:50.397 --> 00:53:52.482
我很好，我們很好，對不對？
but I'm fine, okay. We're fine, aren't we?

826
00:53:52.649 --> 00:53:54.109
我們在這裡好得很
Oh, we're good here, mate.

827
00:53:54.275 --> 00:53:56.236
不管你有什麼提議，我們沒興趣
So, whatever it is that you're offering, we're not into it.

828
00:53:56.403 --> 00:53:57.904
完全不在乎
Don't care. Couldn't care less.

829
00:53:58.071 --> 00:53:59.155
再見
Goodbye.

830
00:54:02.534 --> 00:54:04.244
我們需要你
We need you, pal.

831
00:54:13.670 --> 00:54:15.672
船上有啤酒
There's beer on the ship.

832
00:54:19.718 --> 00:54:21.344
哪一種？
What kind?

833
00:54:25.265 --> 00:54:27.892
（東京）

834
00:54:33.440 --> 00:54:36.443
是他！他在追殺昭彥

835
00:55:03.178 --> 00:55:05.347
你為什麼這麼做？

836
00:55:06.973 --> 00:55:08.641
我們從來沒招惹過你

837
00:55:09.059 --> 00:55:10.268
你們活了下來

838
00:55:10.560 --> 00:55:12.395
地球一半生物卻沒有

839
00:55:12.896 --> 00:55:14.314
他們碰上薩諾斯

840
00:55:14.898 --> 00:55:15.899
你們碰上我

841
00:55:21.154 --> 00:55:23.198
你們不能再傷人了

842
00:55:24.282 --> 00:55:26.368
我們傷人？

843
00:55:29.954 --> 00:55:30.830
你瘋了

844
00:56:01.111 --> 00:56:02.112
等等，救我！

845
00:56:03.530 --> 00:56:05.073
我什麼都能給你

846
00:56:06.324 --> 00:56:07.450
你要什麼？

847
00:56:07.617 --> 00:56:10.704
我要的，你沒辦法給
What I want you can't give me.

848
00:56:34.602 --> 00:56:35.770
妳不該來這裡
You shouldn't be here.

849
00:56:38.481 --> 00:56:40.233
你也不應該
Neither should you.

850
00:56:46.239 --> 00:56:47.699
我有任務在身
I've got a job to do.

851
00:56:49.284 --> 00:56:50.910
這就是你的任務嗎？
Is that what you're calling this?

852
00:56:51.995 --> 00:56:54.414
殺死這些人也不能讓你家人回來
Killing all these people isn't gonna bring your family back.

853
00:57:00.253 --> 00:57:01.338
我們有所發現
We found something.

854
00:57:03.006 --> 00:57:05.175
說不定是個機會
A chance, maybe.

855
00:57:08.511 --> 00:57:09.721
不要
Don't.

856
00:57:10.638 --> 00:57:12.098
不要什麼？
Don't what?

857
00:57:15.143 --> 00:57:16.603
不要給我希望
Don't give me hope.

858
00:57:19.939 --> 00:57:22.400
抱歉我不能早點給你
I'm sorry I couldn't give it to you sooner.

859
00:57:43.963 --> 00:57:45.256
你往左偏了
You're drifting left.

860
00:57:45.840 --> 00:57:47.550
直走，酒鬼
One side there, Lebowski.

861
00:57:50.762 --> 00:57:52.055
火焰，你好嗎？
Ratchet, how's it going?

862
00:57:52.222 --> 00:57:53.223
是火箭
It's Rocket.

863
00:57:53.390 --> 00:57:55.934
放輕鬆，你只在地球上是天才
Take it easy. You're only a genius on Earth, pal.

864
00:58:00.855 --> 00:58:02.440
時間旅行裝，不錯嘛
Time travel suit, not bad.

865
00:58:03.900 --> 00:58:05.318
喂…輕一點…
Hey, hey, hey! Easy! Easy!

866
00:58:05.485 --> 00:58:06.486
我非常小心
I'm being very careful.

867
00:58:06.653 --> 00:58:08.071
才怪，你非常浩克
No, you're being very Hulky.

868
00:58:08.238 --> 00:58:09.155
我非常小心
I'm being careful.

869
00:58:09.322 --> 00:58:10.699
這些是皮姆粒子
These are Pym Particles, all right?

870
00:58:10.865 --> 00:58:13.368
自從漢克皮姆消失後，只剩這個
And ever since Hank Pym got snapped out of existence, this is it.

871
00:58:13.535 --> 00:58:15.286
我們只有這個，再也做不出來了
This is what we have. We're not making any more.

872
00:58:15.453 --> 00:58:17.372
-史考特，冷靜點 -抱歉
- Scott, calm down. - Sorry.

873
00:58:17.706 --> 00:58:20.667
我們只夠一趟來回
We've got enough for one round-trip each. That's it.

874
00:58:20.834 --> 00:58:21.876
不能重來
No do-overs.

875
00:58:22.919 --> 00:58:24.254
再加兩次測試
Plus two test runs.

876
00:58:28.425 --> 00:58:29.259
一次測試
One test run.

877
00:58:30.593 --> 00:58:32.178
好，我還沒準備好
All right. I'm not ready for this.

878
00:58:32.345 --> 00:58:33.638
我可以試試
I'm game.

879
00:58:35.849 --> 00:58:37.600
讓我來
I'll do it.

880
00:58:38.226 --> 00:58:41.229
克林特，你會因時間轉移而感到混亂
Clint, now you're gonna feel a little discombobulated from the chronoshift.

881
00:58:41.396 --> 00:58:43.273
-別擔心 -等等，我先問一件事
Don't worry about that. Wait a second. Let me ask you something.

882
00:58:43.440 --> 00:58:45.066
如果我們能回到過去
If we can do this, you know...

883
00:58:45.233 --> 00:58:47.569
何不乾脆去找薩諾斯寶寶？
go back in time, why don't we just find baby Thanos?

884
00:58:47.736 --> 00:58:48.903
就是…
You know, and...

885
00:58:52.907 --> 00:58:54.784
-首先，那樣很恐怖 -他是薩諾斯啊
First of all, that's horrible. It's Thanos.

886
00:58:54.951 --> 00:58:57.245
第二，時間不是那樣運作的
And secondly, time doesn't work that way.

887
00:58:57.412 --> 00:58:59.581
改變時間不會改變未來
Changing the past doesn't change the future.

888
00:58:59.748 --> 00:59:02.459
我們回去，比薩諾斯先拿到寶石
Look, we go back, we get the stones before Thanos gets them...

889
00:59:02.625 --> 00:59:05.378
薩諾斯沒有寶石，問題解決
Thanos doesn't have the stones. Problem solved.

890
00:59:05.545 --> 00:59:07.380
-沒錯 -不是那樣子
- Bingo. - That's not how it works.

891
00:59:07.547 --> 00:59:09.674
-我聽到的是 -誰，誰告訴你的？
Well, that's what I heard. Wait, but who? Who told you that?

892
00:59:09.841 --> 00:59:11.634
"星際爭霸戰"、"魔鬼終結者"、"時空特警"
Star Trek, Terminator, Timecop...

893
00:59:11.801 --> 00:59:13.386
-"兩世奇人" -"時空怪客"
- Time After Time. - Quantum Leap.

894
00:59:13.553 --> 00:59:15.597
-"時間的皺摺"、"似曾相識" -"扭轉時光機"
Wrinkle in Time, Somewhere in Time.

895
00:59:15.764 --> 00:59:18.141
"扭轉時光機"﹑"阿比阿弟的冒險"
Hot Tub Time Machine. Hot Tub Time Machine.

896
00:59:18.308 --> 00:59:20.393
就是任何講時間旅行的電影
Bill and Ted's Excellent Adventure. Basically, any movie that deals with time travel.

897
00:59:20.560 --> 00:59:22.395
"終極警探"…那部不是
Die Hard. No, that's not one.

898
00:59:22.562 --> 00:59:23.605
這是常識
This is known.

899
00:59:23.772 --> 00:59:26.024
我不知道為何大家都信，那不正確
I don't know why everyone believes that, but that isn't true.

900
00:59:26.191 --> 00:59:28.193
想想看，如果旅行到過去
Think about it. If you travel to the past...

901
00:59:28.360 --> 00:59:30.695
那個過去就成了你的未來
that past becomes your future...

902
00:59:30.862 --> 00:59:33.823
你以前的現在就成為過去
and your former present becomes the past...

903
00:59:33.990 --> 00:59:36.618
無法被新的未來改變
which can't now be changed by your new future.

904
00:59:36.785 --> 00:59:37.994
沒錯
Exactly.

905
00:59:38.578 --> 00:59:41.456
所以"回到未來"都在鬼扯？
So Back to the Future is a bunch of bullshit?

906
00:59:45.377 --> 00:59:46.795
好，克林特
All right, Clint.

907
00:59:47.462 --> 00:59:50.507
倒數三，二…
We're going in three, two...

908
00:59:50.674 --> 00:59:51.675
一
one.

909
00:59:59.057 --> 01:00:01.434
（量子目標）

910
01:01:04.039 --> 01:01:05.373
庫柏
Cooper?

911
01:01:05.540 --> 01:01:07.083
我的耳機呢？
Where are my headphones?

912
01:01:07.250 --> 01:01:08.168
萊拉？
Lila?

913
01:01:08.335 --> 01:01:10.420
-我沒拿 -萊拉？
- I never had them. - Lila?

914
01:01:11.254 --> 01:01:13.173
你昨天拿去了
Yeah, you had them yesterday!

915
01:01:13.757 --> 01:01:15.050
萊拉…
Lila! Lila!

916
01:01:20.555 --> 01:01:21.556
爸？
Yeah, Dad?

917
01:01:25.435 --> 01:01:26.478
爸？
Dad?

918
01:01:28.980 --> 01:01:30.273
萊拉
Lila!

919
01:01:36.196 --> 01:01:38.531
嘿…看著我
Hey. Hey, look at me.

920
01:01:38.698 --> 01:01:39.824
你還好嗎？
You okay?

921
01:01:40.533 --> 01:01:42.577
還好
Yeah. Yeah.

922
01:01:44.496 --> 01:01:45.663
成功了
It worked.

923
01:01:47.415 --> 01:01:48.792
成功了
It worked.

924
01:01:48.958 --> 01:01:50.085
（時間攔劫，腦力激盪時間）

925
01:01:50.585 --> 01:01:51.753
（宇宙魔方，空間寶石）

926
01:01:51.920 --> 01:01:53.755
所以方法可行
Okay, so the how works.

927
01:01:54.422 --> 01:01:57.467
現在要找出時間和地點
Now, we gotta figure out the when and the where.

928
01:01:58.301 --> 01:02:00.095
在場幾乎每個人都曾經…
Almost everyone in this room has had an encounter...

929
01:02:00.261 --> 01:02:01.930
與至少一顆無限寶石交手過
with at least one of the six Infinity Stones.

930
01:02:02.097 --> 01:02:03.598
也可以把交手二字
Or substitute the word "encounter"...

931
01:02:03.765 --> 01:02:06.351
改成差點被無限寶石殺死
for "damn near been killed" by one of the six Infinity Stones.

932
01:02:06.518 --> 01:02:07.686
我沒有
Well, I haven't...

933
01:02:07.852 --> 01:02:10.188
我根本不知道你們在說什麼
but I don't even know what the hell you're all talking about.

934
01:02:10.355 --> 01:02:15.110
無論如何，皮姆粒子只夠一趟來回使用
Regardless, we only have enough Pym Particles for one round-trip each.

935
01:02:15.276 --> 01:02:18.488
這些寶石在歷史上許多地方出現過
And these stones have been in a lot of different places throughout history.

936
01:02:18.655 --> 01:02:19.948
我們的歷史
Our history.

937
01:02:20.115 --> 01:02:23.118
容易前往的時間點並不多
So, not a lot of convenient spots to just drop in, yeah?

938
01:02:23.284 --> 01:02:25.078
所以我們必須挑選目標
Which means we have to pick our targets.

939
01:02:25.537 --> 01:02:26.788
正確
Correct.

940
01:02:28.164 --> 01:02:29.749
那就從以太寶石開始
So, let's start with the Aether.

941
01:02:29.916 --> 01:02:31.126
索爾，你知道什麼？
Thor, what do you know?

942
01:02:36.715 --> 01:02:37.924
他在睡覺嗎？
Is he asleep?

943
01:02:38.091 --> 01:02:40.635
不，我確定他死了
No, no. I'm pretty sure he's dead.

944
01:02:41.177 --> 01:02:43.638
（目標：現實寶石）

945
01:02:44.055 --> 01:02:45.265
從哪裡開始講？
Uh, where to start? Um...

946
01:02:47.058 --> 01:02:49.602
首先，以太寶石不是寶石
The Aether, firstly, is not a stone.

947
01:02:50.061 --> 01:02:51.896
以前有人叫它寶石
Someone called it a stone before.

948
01:02:53.648 --> 01:02:57.277
它應該是一坨憤怒的爛泥
Um, it's more of an angry sludge sort of a thing...

949
01:02:57.444 --> 01:03:00.321
有人必須更正，別再那樣說
so someone's gonna need to amend that and stop saying that.

950
01:03:00.780 --> 01:03:03.324
不過以太有個有趣的故事…
Here's an interesting story, though, about the Aether.

951
01:03:03.491 --> 01:03:05.368
多年前，我祖父…
My grandfather, many years ago...

952
01:03:05.535 --> 01:03:09.039
不得不藏起寶石，避開黑暗精靈
had to hide the stone from the Dark Elves.

953
01:03:10.957 --> 01:03:11.916
他們很恐怖
Ooh. Scary beings.

954
01:03:12.083 --> 01:03:13.793
珍其實…
So, Jane, actually...

955
01:03:14.377 --> 01:03:15.920
她在這裡
Oh, there she is.

956
01:03:16.379 --> 01:03:19.758
珍是我的舊情人
Yeah, so Jane was an old flame of mine.

957
01:03:20.925 --> 01:03:23.970
有一次她的手卡在石頭裡
You know, she stuck her hand inside a rock this one time...

958
01:03:24.137 --> 01:03:26.973
後來以太寶石卡在她體內
and then the Aether stuck itself inside her...

959
01:03:27.390 --> 01:03:29.184
她就病得非常嚴重
and she became very, very sick.

960
01:03:29.351 --> 01:03:32.479
我不得不帶她去阿斯嘉，我老家
And so I had to take her to Asgard, which is where I'm from...

961
01:03:32.645 --> 01:03:34.606
想辦法治療她
and we had to try and fix her.

962
01:03:34.773 --> 01:03:36.399
當時我們在交往
We were dating at the time, you see...

963
01:03:36.566 --> 01:03:39.944
我介紹她給我母親
and I got to introduce her to my mother...

964
01:03:41.488 --> 01:03:43.323
我媽死了…
who's dead and, um...

965
01:03:44.741 --> 01:03:48.286
珍和我已經分手了
Oh, you know, Jane and I aren't even dating anymore, so...

966
01:03:49.079 --> 01:03:50.538
男女分分合合
Yes, these things happen, though. You know?

967
01:03:50.705 --> 01:03:52.040
沒什麼永恆，唯一…
Nothing lasts forever. The only thing that...

968
01:03:52.207 --> 01:03:53.958
-過來坐下吧 -我還沒講完
- Why don't you come sit down? - I'm not done yet.

969
01:03:54.125 --> 01:03:57.170
人生唯一恆久的東西就是無常
The only thing that is permanent in life is impermanence.

970
01:03:57.921 --> 01:04:00.215
棒呆了，想吃蛋嗎？早餐？
Awesome. Eggs? Breakfast?

971
01:04:00.382 --> 01:04:02.425
不，我要一杯血腥瑪莉
No. I'd like a Bloody Mary.

972
01:04:02.592 --> 01:04:04.719
奎爾說他從莫拉格偷走力量寶石
Quill said he stole the Power Stone from Morag.

973
01:04:04.886 --> 01:04:05.970
（目標：力量寶石）

974
01:04:06.137 --> 01:04:08.515
-那是一個人嗎？ -不，莫拉格是星球
- Is that a person? - No, Morag's a planet.

975
01:04:09.224 --> 01:04:10.600
奎爾才是人
Quill was a person.

976
01:04:11.351 --> 01:04:13.687
星球？在外太空？
Like a planet? Like in outer space?

977
01:04:13.853 --> 01:04:18.066
看，好像一隻開心的小狗狗
Oh, look. It's like a little puppy, all happy and everything.

978
01:04:18.233 --> 01:04:21.403
想上太空嗎？想上太空嗎，小狗狗？
Do you wanna go to space? You wanna go to space, puppy?

979
01:04:21.569 --> 01:04:22.696
我帶你上太空
I'll take you to space.

980
01:04:22.862 --> 01:04:23.905
（目標：靈魂寶石）

981
01:04:24.072 --> 01:04:25.990
薩諾斯在佛米爾發現靈魂寶石
Thanos found the Soul Stone on Vormir.

982
01:04:26.157 --> 01:04:28.118
佛米爾是什麼？
What is Vormir?

983
01:04:28.284 --> 01:04:29.452
死亡之地
A dominion of death...

984
01:04:30.161 --> 01:04:32.038
位於宇宙的中心
at the very center of celestial existence.

985
01:04:33.957 --> 01:04:37.961
薩諾斯謀殺我姊的地方
It's where Thanos murdered my sister.

986
01:04:44.384 --> 01:04:45.427
我不去
Not it.

987
01:04:46.845 --> 01:04:48.805
（目標：時間寶石）
-時間寶石男 -奇異博士
- That Time Stone guy. - Doctor Strange.

988
01:04:48.972 --> 01:04:50.765
他是哪種博士？
Yeah, what kind of doctor was he?

989
01:04:50.932 --> 01:04:52.892
耳鼻喉科醫生兼魔術師
Ear-nose-throat meets rabbit-from-hat.

990
01:04:53.059 --> 01:04:54.352
他在格林威治村的家挺漂亮的
Nice place in the Village, though.

991
01:04:54.519 --> 01:04:56.104
在蘇利文街？
Yeah, on Sullivan Street?

992
01:04:56.271 --> 01:04:57.272
布利克街
Mm... Bleecker Street.

993
01:04:57.439 --> 01:04:58.523
他住紐約？
Wait, he lived in New York?

994
01:04:59.190 --> 01:05:01.234
-不，多倫多 -布利克和蘇利文街口
No, he lived in Toronto. Uh, yeah, on Bleecker and Sullivan.

995
01:05:01.401 --> 01:05:03.194
-妳有認真聽嗎？ -各位
Have you been listening to anything? Guys.

996
01:05:03.361 --> 01:05:06.906
如果挑對年份，紐約會有三顆寶石
If you pick the right year, there are three stones in New York.

997
01:05:09.367 --> 01:05:11.077
真的假的
Shut the front door.

998
01:05:11.244 --> 01:05:13.663
（紐約，阿斯嘉，莫拉格／佛米爾）

999
01:05:13.830 --> 01:05:15.957
好，計畫成形
All right. We have a plan.

1000
01:05:16.124 --> 01:05:20.712
六顆寶石，三個團隊，一次機會
Six stones, three teams, one shot.

1001
01:05:30.430 --> 01:05:32.307
五年前我們輸了
Five years ago, we lost.

1002
01:05:33.641 --> 01:05:34.934
一敗塗地
All of us.

1003
01:05:36.853 --> 01:05:38.229
我們失去朋友
We lost friends.

1004
01:05:38.938 --> 01:05:40.607
失去家人
We lost family.

1005
01:05:42.567 --> 01:05:44.402
失去部分的自我
We lost a part of ourselves.

1006
01:05:45.862 --> 01:05:48.198
如今我們有機會扭轉乾坤
Today, we have a chance to take it all back.

1007
01:05:49.616 --> 01:05:52.452
你們知道自己的團隊和任務
You know your teams. You know your missions.

1008
01:05:53.286 --> 01:05:55.205
奪回寶石，救他們回來
Get the stones. Get them back.

1009
01:05:56.039 --> 01:05:57.207
來回一趟
One round-trip each.

1010
01:05:57.374 --> 01:05:58.458
不准出錯
No mistakes...

1011
01:05:58.958 --> 01:06:00.669
不能重來
no do-overs.

1012
01:06:00.835 --> 01:06:02.712
我們大多會去我們熟悉的地方
Most of us are going somewhere we know.

1013
01:06:02.879 --> 01:06:04.714
那不表示我們能預測會遇到什麼
That doesn't mean we should know what to expect.

1014
01:06:05.882 --> 01:06:06.883
萬事小心
Be careful.

1015
01:06:07.550 --> 01:06:08.802
彼此照應
Look out for each other.

1016
01:06:10.261 --> 01:06:12.055
這是我們畢生最大的戰役
This is the fight of our lives...

1017
01:06:12.931 --> 01:06:14.516
只許成功
and we're gonna win.

1018
01:06:16.685 --> 01:06:17.686
不計代價
Whatever it takes.

1019
01:06:20.939 --> 01:06:22.399
祝好運
Good luck.

1020
01:06:22.565 --> 01:06:23.650
他挺會講的
He's pretty good at that.

1021
01:06:23.817 --> 01:06:24.984
-對啊 -好
- Right? - All right.

1022
01:06:25.151 --> 01:06:27.487
你們聽到了，開始輸入，綠巨人
You heard the man. Stroke those keys, Jolly Green.

1023
01:06:28.446 --> 01:06:29.989
追蹤器就緒
Trackers engaged.

1024
01:06:30.782 --> 01:06:32.617
你保證把它完整帶回來？
You promise to bring that back in one piece, right?

1025
01:06:32.784 --> 01:06:34.119
對啦…
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

1026
01:06:34.285 --> 01:06:36.162
好，我會盡力
Okay, I'll do my best.

1027
01:06:36.329 --> 01:06:38.123
這種保證真沒說服力
As promises go, that was pretty lame.

1028
01:06:41.209 --> 01:06:42.335
待會見
See ya in a minute.

1029
01:07:12.115 --> 01:07:15.201
（紐約，2012年）

1030
01:07:36.765 --> 01:07:38.058
我們各有任務在身
All right, we all have our assignments.

1031
01:07:38.224 --> 01:07:40.435
兩顆寶石在上城，一顆在下城
Two stones uptown, one stone down.

1032
01:07:40.602 --> 01:07:42.562
保持低調，注意時間
Stay low. Keep an eye on the clock.

1033
01:07:57.994 --> 01:07:59.788
也許過程中砸爛幾樣東西
Maybe smash a few things along the way.

1034
01:08:00.914 --> 01:08:02.916
我覺得太超過，不過隨便啦
I think it's gratuitous, but whatever.

1035
01:08:30.652 --> 01:08:33.822
走那邊要小心，地板剛打過蠟
I'd be careful going that way. We just had the floors waxed.

1036
01:08:39.160 --> 01:08:40.787
我找奇異博士
Yeah, I'm looking for Doctor Strange.

1037
01:08:42.372 --> 01:08:45.250
你早來了五年
You're about five years too early.

1038
01:08:46.042 --> 01:08:49.754
史蒂芬史傳奇正在20條街以外開刀
Stephen Strange is currently performing surgery about 20 blocks that way.

1039
01:08:51.548 --> 01:08:52.549
找他有什麼事？
What do you want from him?

1040
01:08:53.466 --> 01:08:54.467
要那個東西
That, actually.

1041
01:08:57.846 --> 01:08:58.680
恐怕不行
Ah! I'm afraid not.

1042
01:08:59.097 --> 01:09:00.473
抱歉，我不是在問妳
Sorry, but I wasn't asking.

1043
01:09:01.391 --> 01:09:02.392
最好別這麼做
You don't want to do this.

1044
01:09:02.559 --> 01:09:04.144
對，但我需要那寶石
Ah, you're right, I don't. But I need that stone...

1045
01:09:04.310 --> 01:09:05.812
沒時間跟妳辯
and I don't have time to debate it.

1046
01:09:14.821 --> 01:09:16.406
我們重新來過吧？
Let's start over, shall we?

1047
01:09:19.409 --> 01:09:21.578
（阿斯嘉，2013年）

1048
01:09:27.959 --> 01:09:29.461
給妳的，珍夫人
For you, Lady Jane.

1049
01:09:29.627 --> 01:09:32.005
你們有搭長褲的嗎？
Um, so you have anything with pants?

1050
01:09:32.172 --> 01:09:33.214
長褲？
Pants?

1051
01:09:33.381 --> 01:09:35.467
算了，這件可以，謝謝
Never mind. These will be fine. Thank you.

1052
01:09:35.633 --> 01:09:37.260
-是，夫人 -那是珍
- Yes, milady. - Oh, there's Jane.

1053
01:09:38.887 --> 01:09:39.888
好
All right.

1054
01:09:41.473 --> 01:09:42.724
這樣吧，肥仔
Here's the deal, tubby.

1055
01:09:42.891 --> 01:09:45.268
你去引誘她，我用這個捅她
You're gonna charm her, and I'm gonna poke her with this thing...

1056
01:09:45.435 --> 01:09:47.896
搶走現實寶石就閃人
and extract the Reality Stone, and get gone lickety-split.

1057
01:09:49.647 --> 01:09:52.609
我馬上回來，酒窖就在下面
I'll be right back, okay? The wine cellar is just down here.

1058
01:09:52.776 --> 01:09:55.653
家父以前有一大桶阿孔麥芽啤酒
My father used to have this huge barrel of Aakonian ale.

1059
01:09:55.820 --> 01:09:57.072
我去廚房找外帶杯
I'll see if the scullery has a couple of to-go cups.

1060
01:09:57.238 --> 01:09:59.115
喂！你喝得不夠茫嗎？
Hey. Hey! Aren't you drunk enough already?

1061
01:10:06.498 --> 01:10:08.416
-請妳送湯給洛基 -是，夫人
If you could send Loki some soup. Yes, milady.

1062
01:10:08.583 --> 01:10:12.587
請圖書館員拿些天文學的書
And ask our librarians to pull some volumes from the astronomy shelf.

1063
01:10:18.760 --> 01:10:20.303
那個美魔女是誰？
Who's the fancy broad?

1064
01:10:21.638 --> 01:10:23.139
那是我母親
That's my mother.

1065
01:10:23.640 --> 01:10:25.350
她今天去世
She dies today.

1066
01:10:26.017 --> 01:10:27.811
那是今天？
Oh, that is today?

1067
01:10:34.359 --> 01:10:36.903
我做不到…
I can't do this. I can't do this.

1068
01:10:37.487 --> 01:10:39.030
我不該在這裡，我不該來
I shouldn't be here. I shouldn't have come.

1069
01:10:39.197 --> 01:10:40.323
這是個餿主意
It's a bad idea!

1070
01:10:40.615 --> 01:10:41.658
-過來 -不…
- Come here. - No, no, no.

1071
01:10:41.825 --> 01:10:44.244
我恐慌發作了
I think I'm having a panic attack.

1072
01:10:44.411 --> 01:10:46.413
-過來這裡 -我不該來的，這樣不對
Come here. Right here. I shouldn't be here. This is bad.

1073
01:10:47.205 --> 01:10:48.832
難道只有你失去親友嗎？
You think you're the only one who lost people?

1074
01:10:48.998 --> 01:10:50.834
你以為我們在這裡做什麼？
What do you think we're doing here?

1075
01:10:51.001 --> 01:10:53.169
我失去我僅有的家人
I lost the only family I ever had.

1076
01:10:53.336 --> 01:10:55.755
奎爾、格魯特、德克斯、長觸角的妞
Quill, Groot, Drax, the chick with the antenna...

1077
01:10:55.922 --> 01:10:57.340
全都消失了
all gone.

1078
01:10:58.049 --> 01:10:59.384
我知道你想你媽
I get you miss your mom...

1079
01:10:59.676 --> 01:11:00.885
可是她走了
but she's gone.

1080
01:11:01.052 --> 01:11:02.053
真的走了
Really gone.

1081
01:11:02.637 --> 01:11:05.473
有很多人只是消失
And there are plenty of people who are only kind of gone...

1082
01:11:05.640 --> 01:11:06.766
你能救他們
and you can help them.

1083
01:11:07.892 --> 01:11:11.104
所以請你刷掉鬍鬚上的碎屑
So, is it too much to ask that you brush the crumbs out of your beard...

1084
01:11:11.271 --> 01:11:13.565
去跟那個褲子姊喇低賽
make schmoopy talk to Pretty Pants...

1085
01:11:14.024 --> 01:11:16.901
趁她不注意時拿走無限寶石
and when she's not looking, suck out the Infinity Stone...

1086
01:11:17.068 --> 01:11:18.653
救我家人回來，行嗎？
and help me get my family back?

1087
01:11:20.321 --> 01:11:21.322
好
Okay.

1088
01:11:21.614 --> 01:11:22.615
你哭了？
Are you crying?

1089
01:11:23.533 --> 01:11:24.534
哪有
No.

1090
01:11:26.369 --> 01:11:27.537
對啦
Yes.

1091
01:11:27.704 --> 01:11:28.913
我快淚崩了
I feel like I'm losing it.

1092
01:11:29.080 --> 01:11:30.081
振作一點
Get it together!

1093
01:11:30.248 --> 01:11:31.249
你做得到
You can do this.

1094
01:11:32.334 --> 01:11:33.752
你做得到
You can do this.

1095
01:11:36.921 --> 01:11:37.922
好不好？
All right?

1096
01:11:38.089 --> 01:11:39.090
對，我可以
Yes, I can.

1097
01:11:39.257 --> 01:11:40.258
很好
Good.

1098
01:11:42.469 --> 01:11:44.804
我做得到…
I can do this. I can do this.

1099
01:11:45.638 --> 01:11:47.098
我做不到
I can't do this.

1100
01:11:47.265 --> 01:11:50.685
撩妹王，她落單，機會來了
All right, heartbreaker, she's alone.

1101
01:11:50.852 --> 01:11:53.438
索爾？
This is our shot. Thor? Thor!

1102
01:11:57.359 --> 01:11:59.903
（莫拉格星，2014年）

1103
01:12:03.823 --> 01:12:05.075
降落，藍臉妹
All right, bring it down, Blue.

1104
01:12:05.241 --> 01:12:07.660
降在線上，下去
Right on that line. That's it. Down, down.

1105
01:12:12.957 --> 01:12:14.000
可以快點嗎？
Hey, can we hurry it up?

1106
01:12:14.167 --> 01:12:16.252
動作快，我們趕時間
Guys, chop-chop. Come on. We're on the clock.

1107
01:12:16.419 --> 01:12:18.171
這樣嗆聲很有幫助喔
All that is really helpful.

1108
01:12:20.382 --> 01:12:21.883
-保重 -好
- Take care, okay? - Yeah.

1109
01:12:22.050 --> 01:12:24.511
把寶石拿回來，別玩瘋了
Get that stone and come back. No messing around.

1110
01:12:25.053 --> 01:12:26.721
-嘿 -我們可以的
- Hey. - We got this.

1111
01:12:26.888 --> 01:12:28.098
-完成任務 -是
- Let's get it done. - Yes, sir.

1112
01:12:28.264 --> 01:12:29.557
回頭見
I'll see you back.

1113
01:12:30.266 --> 01:12:31.601
記得互相照應
You guys watch each other's six.

1114
01:12:32.268 --> 01:12:33.520
好
Yeah.

1115
01:12:42.195 --> 01:12:43.738
佛米爾星的座標已儲存
Coordinates for Vormir are laid in.

1116
01:12:45.365 --> 01:12:47.283
他們只要別起衝突就好
All they have to do is not fall out.

1117
01:12:53.206 --> 01:12:55.583
布達佩斯是好久以前的事了
We're a long way from Budapest.

1118
01:13:00.463 --> 01:13:01.965
好
Okay, so, uh...

1119
01:13:03.216 --> 01:13:06.428
我們等奎爾出現
we just wait around for this Quill guy to show up...

1120
01:13:06.594 --> 01:13:08.430
他就會帶我們去找力量寶石，對吧？
and then he leads us to the Power Stone, is that it?

1121
01:13:09.431 --> 01:13:10.849
我們找掩護
Let's take cover.

1122
01:13:12.475 --> 01:13:14.936
2014年不只有我們在找寶石
We're not the only ones in 2014 looking for the stones.

1123
01:13:15.103 --> 01:13:16.354
等一下，妳在說什麼？
Wait a minute. What are you talking about right now?

1124
01:13:16.521 --> 01:13:17.856
還有誰在找這些寶石？
Who else is looking for these stones?

1125
01:13:21.484 --> 01:13:22.902
我父親
My father...

1126
01:13:23.069 --> 01:13:24.863
我姊
my sister...

1127
01:13:25.030 --> 01:13:26.156
和我
and me.

1128
01:13:26.322 --> 01:13:27.490
妳？
And you?

1129
01:13:29.367 --> 01:13:30.952
妳現在在哪裡？
Where are you right now?

1130
01:13:59.647 --> 01:14:00.815
別客氣
You're welcome.

1131
01:14:00.982 --> 01:14:03.276
我沒請妳幫忙
I didn't ask for your help.

1132
01:14:03.943 --> 01:14:05.570
但妳一向需要幫忙
And yet, you always need it.

1133
01:14:09.616 --> 01:14:11.618
起來，父親要我們回船上
Get up. Father wants us back on the ship.

1134
01:14:11.785 --> 01:14:12.786
為什麼？
Why?

1135
01:14:12.952 --> 01:14:14.954
他發現了一顆無限寶石
He's found an Infinity Stone.

1136
01:14:19.417 --> 01:14:20.877
在哪裡？
Where?

1137
01:14:21.044 --> 01:14:22.796
一個叫莫拉格的星球
On a planet called Morag.

1138
01:14:24.422 --> 01:14:26.341
父親的計畫終於啟動了
Father's plan is finally in motion.

1139
01:14:26.508 --> 01:14:28.510
才一顆寶石而已，涅布拉
One stone isn't six, Nebula.

1140
01:14:28.677 --> 01:14:29.886
總是個開始
It's a start.

1141
01:14:30.053 --> 01:14:31.846
如果他全部拿到手…
If he gets all of them...

1142
01:14:44.859 --> 01:14:48.405
羅南發現力量寶石位置，我派妳們去他船上
Ronan's located the Power Stone. I'm dispatching you to his ship.

1143
01:14:48.571 --> 01:14:49.781
他會不高興
He won't like that.

1144
01:14:49.948 --> 01:14:52.075
那他就別想活了
His alternative is death.

1145
01:14:53.576 --> 01:14:55.328
羅南的執迷
Ronan's obsession...

1146
01:14:56.371 --> 01:14:58.540
影響了他的判斷力
clouds his judgment.

1147
01:15:02.961 --> 01:15:04.754
我們不會讓你失望，父親
We will not fail you, Father.

1148
01:15:05.797 --> 01:15:07.424
妳們不會
No, you won't.

1149
01:15:10.135 --> 01:15:11.136
我發誓…
I swear...

1150
01:15:13.013 --> 01:15:14.931
我會讓你感到驕傲
I will make you proud.

1151
01:15:23.314 --> 01:15:26.985
我們等奎爾出現
...we just wait around for this Quill guy to show up...

1152
01:15:27.152 --> 01:15:29.154
他會帶我們去找力量寶石，對吧？
and then he leads us to the Power Stone, is that it?

1153
01:15:29.320 --> 01:15:30.905
我們找掩護
Let's take cover.

1154
01:15:31.906 --> 01:15:34.784
2014年不只有我們在找寶石
We're not the only ones in 2014 looking for the stones.

1155
01:15:37.203 --> 01:15:38.663
那是誰？
Who was that?

1156
01:15:38.830 --> 01:15:39.831
我不知道
I don't know.

1157
01:15:39.998 --> 01:15:42.167
我頭痛欲裂，不知道
My head is splitting. I don't know.

1158
01:15:43.626 --> 01:15:46.588
她的突觸硬碟大概在打鬥時受損
Her synaptic drive was probably damaged in battle.

1159
01:15:47.807 --> 01:15:49.274
Shh.

1160
01:15:56.848 --> 01:15:58.892
帶她到我船上
Bring her to my ship.

1161
01:16:06.824 --> 01:16:07.359
最好快點，隊長
Better hustle, Cap.

1162
01:16:07.525 --> 01:16:09.611
看來他們這裡要結束了
Things look like they're just about wrapped up here.

1163
01:16:09.778 --> 01:16:11.404
瞭解，我正接近電梯
Got it. I'm approaching the elevator now.

1164
01:16:17.869 --> 01:16:19.454
如果對你來說沒差…
If it's all the same to you...

1165
01:16:21.748 --> 01:16:23.291
我現在就喝那杯酒
I'll have that drink now.

1166
01:16:23.833 --> 01:16:25.293
好，讓他站起來
All right, get him on his feet.

1167
01:16:25.460 --> 01:16:28.463
其他的晚一點再說
We can all stand around posing up a storm later.

1168
01:16:28.630 --> 01:16:29.964
盡量清理一下
By the way, feel free to clean up.

1169
01:16:30.882 --> 01:16:33.134
羅傑斯先生，我差點忘了這套服裝…
Mr. Rogers, I almost forgot that that suit...

1170
01:16:33.301 --> 01:16:35.220
完全沒讓你屁股變翹
did nothing for your ass.

1171
01:16:35.387 --> 01:16:36.513
沒人叫你看，東尼
No one asked you to look, Tony.

1172
01:16:36.680 --> 01:16:38.306
-太可笑了 -你很帥，隊長
It's ridiculous. I think you look great, Cap.

1173
01:16:38.765 --> 01:16:41.267
我認為那就是美國翹臀
As far as I'm concerned, that's America's ass.

1174
01:16:41.476 --> 01:16:43.395
誰拿魔杖？
Who gets the, uh, magic wand?

1175
01:16:43.561 --> 01:16:44.604
神盾局團隊來保護它了
S.T.R.I.K.E. team's coming to secure it.

1176
01:16:55.782 --> 01:16:57.534
我們能幫妳保管
We can take that off your hands.

1177
01:16:57.701 --> 01:16:58.702
請便
By all means.

1178
01:17:00.954 --> 01:17:02.664
小心那玩意
Careful with that thing.

1179
01:17:02.831 --> 01:17:04.290
除非你想讓心智被抹除
Yeah, unless you want your mind erased.

1180
01:17:04.457 --> 01:17:05.458
那可不好玩
And not in a fun way.

1181
01:17:05.625 --> 01:17:06.626
我們保證會小心
We promise to be careful.

1182
01:17:06.793 --> 01:17:07.794
這些人是誰？
Who are these guys?

1183
01:17:07.961 --> 01:17:09.254
他們是神盾局的
They are S.H.I.E.L.D.

1184
01:17:09.421 --> 01:17:12.507
其實是九頭蛇，但當時我們不知道
Well, actually Hydra, but we didn't know that yet.

1185
01:17:12.674 --> 01:17:14.843
真假？你們不知道？
Seriously? You didn't?

1186
01:17:15.010 --> 01:17:16.511
他們一副壞蛋臉
I mean, they look like bad guys.

1187
01:17:16.678 --> 01:17:18.096
你個子小，嗓門卻很大
You're small, but you're talking loud.

1188
01:17:18.263 --> 01:17:20.098
我下去協調搜救行動
On my way down to coordinate search and rescue.

1189
01:17:20.265 --> 01:17:22.225
我下去協調搜救行動
On my way down to coordinate search and rescue.

1190
01:17:22.392 --> 01:17:24.853
說真的，你怎麼沒吐出來？
I mean, honestly, how do you keep your food down?

1191
01:17:25.020 --> 01:17:26.438
閉嘴
Shut up.

1192
01:17:27.022 --> 01:17:28.314
該你上場了，小兄弟
Ooh. All right, you're up, little buddy.

1193
01:17:28.481 --> 01:17:30.608
我們的寶石在那裡
There's our stone.

1194
01:17:30.775 --> 01:17:31.776
好
All right.

1195
01:17:31.943 --> 01:17:33.111
彈我出去
Flick me.

1196
01:17:47.208 --> 01:17:48.209
讓開
- Move. - Hey.

1197
01:17:48.376 --> 01:17:50.128
兄弟
- Whoa, whoa, whoa! - Hey, hey. Buddy!

1198
01:17:50.295 --> 01:17:52.088
你覺得呢？已達人數上限
What do you think? Maximum occupancy has been reached.

1199
01:17:52.255 --> 01:17:53.256
走樓梯
Take the stairs.

1200
01:17:53.423 --> 01:17:55.300
對啊，停…
Yeah. Stop, stop.

1201
01:17:58.053 --> 01:18:00.847
走樓梯，我討厭樓梯
"Take the stairs." Hate the stairs.

1202
01:18:04.559 --> 01:18:06.936
隊長，我看到權杖在電梯裡
All right, Cap, I got our sceptre in the elevator...

1203
01:18:07.103 --> 01:18:08.897
剛經過80樓
just passing the 80th floor.

1204
01:18:09.689 --> 01:18:10.690
馬上去
On it.

1205
01:18:11.524 --> 01:18:13.401
-前往大廳 -到那裡見
Head to the lobby. All right,

1206
01:18:13.777 --> 01:18:15.362
證據安全無虞
I'll see you there. Evidence secure.

1207
01:18:15.528 --> 01:18:16.946
我們正要去找李斯特博士
We're en route to Doctor List.

1208
01:18:17.655 --> 01:18:20.533
完全沒耽誤，局長
No. No hitches at all, Mr. Secretary.

1209
01:18:25.955 --> 01:18:26.706
隊長
Captain.

1210
01:18:26.873 --> 01:18:28.917
我以為你在協調搜救行動
I thought you were coordinating

1211
01:18:29.084 --> 01:18:30.627
計畫有變
search and rescue. Change of plans.

1212
01:18:34.464 --> 01:18:35.882
隊長
Hey, Cap.

1213
01:18:37.175 --> 01:18:38.218
朗姆洛
Rumlow.

1214
01:18:44.516 --> 01:18:46.351
我剛接到局長的電話
I just got a call from the secretary.

1215
01:18:46.518 --> 01:18:48.395
由我主導保護權杖的行動
I'm gonna be running point on the sceptre.

1216
01:18:50.897 --> 01:18:53.149
長官？我不懂
Sir? I don't understand.

1217
01:18:55.610 --> 01:18:57.445
據說有人想竊取它
We got word there may be an attempt to steal it.

1218
01:18:57.612 --> 01:18:59.197
抱歉，隊長
Sorry, Cap.

1219
01:18:59.364 --> 01:19:00.782
權杖不能交給你
We can't give you the sceptre.

1220
01:19:01.366 --> 01:19:03.243
我必須聯絡局長
I'm gonna have to call the director.

1221
01:19:03.410 --> 01:19:05.537
沒關係，相信我
That's okay. Trust me.

1222
01:19:09.124 --> 01:19:10.041
九頭蛇萬歲
Hail Hydra.

1223
01:19:24.764 --> 01:19:26.641
好多階樓梯！
So many stairs!

1224
01:19:38.361 --> 01:19:40.989
拇指姑娘，收到了嗎？我看到目標了
Thumbelina, do you copy? I've got eyes on the prize.

1225
01:19:41.156 --> 01:19:42.240
該行動了
It is go time.

1226
01:19:42.407 --> 01:19:43.408
馬上去
Bombs away.

1227
01:19:50.665 --> 01:19:53.043
那是體香劑嗎？
Is that Axe Body Spray?

1228
01:19:53.209 --> 01:19:55.420
我桌子有一罐以備不時之需，放輕鬆
Yeah, I had a can in the desk for emergencies. Relax.

1229
01:19:55.587 --> 01:19:56.671
可以專心點嗎？
Can we focus, please?

1230
01:19:56.838 --> 01:19:58.089
我要進入你體內…
I'm going inside you...

1231
01:19:58.798 --> 01:19:59.799
現在
now.

1232
01:20:05.680 --> 01:20:07.140
請問你們要去哪裡？
Uh, may I ask you where you're going?

1233
01:20:07.307 --> 01:20:09.559
先吃午飯再去阿斯嘉，你是？
Bit of lunch and then Asgard. I'm sorry, you are...?

1234
01:20:09.726 --> 01:20:10.727
亞歷山大皮爾斯
Alexander Pierce.

1235
01:20:10.894 --> 01:20:13.355
他是尼克福瑞背後那批人的上級
He's the man above the folks - behind Nick Fury. - Oh.

1236
01:20:13.521 --> 01:20:14.647
我朋友叫我局長先生
My friends call me Mr. Secretary.

1237
01:20:14.814 --> 01:20:17.192
我得要求你把那位囚犯交給我
I'm gonna have to ask you to turn that prisoner over to me.

1238
01:20:17.609 --> 01:20:19.152
洛基會向奧丁本人報到
Uh, Loki will be answering to Odin himself.

1239
01:20:19.319 --> 01:20:21.696
他向我們報到，其他人可交給奧丁
No, he's going to answer to us. Odin can have what's left.

1240
01:20:21.863 --> 01:20:23.323
我也需要那個手提箱
And I'm gonna need that case.

1241
01:20:23.490 --> 01:20:25.283
70多年來它都是神盾局財產
That's been S.H.I.E.L.D. property for over 70 years.

1242
01:20:25.450 --> 01:20:26.659
手提箱交出來，史塔克
Hand over the case, Stark.

1243
01:20:26.826 --> 01:20:29.204
動作快，一家之鼠，情況變棘手，快
All right, move it, Stuart Little. Things are getting dicey out here. Let's go.

1244
01:20:29.371 --> 01:20:31.081
我不想爭論誰層級較高…
I'm not gonna argue who's got the higher authority here...

1245
01:20:31.539 --> 01:20:32.832
你保證你不會死？
You promise me you won't die?

1246
01:20:32.999 --> 01:20:35.710
我只會輕微心律不整
We're only giving me a mild cardiac dysrhythmia.

1247
01:20:35.877 --> 01:20:37.462
聽起來並不輕微
That doesn't sound mild.

1248
01:20:37.629 --> 01:20:38.630
我需要那個箱子
I need the case.

1249
01:20:38.797 --> 01:20:40.173
我知道你很大咖，但是管轄權…
I know you got a lot of pull, I'm just saying,

1250
01:20:40.340 --> 01:20:41.508
那就把箱子給我
- jurisdiction... - Okay, then give me the case.

1251
01:20:41.675 --> 01:20:43.718
-管轄權… -交出來
Well, jurisdiction...

1252
01:20:43.885 --> 01:20:44.803
快點！朗恩
Hand it over. Do it, Lang!

1253
01:20:44.969 --> 01:20:46.763
-放開我 -沒時間了，拉我的開關
Get your hands off me. Window's closing. Pull my pin.

1254
01:20:47.931 --> 01:20:49.182
來囉
Here goes!

1255
01:20:52.018 --> 01:20:53.561
-史塔克？ -史塔克？
- Stark? - Stark?

1256
01:20:54.896 --> 01:20:55.980
他在抽搐，讓他透透氣
He's convulsing. Give him air!

1257
01:20:56.147 --> 01:20:57.857
-醫護員 -醫護員
- Medic! - Medic!

1258
01:20:58.400 --> 01:20:59.776
過來幫忙
Give these guys some help.

1259
01:21:00.151 --> 01:21:01.152
說話啊
Speak to me.

1260
01:21:01.611 --> 01:21:03.405
史塔克，是你胸部的機器嗎？
Stark, is it your chest machine?

1261
01:21:06.157 --> 01:21:07.492
呼吸…
Breathe, breathe.

1262
01:21:12.747 --> 01:21:15.083
很好，小巷見，我去吃片披薩
Good job. Meet me in the alley. I'm gonna grab a quick slice.

1263
01:21:20.797 --> 01:21:22.507
不要走樓梯！
No stairs!

1264
01:21:30.724 --> 01:21:32.142
史塔克，撐下去
Uh... Come on, Stark, stay with us.

1265
01:21:32.308 --> 01:21:34.269
我要試一個辦法，不知道有沒有用
I'm going to try something. Okay? I have no idea if it's going to work.

1266
01:21:36.271 --> 01:21:37.147
太好了！
Yes!

1267
01:21:37.313 --> 01:21:38.690
一拍見效
Oh, that worked a treat.

1268
01:21:38.857 --> 01:21:39.858
好誇張
Dude, that was so crazy.

1269
01:21:40.025 --> 01:21:41.401
我也不知道有沒有用
I had no idea if that was gonna work.

1270
01:21:41.568 --> 01:21:43.445
-手提箱 -手提箱…
- The case. - The case is, uh...

1271
01:21:43.611 --> 01:21:45.613
手提箱在哪？洛基呢？
Where's the case? Where's Loki?

1272
01:21:46.614 --> 01:21:47.615
洛基！
Loki!

1273
01:21:47.782 --> 01:21:48.950
那不該發生吧？
That wasn't supposed to happen, was it?

1274
01:21:49.117 --> 01:21:50.243
我們搞砸了
Oh, we blew it.

1275
01:21:50.410 --> 01:21:51.911
洛基？
Loki?

1276
01:21:53.955 --> 01:21:55.248
東尼，怎麼回事？
Tony, what's going on?

1277
01:21:56.249 --> 01:21:57.917
跟我說你找到了那方塊
Tell me you found that Cube.

1278
01:22:00.795 --> 01:22:02.213
開什麼玩笑
Oh, you gotta be shitting me.

1279
01:22:06.301 --> 01:22:08.511
我看到洛基，14樓
I have eyes on Loki. 14th floor.

1280
01:22:08.678 --> 01:22:10.055
我不是洛基
I'm not Loki...

1281
01:22:13.641 --> 01:22:15.268
我不想傷害你
and I don't wanna hurt you.

1282
01:22:24.194 --> 01:22:25.195
我可以陪你慢慢玩
I can do this all day.

1283
01:22:25.362 --> 01:22:26.654
我知道
Yeah, I know.

1284
01:22:26.821 --> 01:22:27.822
我知道
I know.

1285
01:23:00.563 --> 01:23:01.564
你怎麼有這個？
Where did you get this?

1286
01:23:12.867 --> 01:23:15.912
巴奇還活著
Bucky is alive.

1287
01:23:19.457 --> 01:23:20.500
什麼？
What?

1288
01:23:35.432 --> 01:23:36.975
明明就是美國翹臀
That is America's ass.

1289
01:23:41.354 --> 01:23:42.355
求求妳
Please, please.

1290
01:23:42.522 --> 01:23:44.399
抱歉我幫不上忙，布魯斯
I'm sorry, I can't help you, Bruce.

1291
01:23:45.442 --> 01:23:48.570
放棄時間寶石來幫助你的現實，會危及我自己
If I give up the Time Stone to help your reality, I'm dooming my own.

1292
01:23:48.737 --> 01:23:50.488
我有話直說
With all due respect, all right...

1293
01:23:50.655 --> 01:23:53.742
我覺得科學無法支持這一點
I'm not sure the science really supports that.

1294
01:23:59.372 --> 01:24:03.668
無限寶石創造了你體驗到的時間流
The Infinity Stones create what you experience as the flow of time.

1295
01:24:03.835 --> 01:24:05.378
移除一顆寶石
Remove one of the stones...

1296
01:24:05.545 --> 01:24:07.630
時間流便會分裂
and that flow splits.

1297
01:24:07.797 --> 01:24:10.258
它或許有利於你的現實
Now, this may benefit your reality...

1298
01:24:10.425 --> 01:24:12.552
卻不利我的新現實
but my new one, not so much.

1299
01:24:12.927 --> 01:24:14.637
在這新的分支現實
In this new branch reality...

1300
01:24:14.804 --> 01:24:17.891
少了對抗黑暗力量的主要武器
without our chief weapon against the forces of darkness...

1301
01:24:18.308 --> 01:24:20.226
我們的世界將慘遭蹂躪
our world would be overrun.

1302
01:24:20.393 --> 01:24:22.103
千百萬人將受苦受難
Millions will suffer.

1303
01:24:22.270 --> 01:24:23.521
告訴我，博士
So, tell me, Doctor.

1304
01:24:24.105 --> 01:24:26.274
你的科學能預防這一切嗎？
Can your science prevent all that?

1305
01:24:26.441 --> 01:24:27.442
不能
No...

1306
01:24:28.443 --> 01:24:29.569
但我們能抹除它
but we can erase it.

1307
01:24:29.736 --> 01:24:31.446
一旦取回寶石
Because once we're done with the stones...

1308
01:24:31.613 --> 01:24:33.782
我們能將它們送回自己的時間軸
we can return each one to its own timeline...

1309
01:24:33.948 --> 01:24:35.450
回到它們被奪走的時刻
at the moment it was taken.

1310
01:24:35.617 --> 01:24:38.078
所以，在時間上
So, chronologically...

1311
01:24:39.120 --> 01:24:40.163
在那個現實裡
in that reality...

1312
01:24:42.749 --> 01:24:44.417
它從未離開
it never left.

1313
01:24:46.795 --> 01:24:49.881
但你遺漏了最重要的部分
Yes, but you're leaving out the most important part.

1314
01:24:53.468 --> 01:24:55.929
想要送回寶石，你們必須存活
In order to return the stones, you have to survive.

1315
01:24:56.096 --> 01:24:58.682
我們會的，我會，我保證
We will. I will. I promise.

1316
01:24:59.516 --> 01:25:01.559
我不能靠保證讓這個現實冒險
I can't risk this reality on a promise.

1317
01:25:03.228 --> 01:25:07.857
保護時間寶石是至尊魔法師的責任
It's the duty of the Sorcerer Supreme to protect the Time Stone.

1318
01:25:08.233 --> 01:25:10.110
那史傳奇為何把它交出去？
Then why the hell did Strange give it away?

1319
01:25:12.070 --> 01:25:13.154
你說什麼？
What did you say?

1320
01:25:13.321 --> 01:25:15.657
史傳奇，他把它交給薩諾斯
Strange. He gave it away. He gave it to Thanos.

1321
01:25:16.282 --> 01:25:17.867
-自願的？ -對
- Willingly? - Yes.

1322
01:25:21.788 --> 01:25:23.373
-為什麼？ -我不知道
- Why? - I have no idea.

1323
01:25:23.540 --> 01:25:25.291
或許他犯了錯
Maybe he made a mistake.

1324
01:25:35.427 --> 01:25:36.720
也許是我犯了錯
Or I did.

1325
01:25:56.990 --> 01:25:59.409
史傳奇應該是我們當中最優秀的
Strange is meant to be the best of us.

1326
01:25:59.576 --> 01:26:02.078
那他那麼做必定有原因
So, he must've done it for a reason.

1327
01:26:02.871 --> 01:26:04.497
恐怕沒錯
I fear you might be right.

1328
01:26:09.669 --> 01:26:10.670
謝謝
Thank you.

1329
01:26:16.926 --> 01:26:18.595
我就指望你了，布魯斯
I'm counting on you, Bruce.

1330
01:26:20.638 --> 01:26:21.848
我們都是
We all are.

1331
01:26:42.327 --> 01:26:43.870
進行診斷
Run diagnostics.

1332
01:26:44.621 --> 01:26:46.581
呈現她的記憶檔案
Show me her memory file.

1333
01:26:48.166 --> 01:26:50.627
老大，檔案顯得非常亂
Sire, the file appears entangled.

1334
01:26:51.795 --> 01:26:53.755
是記憶，卻不是她的
It was a memory, but not hers.

1335
01:26:55.006 --> 01:26:56.424
有另一個意識…
There's another consciousness...

1336
01:26:56.591 --> 01:26:57.884
在共用她的網絡
sharing her network.

1337
01:26:58.426 --> 01:26:59.761
另一個涅布拉
Another Nebula.

1338
01:27:01.888 --> 01:27:03.348
不可能
Impossible.

1339
01:27:03.515 --> 01:27:06.142
這個分身有一個時間戳記
This duplicate carries a time stamp...

1340
01:27:07.060 --> 01:27:09.229
來自九年後
from nine years in the future.

1341
01:27:13.817 --> 01:27:16.319
另一個涅布拉在哪裡？
Where is this other Nebula?

1342
01:27:16.986 --> 01:27:18.988
在我們太陽系，莫拉格星
In our solar system on Morag.

1343
01:27:20.532 --> 01:27:21.825
你能進入她的記憶嗎？
Can you access her?

1344
01:27:21.991 --> 01:27:24.035
可以，兩者相連
Yes, the two are linked.

1345
01:27:24.202 --> 01:27:26.287
搜尋分身的記憶…
Search the duplicate's memories...

1346
01:27:26.454 --> 01:27:28.665
找出無限寶石
for Infinity Stones.

1347
01:27:32.210 --> 01:27:35.171
這些寶石在歷史上許多地方出現過
And these stones have been in a lot of different places throughout history.

1348
01:27:35.338 --> 01:27:36.339
我們的歷史
Our history.

1349
01:27:36.506 --> 01:27:38.633
容易前往的時間點…
So, not a lot of convenient spots

1350
01:27:38.800 --> 01:27:39.926
並不多
to just drop in.

1351
01:27:40.093 --> 01:27:41.761
所以我們必須挑選目標
Which means we have to pick our targets.

1352
01:27:41.928 --> 01:27:43.221
-沒錯 -暫停影像
- Correct. - Freeze image.

1353
01:27:45.181 --> 01:27:46.391
地球人
Terrans.

1354
01:27:47.475 --> 01:27:49.144
復仇者聯盟
Avengers.

1355
01:27:50.228 --> 01:27:51.938
任性的下流胚子
Unruly wretches.

1356
01:27:52.105 --> 01:27:53.606
那反射影像是什麼？
What's that reflection?

1357
01:27:55.233 --> 01:27:56.401
強化它，烏木喉
Amplify this, Maw.

1358
01:27:59.904 --> 01:28:01.114
我不懂
I don't understand.

1359
01:28:05.827 --> 01:28:07.412
兩個涅布拉
Two Nebulas.

1360
01:28:07.579 --> 01:28:09.998
不，同一個涅布拉
No. The same Nebula...

1361
01:28:10.790 --> 01:28:12.542
來自兩個不同時間
from two different times.

1362
01:28:13.835 --> 01:28:15.462
航向莫拉格星
Set course for Morag.

1363
01:28:15.628 --> 01:28:18.006
掃描分身的記憶
And scan the duplicate's memories.

1364
01:28:18.757 --> 01:28:21.134
我想看個一清二楚
I wanna see everything.

1365
01:28:30.935 --> 01:28:34.397
回頭見，妳們走吧
My ladies, I'll see you after. I'll see you after. Go on ahead.

1366
01:28:48.787 --> 01:28:49.788
你在做什麼？
What are you doing?

1367
01:28:51.414 --> 01:28:52.624
天啊
Oh, God!

1368
01:28:52.791 --> 01:28:55.251
不要學你弟偷溜
You're better off leaving the sneaking to your brother.

1369
01:28:55.418 --> 01:28:57.295
我沒有偷溜，我想去散步
No, I wasn't sneaking. I was just going for a walk.

1370
01:28:57.462 --> 01:28:58.797
你穿這是什麼？
What are you wearing?

1371
01:28:58.963 --> 01:29:01.341
我常穿這個，我最喜歡的
I always wear this. It's one of my favourites.

1372
01:29:05.428 --> 01:29:06.805
你眼睛怎麼了？
Mm... What's wrong with your eye?

1373
01:29:06.971 --> 01:29:07.972
我的眼睛
Oh, my eye.

1374
01:29:08.139 --> 01:29:10.100
記得哈洛金戰役
Remember the, uh, Battle of Harokin...

1375
01:29:10.266 --> 01:29:13.353
我的臉被大刀砍傷嗎？
when I got hit in the face with the broadsword?

1376
01:29:16.898 --> 01:29:18.942
你根本不是我認識的索爾吧？
You're not the Thor I know at all, are you?

1377
01:29:19.693 --> 01:29:21.444
我是
Yes, I am.

1378
01:29:21.945 --> 01:29:24.447
你在未來過得不好，對吧？
The future hasn't been kind to you, has it?

1379
01:29:24.906 --> 01:29:26.825
我沒說我來自未來
I didn't say I was from the future.

1380
01:29:27.283 --> 01:29:29.828
我是女巫養大的，孩子
I was raised by witches, boy.

1381
01:29:30.870 --> 01:29:33.248
你知道我不只用眼睛看
I see with more than eyes, you know that.

1382
01:29:35.333 --> 01:29:37.585
對，我就是來自未來
Yeah, I'm totally from the future.

1383
01:29:37.752 --> 01:29:39.379
你是，親愛的
Yes, you are, honey.

1384
01:29:39.546 --> 01:29:41.047
我真的很需要跟妳談
I really need to talk to you.

1385
01:29:41.214 --> 01:29:42.215
我們可以談談
We can talk.

1386
01:30:06.364 --> 01:30:08.324
他的頭在那裡
His head was over there...

1387
01:30:08.950 --> 01:30:11.453
身體在那邊
and his body over there...

1388
01:30:12.746 --> 01:30:15.248
有什麼意義呢？我太遲了
I mean, what was the point? I was too late.

1389
01:30:15.915 --> 01:30:17.542
我只是杵在那裡
I was just standing there.

1390
01:30:18.501 --> 01:30:20.253
一個拿著斧頭的白癡
Some idiot with an axe.

1391
01:30:20.420 --> 01:30:22.130
你不是白癡
Now, you're no idiot.

1392
01:30:23.256 --> 01:30:24.841
你不是來了嗎？
You're here, aren't you?

1393
01:30:25.050 --> 01:30:27.510
向阿斯嘉最睿智的人徵詢意見
Seeking counsel from the wisest person in Asgard.

1394
01:30:27.844 --> 01:30:28.887
對
I am. Yes.

1395
01:30:29.054 --> 01:30:30.388
白癡，不是
Idiot, no.

1396
01:30:30.555 --> 01:30:32.057
失敗者？
A failure?

1397
01:30:32.223 --> 01:30:33.350
當然
Absolutely.

1398
01:30:33.516 --> 01:30:35.310
有點傷人
That's a little bit harsh.

1399
01:30:35.477 --> 01:30:36.978
這讓你成了什麼呢？
Do you know what that makes you?

1400
01:30:38.188 --> 01:30:40.190
跟其他人沒兩樣
Just like everyone else.

1401
01:30:40.357 --> 01:30:43.234
我不該跟其他人沒兩樣吧？
I'm not supposed to be like everyone else, am I?

1402
01:30:43.735 --> 01:30:46.905
每個人都無法成為理想中的自己，索爾
Mm. Everyone fails at who they're supposed to be, Thor.

1403
01:30:47.614 --> 01:30:50.658
衡量一個人，一個英雄
The measure of a person, of a hero...

1404
01:30:50.825 --> 01:30:54.204
要看他們是否成功做自己
is how well they succeed at being who they are.

1405
01:30:59.459 --> 01:31:00.919
我真的好想妳，媽
I've really missed you, Mom.

1406
01:31:06.800 --> 01:31:08.551
索爾！我拿到了
Thor! I got it!

1407
01:31:09.427 --> 01:31:10.970
抓住那隻兔子
Get that rabbit!

1408
01:31:13.973 --> 01:31:15.558
媽，我得告訴妳一件事
Mom, I have to tell you something.

1409
01:31:15.725 --> 01:31:17.519
兒子，你不必說
No, son, you don't.

1410
01:31:17.686 --> 01:31:20.188
你是來修補你的未來，不是我的
You're here to repair your future, not mine.

1411
01:31:20.355 --> 01:31:22.023
這關乎妳的未來
This is about your future.

1412
01:31:22.190 --> 01:31:23.525
與我無關
Uh, it's none of my business.

1413
01:31:27.529 --> 01:31:28.780
妳好
Hi.

1414
01:31:28.947 --> 01:31:30.949
妳一定是索爾的媽
You must be Mom.

1415
01:31:31.116 --> 01:31:32.575
我拿到了，我們快走
I got the thing. Come on. We gotta move.

1416
01:31:32.742 --> 01:31:34.202
真希望能留久一點
Oh, I wish we had more time.

1417
01:31:34.369 --> 01:31:36.204
不，這是上天的恩賜
No, this was a gift.

1418
01:31:36.371 --> 01:31:39.791
去承擔你該當的角色吧
Now you go and be the man you're meant to be.

1419
01:31:40.250 --> 01:31:41.334
我愛妳，媽
I love you, Mom.

1420
01:31:41.501 --> 01:31:42.419
我愛你
I love you.

1421
01:31:46.881 --> 01:31:48.800
多吃沙拉
And eat a salad.

1422
01:31:49.801 --> 01:31:50.927
我們該走了
Come on, we gotta go.

1423
01:31:51.094 --> 01:31:52.679
-再見 -三…
- Goodbye. - Three...

1424
01:31:52.846 --> 01:31:53.930
-二… -不，等等！
- Two... - No, wait!

1425
01:31:57.183 --> 01:31:58.393
現在是怎樣？
What am I looking at?

1426
01:31:58.560 --> 01:32:00.020
有時需要一下子
Oh, sometimes it takes a second.

1427
01:32:09.904 --> 01:32:11.531
我還有資格
I'm still worthy.

1428
01:32:12.949 --> 01:32:14.576
天啊
Oh, boy.

1429
01:32:15.744 --> 01:32:17.662
-再見，媽 -再見
- Goodbye, Mom. - Goodbye.

1430
01:32:56.910 --> 01:32:58.536
所以他是白癡？
So, he's an idiot?

1431
01:32:59.871 --> 01:33:01.289
嗯
Yeah.

1432
01:33:09.798 --> 01:33:11.007
那是什麼？
What's that?

1433
01:33:11.174 --> 01:33:13.051
小偷的傢伙
The tool of a thief.

1434
01:33:20.811 --> 01:33:24.437
這時牆面會有尖刺伸出來
Whoa, whoa, whoa. This is the part where spikes come out...

1435
01:33:24.604 --> 01:33:26.022
尾端還有骷髏
with skeletons on the end of them and everything.

1436
01:33:26.189 --> 01:33:27.399
你在說什麼？
What are you talking about?

1437
01:33:27.565 --> 01:33:29.901
闖入力量寶石神殿時
When you break into a place called "The Temple of the Power Stone"...

1438
01:33:30.068 --> 01:33:31.361
一定會有不少陷阱
there's gonna be a bunch of booby traps.

1439
01:33:31.528 --> 01:33:33.780
-天啊 -好吧，妳走吧
- Oh, my God. - Okay. All right. Go ahead.

1440
01:34:07.063 --> 01:34:08.565
我並非一直這副模樣
I wasn't always like this.

1441
01:34:09.482 --> 01:34:10.483
我也不是
Me either.

1442
01:34:12.277 --> 01:34:13.737
我們只能物盡其用，對吧？
But we work with what we got, right?

1443
01:34:17.490 --> 01:34:19.159
一起
Hmm. Let's sync up.

1444
01:34:21.036 --> 01:34:23.496
三，二，一
Three, two, one.

1445
01:34:36.343 --> 01:34:37.969
你謀殺了數十億人
You murdered trillions!

1446
01:34:38.136 --> 01:34:39.554
你應該心存感激
You should be grateful.

1447
01:34:41.181 --> 01:34:42.766
寶石在哪裡？
Where are the stones?

1448
01:34:42.932 --> 01:34:43.933
灰飛煙滅
Gone.

1449
01:34:44.684 --> 01:34:45.685
縮小成原子
Reduced to atoms.

1450
01:34:46.394 --> 01:34:48.063
兩天前你才用過它們
You used them two days ago!

1451
01:34:48.355 --> 01:34:51.358
我用寶石來摧毀寶石
I used the stones to destroy the stones.

1452
01:34:51.524 --> 01:34:53.360
差點害我沒命
It nearly killed me.

1453
01:34:53.526 --> 01:34:55.445
但任務結束了
But the work is done.

1454
01:34:55.612 --> 01:34:57.447
總是會結束的
It always will be.

1455
01:34:58.740 --> 01:35:02.202
我是無可匹敵的
I am inevitable.

1456
01:35:03.453 --> 01:35:05.497
你對他們做了什麼？
What did you do to them?

1457
01:35:05.663 --> 01:35:06.915
沒有
Nothing.

1458
01:35:07.791 --> 01:35:09.084
還沒
Yet.

1459
01:35:10.877 --> 01:35:14.589
他們不是想阻止我即將做的事
They're not trying to stop something I'm going to do in our time.

1460
01:35:14.923 --> 01:35:18.551
他們想逆轉我在他們那時候已經做的事
They're trying to undo something I've already done in theirs.

1461
01:35:18.718 --> 01:35:20.387
寶石
The stones.

1462
01:35:21.304 --> 01:35:23.223
我全都找到了
I found them all.

1463
01:35:25.016 --> 01:35:26.393
我贏了
I won.

1464
01:35:27.143 --> 01:35:30.105
讓宇宙達到平衡
Tipped the cosmic scales to balance.

1465
01:35:34.109 --> 01:35:35.860
這是您的未來
This is your future.

1466
01:35:36.194 --> 01:35:38.238
這是我的天命
It's my destiny.

1467
01:35:39.447 --> 01:35:41.491
我父親有很多面向
My father is many things.

1468
01:35:41.658 --> 01:35:43.493
卻不會說謊
A liar is not one of them.

1469
01:35:47.205 --> 01:35:49.124
謝謝妳，女兒
Ah. Thank you, daughter.

1470
01:35:49.290 --> 01:35:51.459
或許我對妳太嚴厲了
Perhaps I treated you too harshly.

1471
01:35:55.964 --> 01:35:58.842
天命就此實現
And that is destiny fulfilled.

1472
01:35:59.259 --> 01:36:00.635
老大
Sire...

1473
01:36:00.802 --> 01:36:01.928
您女兒…
your daughter...

1474
01:36:04.389 --> 01:36:05.390
不！
No!

1475
01:36:05.849 --> 01:36:06.891
是叛徒
...is a traitor.

1476
01:36:07.058 --> 01:36:09.519
那不是我，我不可能…
That's not me. It's not, I could never...

1477
01:36:09.686 --> 01:36:10.854
我絕對不會背叛你
I would never betray you.

1478
01:36:11.021 --> 01:36:12.856
絕對不會
Never. Never.

1479
01:36:18.611 --> 01:36:19.779
我知道
I know.

1480
01:36:20.739 --> 01:36:23.992
妳會有機會證明的
And you'll have the chance to prove it.

1481
01:36:30.290 --> 01:36:31.374
糟糕
No!

1482
01:36:32.083 --> 01:36:33.293
他知道了
He knows!

1483
01:36:37.881 --> 01:36:39.924
巴頓…請回答
Barton! Barton, come in.

1484
01:36:40.550 --> 01:36:41.843
羅曼諾夫
Romanoff!

1485
01:36:42.469 --> 01:36:43.887
請回答，我們碰上麻煩了
Come in, we have a problem.

1486
01:36:44.054 --> 01:36:45.180
快啊
Come on!

1487
01:36:45.347 --> 01:36:46.765
請回答，我們碰上…
Come in, we have a...

1488
01:36:46.931 --> 01:36:48.266
薩諾斯知道了
Thanos knows.

1489
01:36:48.933 --> 01:36:50.185
薩諾斯…
Thanos...

1490
01:37:03.907 --> 01:37:04.991
隊長
Cap.

1491
01:37:06.618 --> 01:37:08.870
抱歉，我們碰上問題了
Sorry, buddy, we got a problem.

1492
01:37:09.704 --> 01:37:11.039
真的
Yeah, we do.

1493
01:37:11.623 --> 01:37:12.624
現在怎麼辦？
Well, what are we gonna do now?

1494
01:37:12.791 --> 01:37:13.792
饒了我吧，史帝夫
You know what? Give me a break, Steve.

1495
01:37:13.958 --> 01:37:15.377
我的頭剛挨了浩克一拳
I just got hit in the head with the Hulk.

1496
01:37:15.543 --> 01:37:16.961
你說我們只有一次機會
You said that we had one shot.

1497
01:37:17.128 --> 01:37:18.463
這就是我們的機會
This was our shot.

1498
01:37:18.630 --> 01:37:20.632
我們試過了，不拿到六顆就沒用
We shot it. It's shot. Six stones or nothing.

1499
01:37:20.799 --> 01:37:22.175
-不拿到六顆就沒用 -你在鬼打牆
- It was six stones or nothing. - You're repeating yourself,

1500
01:37:22.342 --> 01:37:23.343
你在鬼打牆
you know that? You're repeating yourself.

1501
01:37:23.510 --> 01:37:25.220
你才在鬼打牆…
You're repeating yourself. You're repeating yourself.

1502
01:37:25.387 --> 01:37:27.180
-拜託 -你根本不要時間攔劫
Dude. Come on! No. You never wanted a time heist.

1503
01:37:27.347 --> 01:37:28.348
你不贊成時間攔劫
You weren't on board with the time heist.

1504
01:37:28.515 --> 01:37:29.641
-我錯了 -你毀了時間攔劫
- I dropped the ball. - You ruined the time heist.

1505
01:37:29.808 --> 01:37:31.101
-我有嗎？ -有
- Is that what I did? - Yeah.

1506
01:37:31.267 --> 01:37:33.061
有別的辦法能拿到宇宙魔方嗎？
Are there any other options with the Tesseract?

1507
01:37:33.228 --> 01:37:34.437
沒有別的辦法
No, no, no, there's no other options.

1508
01:37:34.604 --> 01:37:35.855
不能重來
There's no do-overs.

1509
01:37:36.022 --> 01:37:38.108
我們不能亂跑，只剩一管粒子
We're not going anywhere else. We have one particle left.

1510
01:37:38.274 --> 01:37:39.109
每人一管
Each.

1511
01:37:39.275 --> 01:37:41.569
就這樣，懂嗎？只要用了…
That's it. All right? We use that...

1512
01:37:41.736 --> 01:37:42.904
掰掰，你們就別想回家
bye-bye, you're not going home.

1513
01:37:43.071 --> 01:37:45.031
如果我們不嘗試
Yeah, well, if we don't try...

1514
01:37:45.198 --> 01:37:46.366
誰都別想回家
then no one else is going home, either.

1515
01:37:46.533 --> 01:37:47.450
我想到了
I got it.

1516
01:37:48.743 --> 01:37:52.789
有辦法能拿回宇宙魔方，取得新的粒子
There's another way to retake the Tesseract and acquire new particles.

1517
01:37:53.623 --> 01:37:54.666
回憶一下往事
Little stroll down memory lane.

1518
01:37:55.458 --> 01:37:57.293
軍事設施，紐澤西州
Military installation, Garden State.

1519
01:38:01.381 --> 01:38:02.674
他們倆都在那邊的時候？
When were they both there?

1520
01:38:02.841 --> 01:38:05.218
他們曾經在那裡，我有點模糊
They were there at a time... I have a vaguely exact idea.

1521
01:38:05.885 --> 01:38:06.886
-多模糊？ -你們說什麼？
- How vague? - What are you talking about?

1522
01:38:07.053 --> 01:38:07.929
我們要去哪？
Where are we going?

1523
01:38:08.096 --> 01:38:09.014
我確定他們在那裡
I know for a fact they were there.

1524
01:38:09.180 --> 01:38:10.890
-誰啊？這幹嘛？ -我知道我怎麼知道的
Who's they? What are we doing? And I know how I know.

1525
01:38:13.268 --> 01:38:14.811
到底是怎樣？
Guys, what is it?

1526
01:38:15.395 --> 01:38:17.022
看來我們要隨機應變
Looks like we're improvising.

1527
01:38:17.188 --> 01:38:18.314
-太好了 -隨機應變什麼？
- Great. - What are we improvising?

1528
01:38:18.481 --> 01:38:20.233
史考特，把這拿回總部
Scott, get this back to the compound.

1529
01:38:20.400 --> 01:38:21.317
整裝
Suit up.

1530
01:38:21.651 --> 01:38:23.111
-紐澤西有什麼？ -04
- What's in New Jersey? - 0-4.

1531
01:38:23.278 --> 01:38:24.112

1532
0-4.

1533
01:38:24.279 --> 01:38:25.280
-07
-07

1534
01:38:25.447 --> 01:38:27.323
-請問一下 -1970 - Uh, 0-7.
- 0-7. - Excuse me. - 1-9-7-0.

1535
01:38:27.782 --> 01:38:28.700
你確定嗎？
Are you sure?

1536
01:38:28.867 --> 01:38:30.160
隊長？
Cap? Captain?

1537
01:38:30.326 --> 01:38:32.162
史帝夫？抱歉
Steve? Sorry.

1538
01:38:32.328 --> 01:38:33.955
美國…羅傑斯
America. Rogers.

1539
01:38:34.122 --> 01:38:35.331
如果這麼做
Look, if you do this...

1540
01:38:35.623 --> 01:38:38.168
卻沒用，你們就回不來了
and it doesn't work, you're not coming back.

1541
01:38:39.252 --> 01:38:41.046
謝謝你的鼓勵，小蟻子
Thanks for the pep talk, pissant.

1542
01:38:42.088 --> 01:38:43.298
你相信我嗎？
You trust me?

1543
01:38:44.174 --> 01:38:45.342
相信
I do.

1544
01:38:46.384 --> 01:38:47.719
你決定
Your call.

1545
01:38:48.595 --> 01:38:50.305
出發吧
Here we go.

1546
01:38:57.228 --> 01:38:59.814
（紐澤西，1970年）

1547
01:39:00.732 --> 01:39:03.193
（說夠了）

1548
01:39:06.363 --> 01:39:09.991
老兄！做愛不打仗
Hey, man! Make love, not war.

1549
01:39:10.158 --> 01:39:12.911
（美國陸軍勒海營基地）

1550
01:39:13.078 --> 01:39:15.747
（第78步兵師，美國隊長誕生地）

1551
01:39:15.914 --> 01:39:18.583
顯然你不是在這裡出生吧？
Clearly you weren't actually born here, right?

1552
01:39:18.750 --> 01:39:20.251
我的概念是
The idea of me was.

1553
01:39:21.419 --> 01:39:22.962
假設你是神盾局
Right. Well, imagine you're S.H.I.E.L.D...

1554
01:39:23.129 --> 01:39:26.383
運作一個類法西斯情報組織
running a quasi-fascistic intelligence organization...

1555
01:39:27.717 --> 01:39:29.302
你會藏在哪裡？
where do you hide it?

1556
01:39:29.469 --> 01:39:31.137
近在眼前
In plain sight.

1557
01:39:59.541 --> 01:40:00.667
祝你任務順利，隊長
Good luck on your mission, Captain.

1558
01:40:00.834 --> 01:40:03.378
祝你計畫順利，博士
Good luck on your project, Doctor.

1559
01:40:06.798 --> 01:40:07.882
新來的嗎？
You new here?

1560
01:40:10.427 --> 01:40:11.761
不算
Not exactly.

1561
01:40:18.435 --> 01:40:20.228
快啊，混蛋
Come on, you bastard.

1562
01:40:20.395 --> 01:40:23.148
（伽瑪特徵不符）

1563
01:40:25.442 --> 01:40:26.860
（目標相符）

1564
01:40:27.027 --> 01:40:28.528
找到了
Gotcha.

1565
01:40:34.033 --> 01:40:35.034
Whew.

1566
01:40:46.087 --> 01:40:47.756
重回戰場
Back in the game.

1567
01:40:50.425 --> 01:40:51.634
阿尼姆，你在裡面嗎？
Arnim, you in there?

1568
01:40:52.594 --> 01:40:53.636
阿尼姆？
Arnim?

1569
01:40:58.933 --> 01:41:00.268
喂！
Hey!

1570
01:41:00.935 --> 01:41:02.645
門在這邊，老兄
The door is this way, pal.

1571
01:41:03.646 --> 01:41:04.522
對喔
Oh, yeah.

1572
01:41:04.689 --> 01:41:06.566
我在找左拉博士，有看到他嗎？
Looking for Doctor Zola, have you seen him?

1573
01:41:06.733 --> 01:41:10.153
左拉博士…我沒看到任何人
Yeah, Doctor Zola. No, I haven't seen a soul.

1574
01:41:11.654 --> 01:41:12.989
不好意思
Pardon me.

1575
01:41:13.740 --> 01:41:15.367
我們認識嗎？
Do I know you?

1576
01:41:16.618 --> 01:41:17.619
不認識
No, sir. Uh...

1577
01:41:19.079 --> 01:41:20.872
我從麻省理工學院來訪
I'm a visitor from MIT.

1578
01:41:21.456 --> 01:41:22.582
麻省理工學院
Oh. MIT.

1579
01:41:23.041 --> 01:41:24.167
大名？
Got a name?

1580
01:41:24.626 --> 01:41:25.752
霍華
Howard.

1581
01:41:25.919 --> 01:41:28.421
-很好記 -霍華…
- That'll be easy to remember. - Howard...

1582
01:41:29.422 --> 01:41:30.423
波茲
Potts.

1583
01:41:31.007 --> 01:41:33.218
我是霍華史塔克
Well, I'm Howard Stark.

1584
01:41:33.385 --> 01:41:34.302
你好
Hi.

1585
01:41:34.469 --> 01:41:35.762
握手，別拉手指
Shake that, don't pull it.

1586
01:41:35.929 --> 01:41:36.930
是
Yeah.

1587
01:41:38.348 --> 01:41:40.558
你看來氣色不太好，波茲
You look a little green around the gills, there, Potts.

1588
01:41:40.725 --> 01:41:42.894
我很好，只是上班累了
I'm fine. Just long hours.

1589
01:41:43.061 --> 01:41:44.771
想出去透透氣嗎？
You wanna get some air?

1590
01:41:47.315 --> 01:41:49.109
-喂，波茲 -是
- Hello, Potts. - Yeah.

1591
01:41:49.275 --> 01:41:50.527
-好啊 -這邊請
- That'd be swell. - That way.

1592
01:41:50.694 --> 01:41:51.653
好
Okay.

1593
01:41:51.820 --> 01:41:53.488
需要拿公事包嗎？
Need your briefcase?

1594
01:41:57.826 --> 01:42:00.412
你不是披頭族吧，波茲？
You're not one of those beatniks, are you, Potts?

1595
01:42:06.251 --> 01:42:08.044
-喂？ -皮姆博士？
- Hello? - Doctor Pym?

1596
01:42:08.211 --> 01:42:10.422
你打的號碼沒錯，是
That would be the number that you called, yes.

1597
01:42:10.588 --> 01:42:12.841
我是快遞公司的史帝芬斯隊長
This is Captain Stevens from shipping.

1598
01:42:13.008 --> 01:42:14.134
有你的包裹
We have a package for you.

1599
01:42:14.509 --> 01:42:15.677
拿上來
Oh, bring it up.

1600
01:42:15.844 --> 01:42:17.804
問題就在這，沒辦法
That's the thing, sir, we can't.

1601
01:42:18.930 --> 01:42:21.558
我不懂，那不是你的工作嗎？
I'm confused. I thought that was your job.

1602
01:42:21.725 --> 01:42:23.101
因為…
Well, it's just...

1603
01:42:23.268 --> 01:42:24.728
先生，這箱子在發光
Sir, the box is glowing...

1604
01:42:24.894 --> 01:42:27.689
我們有些快遞員覺得不舒服
and to be honest, some of our mail guys aren't feeling that great.

1605
01:42:27.856 --> 01:42:29.566
他們沒打開箱子吧？
They didn't open it, did they?

1606
01:42:29.733 --> 01:42:31.901
有，你最好下來
Uh, yeah, they did. You better get down here.

1607
01:42:32.736 --> 01:42:34.654
借過，讓開
Excuse me! Out of the way!

1608
01:42:39.367 --> 01:42:41.786
（亨利皮姆博士）

1609
01:42:53.590 --> 01:42:55.633
（皮姆粒子，請勿碰觸）

1610
01:43:01.848 --> 01:43:05.352
鮮花和德國酸菜，晚上有重要約會嗎？
So, flowers and sauerkraut. You got a big date tonight?

1611
01:43:06.102 --> 01:43:07.562
我太太懷孕了
Uh, my wife's expecting.

1612
01:43:07.729 --> 01:43:10.565
我花太多時間在辦公室
And too much time at the office.

1613
01:43:12.400 --> 01:43:13.777
恭喜
Congratulations.

1614
01:43:13.943 --> 01:43:16.071
-謝謝，麻煩拿一下 -沒問題
- Thanks. Hold this, will ya? - Yeah, sure.

1615
01:43:17.155 --> 01:43:19.240
-她懷孕幾個月？ -不知道
- How far along is she? - Uh, I don't know.

1616
01:43:21.034 --> 01:43:23.787
目前她受不了我嚼東西的聲音
She's at the point where she can't stand the sound of my chewing.

1617
01:43:23.953 --> 01:43:27.415
我又得在廚房角落吃晚餐了
I guess I'll be eating dinner in the pantry again.

1618
01:43:28.333 --> 01:43:29.334
我有個女兒
I have a little girl.

1619
01:43:29.501 --> 01:43:31.002
生女兒不錯
A girl would be nice.

1620
01:43:31.169 --> 01:43:33.171
比較不會變得跟我一個樣
Less of a chance she'd turn out exactly like me.

1621
01:43:33.838 --> 01:43:35.298
那有什麼不好？
What'd be so awful about that?

1622
01:43:35.465 --> 01:43:40.845
我認為我通常是個自私的人
Let's just say that the greater good has rarely outweighed my own self-interest.

1623
01:43:44.891 --> 01:43:45.934
妳沒見過這兩個人？
And you've never seen these two men before?

1624
01:43:46.101 --> 01:43:47.936
我直覺很準，他們倆怪怪的
No, I've got an eye for this. The two of them looked fishy.

1625
01:43:48.103 --> 01:43:50.355
-長什麼樣子？ -一個留嬉皮鬍鬚
Can you describe them? One of them had a hippie beard.

1626
01:43:50.522 --> 01:43:52.691
嬉皮，像比吉斯還是蒙哥傑瑞？
Hippie. Like Bee Gees or Mungo Jerry?

1627
01:43:52.857 --> 01:43:53.900
很像蒙哥傑瑞
Definitely Mungo Jerry.

1628
01:43:54.067 --> 01:43:56.236
我是契斯勒，請所有憲兵到地下六樓
Yeah, this is Chesler. I need every available MP to sublevel six.

1629
01:43:56.403 --> 01:43:58.279
可能有外人闖入
We have a potential breach.

1630
01:44:13.920 --> 01:44:16.006
（瑪格麗特卡特，局長）

1631
01:44:16.172 --> 01:44:17.132
我說把他們轉過來
I said bring them in.

1632
01:44:17.298 --> 01:44:18.299
他們在想辦法，
They're trying, ma'am, but Braddock's unit

1633
01:44:18.466 --> 01:44:19.467
但布拉多克的小組因雷擊受阻
has been stopped by lightning strikes.

1634
01:44:19.634 --> 01:44:20.468
真是的
Oh, for the love of...

1635
01:44:20.635 --> 01:44:22.137
我來看看氣象預報
I'll look at the weather projections.

1636
01:44:46.161 --> 01:44:48.163
情況不是雷擊
It's not lightning strikes we're looking at.

1637
01:44:59.507 --> 01:45:01.217
你們想好名字了嗎？
So, where you at with names?

1638
01:45:01.384 --> 01:45:04.512
如果是男生，我太太喜歡艾蒙佐
Well, if it's a boy, my wife likes Elmonzo. Huh.

1639
01:45:05.472 --> 01:45:07.766
再考慮一下，還有時間
Might wanna let that stew awhile. You got time. - Uh-huh.

1640
01:45:09.559 --> 01:45:11.061
問你一個問題
Let me ask you a question.

1641
01:45:12.062 --> 01:45:15.315
小孩出生時，你緊張嗎？
When your kid was born, were you nervous?

1642
01:45:15.482 --> 01:45:16.816
快瘋了
Wildly.

1643
01:45:17.067 --> 01:45:18.777
-嗯 -你覺得自己夠格嗎？
- Yeah. - Did you feel qualified?

1644
01:45:18.943 --> 01:45:22.530
你知道如何當個成功的父親嗎？
Like you had any idea how to successfully operate that thing?

1645
01:45:22.947 --> 01:45:25.784
我一路走來邊做邊學
I literally pieced it together as I went along.

1646
01:45:25.950 --> 01:45:27.952
回想我爸的做法
I thought about what my dad did.

1647
01:45:28.661 --> 01:45:30.830
我老爸一律用皮帶解決問題
My old man, he never met a problem he couldn't solve with a belt.

1648
01:45:31.623 --> 01:45:33.667
我以為我爸對我很嚴格
I thought my dad was tough on me.

1649
01:45:33.833 --> 01:45:36.544
如今回想起來，我只記得好的事情
And now, looking back on it, I just remember the good stuff.

1650
01:45:36.711 --> 01:45:38.296
他說過一些至理名言
You know? He did drop the odd pearl.

1651
01:45:38.463 --> 01:45:39.839
是嗎？譬如說？
Yeah? Like what?

1652
01:45:40.965 --> 01:45:43.468
金錢買不到時間
"No amount of money ever bought a second of time."

1653
01:45:44.803 --> 01:45:45.845
有智慧
Smart guy.

1654
01:45:46.262 --> 01:45:47.722
他盡力了
He did his best.

1655
01:45:49.099 --> 01:45:53.061
孩子還沒出生，我已願為他付出一切
I'll tell you, that kid's not even here yet and there's nothing I wouldn't do for him.

1656
01:46:01.820 --> 01:46:03.196
幸會，波茲
Good to meet you, Potts.

1657
01:46:03.863 --> 01:46:04.698
嗯
Yeah.

1658
01:46:05.115 --> 01:46:06.282
霍華
Howard...

1659
01:46:06.866 --> 01:46:08.451
一切都會很順利的
everything's gonna be all right.

1660
01:46:11.454 --> 01:46:12.706
謝謝你…
Thank you...

1661
01:46:13.665 --> 01:46:15.000
所做的一切…
for everything...

1662
01:46:15.417 --> 01:46:17.711
為我們國家效力
you've done for this country.

1663
01:46:20.588 --> 01:46:21.715
老賈
Jarvis.

1664
01:46:25.427 --> 01:46:26.970
我們見過那個人嗎？
Have we ever met that guy?

1665
01:46:28.972 --> 01:46:30.473
您見過很多人，先生
You meet a lot of people, sir.

1666
01:46:33.101 --> 01:46:34.728
看來非常面熟
Seems very familiar.

1667
01:46:35.645 --> 01:46:37.105
奇怪的鬍子
Weird beard.

1668
01:46:45.447 --> 01:46:46.448
妳真弱
You're weak.

1669
01:46:46.990 --> 01:46:48.074
我是妳
I'm you.

1670
01:47:05.717 --> 01:47:07.802
妳可以阻止這件事
You could stop this.

1671
01:47:08.094 --> 01:47:09.888
妳知道妳想阻止它
You know you want to.

1672
01:47:10.597 --> 01:47:12.766
妳看到未來發生的情況了嗎？
Did you see what happens in the future?

1673
01:47:14.059 --> 01:47:16.436
薩諾斯找到靈魂寶石
Thanos finds the Soul Stone.

1674
01:47:17.979 --> 01:47:19.981
想知道他怎麼找到的嗎？
You wanna know how he does that?

1675
01:47:21.358 --> 01:47:25.528
想知道他怎麼對妳的嗎？
You wanna know what he does to you?

1676
01:47:26.029 --> 01:47:27.030
夠了
That's enough.

1677
01:47:39.709 --> 01:47:41.294
妳令我覺得噁心
You disgust me.

1678
01:47:42.587 --> 01:47:47.467
但這不代表妳毫無用處
But that doesn't mean you're useless.

1679
01:48:09.155 --> 01:48:10.865
我看起來如何？
How do I look?

1680
01:48:13.159 --> 01:48:15.704
（佛米爾星，2014年）

1681
01:48:17.455 --> 01:48:18.456
哇
Wow.

1682
01:48:19.457 --> 01:48:22.585
要是情況不同
Under different circumstances...

1683
01:48:22.752 --> 01:48:24.754
這會讓人十分驚豔
this would be totally awesome.

1684
01:48:36.891 --> 01:48:39.728
我敢說那隻浣熊不必爬山
I bet the raccoon didn't have to climb a mountain.

1685
01:48:39.894 --> 01:48:41.813
嚴格說來他不是浣熊
Technically he's not a raccoon, you know?

1686
01:48:41.980 --> 01:48:43.523
隨便，他都吃垃圾
Oh, whatever. He eats garbage.

1687
01:48:43.690 --> 01:48:45.025
歡迎
Welcome.

1688
01:48:48.194 --> 01:48:49.529
娜塔莎
Natasha.

1689
01:48:49.696 --> 01:48:50.697
伊凡之女
Daughter of Ivan.

1690
01:48:52.032 --> 01:48:53.158
克林特
Clint.

1691
01:48:53.324 --> 01:48:55.618
伊蒂絲之子
Son of Edith.

1692
01:49:00.999 --> 01:49:02.459
你是誰？
Who are you?

1693
01:49:03.084 --> 01:49:05.545
就把我當成嚮導…
Consider me a guide...

1694
01:49:05.712 --> 01:49:07.380
帶領你們…
to you...

1695
01:49:07.547 --> 01:49:09.382
以及所有尋找靈魂寶石的人
and to all who seek the Soul Stone.

1696
01:49:09.549 --> 01:49:10.592
很好
Oh, good.

1697
01:49:10.759 --> 01:49:12.886
說出它的下落，我們就啟程
You tell us where it is, then we'll be on our way.

1698
01:49:16.806 --> 01:49:19.059
有那麼簡單就好了
If only it were that easy.

1699
01:49:31.154 --> 01:49:34.866
你們尋找的就在你們眼前
What you seek lies in front of you.

1700
01:49:36.117 --> 01:49:38.536
你們所恐懼的也是
As does what you fear.

1701
01:49:43.458 --> 01:49:45.335
寶石在下面
The stone's down there.

1702
01:49:45.960 --> 01:49:47.879
你們其中一人能帶走
For one of you.

1703
01:49:48.171 --> 01:49:49.881
至於另一個…
For the other...

1704
01:49:52.550 --> 01:49:54.469
若想拿到寶石
In order to take the stone...

1705
01:49:54.636 --> 01:49:57.639
就必須失去所愛
you must lose that which you love.

1706
01:49:59.015 --> 01:50:02.185
一項永恆的交易
An everlasting exchange.

1707
01:50:03.186 --> 01:50:07.273
以靈魂換取靈魂
A soul for a soul.

1708
01:50:09.859 --> 01:50:11.236
你好嗎？
How's it going?

1709
01:50:14.656 --> 01:50:16.074
天啊
Jesus.

1710
01:50:16.408 --> 01:50:18.118
也許他是瞎掰的
Maybe he's making this shit up.

1711
01:50:18.993 --> 01:50:20.328
不
No.

1712
01:50:21.162 --> 01:50:22.163
我覺得不是
I don't think so.

1713
01:50:22.872 --> 01:50:25.041
因為他知道妳爸的名字嗎？
Why? 'Cause he knows your daddy's name?

1714
01:50:26.668 --> 01:50:27.585
我不知道他的名字
I didn't.

1715
01:50:29.087 --> 01:50:31.464
薩諾斯帶走寶石
Thanos left here with the stone...

1716
01:50:32.132 --> 01:50:33.675
卻沒帶女兒走
without his daughter.

1717
01:50:33.842 --> 01:50:35.927
那不是巧合
That's not a coincidence.

1718
01:50:37.012 --> 01:50:38.638
是啊
Yeah.

1719
01:50:40.348 --> 01:50:42.225
不計代價
Whatever it takes.

1720
01:50:46.730 --> 01:50:48.231
不計代價
Whatever it takes.

1721
01:50:52.610 --> 01:50:54.571
如果不拿到那顆寶石
If we don't get that stone...

1722
01:50:54.738 --> 01:50:56.406
數十億人無法起死回生
billions of people stay dead.

1723
01:50:57.282 --> 01:50:58.450
是啊
Yeah.

1724
01:51:00.326 --> 01:51:02.454
我想我們都知道應該是誰
Then I guess we both know who it's gotta be.

1725
01:51:03.204 --> 01:51:04.372
沒錯
I guess we do.

1726
01:51:12.797 --> 01:51:17.510
我開始覺得我們指的是不同人，娜塔莎
I'm starting to think we mean different people here, Natasha.

1727
01:51:18.011 --> 01:51:19.846
五年來，我一直想做一件事
For the last five years, I've been trying to do one thing.

1728
01:51:20.013 --> 01:51:21.264
來到這裡
Get to right here.

1729
01:51:21.431 --> 01:51:23.433
達成目標，將所有人救回來
That's all it's been about. Bringing everybody back.

1730
01:51:23.600 --> 01:51:25.810
不准擺出正義女俠的樣子
No, don't you get all decent on me now.

1731
01:51:25.977 --> 01:51:27.979
你以為我想做嗎？
What, you think I wanna do it?

1732
01:51:28.563 --> 01:51:30.315
我是想救你，白癡
I'm trying to save your life, you idiot.

1733
01:51:30.482 --> 01:51:32.817
我不要妳去，如何？
Yeah, well, I don't want you to. How's that?

1734
01:51:33.735 --> 01:51:35.945
娜塔莎，妳知道我做過什麼
Natasha, you know what I've done.

1735
01:51:37.614 --> 01:51:39.407
妳知道我背負的罪
You know what I've become.

1736
01:51:41.534 --> 01:51:44.120
我不憑別人的大錯來評斷他們
Oh, I don't judge people on their worst mistakes.

1737
01:51:48.291 --> 01:51:49.542
或許妳應該
Maybe you should.

1738
01:51:50.418 --> 01:51:51.961
你就沒有
You didn't.

1739
01:51:58.134 --> 01:52:00.345
妳讓我很傷腦筋，知道嗎？
You're a pain in my ass, you know that?

1740
01:52:11.439 --> 01:52:12.649
好吧
Okay.

1741
01:52:14.401 --> 01:52:15.902
妳贏了
You win.

1742
01:52:22.367 --> 01:52:23.535
告訴我家人我愛他們
Tell my family I love 'em.

1743
01:52:27.247 --> 01:52:28.456
你自己告訴他們
You tell 'em yourself.

1744
01:53:01.322 --> 01:53:02.323
可惡
Damn you.

1745
01:53:09.831 --> 01:53:10.832
等等
Wait.

1746
01:53:18.882 --> 01:53:20.717
放開我
Let me go.

1747
01:53:21.968 --> 01:53:22.969
不
No.

1748
01:53:24.721 --> 01:53:25.722
不，求求妳
No. Please, no.

1749
01:53:29.100 --> 01:53:30.935
沒關係
It's okay.

1750
01:53:33.146 --> 01:53:33.980
求求妳
Please.

1751
01:53:36.066 --> 01:53:37.067
不！
No!

1752
01:55:18.543 --> 01:55:19.544
全都拿到了嗎？
Did we get 'em all?

1753
01:55:20.962 --> 01:55:22.756
你是說真的成功了？
Are you telling me this actually worked?

1754
01:55:27.594 --> 01:55:28.803
克林特，小娜呢？
Clint, where's Nat?

1755
01:55:58.041 --> 01:55:59.042
她有家人嗎？
Do we know if she had family?

1756
01:56:00.210 --> 01:56:01.378
有
Yeah.

1757
01:56:01.544 --> 01:56:02.545
我們
Us.

1758
01:56:03.963 --> 01:56:05.006
怎麼了？
What?

1759
01:56:06.966 --> 01:56:08.134
-你在幹嘛？ -問他問題
Huh? - What are you doing? - Just asked him a question.

1760
01:56:08.301 --> 01:56:09.552
你一副她死了的樣子
Yeah, no, you're acting like she's dead.

1761
01:56:09.719 --> 01:56:12.180
何必如喪考妣？我們有寶石啊
Why are we acting like she's dead? We have the stones, right?

1762
01:56:12.347 --> 01:56:13.348
只要我們有寶石…
As long as we have the stones...

1763
01:56:13.515 --> 01:56:15.266
就能救她回來，不是嗎？
Cap, we can bring her back. Isn't that right?

1764
01:56:15.433 --> 01:56:17.435
別這樣，我們是復仇者聯盟，振作
So, stop this shit. We're the Avengers. Get it together.

1765
01:56:17.602 --> 01:56:18.812
我們不能救她回來
Can't get her back.

1766
01:56:21.815 --> 01:56:23.066
什麼？
What's he...? What?

1767
01:56:23.233 --> 01:56:24.442
那無法逆轉
It can't be undone.

1768
01:56:25.026 --> 01:56:26.736
沒辦法
It can't.

1769
01:56:29.239 --> 01:56:32.367
抱歉，恕我直說，你是凡人
Look, I'm sorry, no offence, but you're a very earthly being, okay?

1770
01:56:32.534 --> 01:56:33.827
我們說的是太空魔法
And we're talking about space magic.

1771
01:56:33.993 --> 01:56:35.995
講"無法"好像太鐵齒了
And "can't" seems very definitive. Don't you think?

1772
01:56:36.162 --> 01:56:38.998
我知道我層次不夠高
Yeah, look, I know that I'm way outside my pay grade here.

1773
01:56:39.165 --> 01:56:40.625
但她還是不在這裡
But she still isn't here, is she?

1774
01:56:40.792 --> 01:56:41.793
這就是我要講的
No, that's my point.

1775
01:56:41.960 --> 01:56:44.921
它無法逆轉
It can't be undone.

1776
01:56:45.088 --> 01:56:48.425
至少那個紅色漂浮人是這麼說的
Or that's at least what the red, floating guy had to say.

1777
01:56:48.591 --> 01:56:50.051
你可以去找他談
Maybe you wanna go talk to him, okay?

1778
01:56:50.218 --> 01:56:53.263
拿你的鎚子飛去找他談
Go grab your hammer and you go fly and you talk to him.

1779
01:57:01.813 --> 01:57:03.857
原本應該是我
It was supposed to be me.

1780
01:57:06.109 --> 01:57:08.403
她為那顆寶石犧牲生命
She sacrificed her life for that goddamn stone.

1781
01:57:08.570 --> 01:57:10.030
她賭上自己的命
She bet her life on it.

1782
01:57:14.951 --> 01:57:17.287
她不會回來了
She's not coming back.

1783
01:57:19.080 --> 01:57:20.623
我們得讓她犧牲得有價值
We have to make it worth it.

1784
01:57:21.124 --> 01:57:22.584
重如泰山
We have to.

1785
01:57:24.002 --> 01:57:25.670
我們會的
We will.

1786
01:57:50.362 --> 01:57:51.488
砰！
Boom!

1787
01:57:57.160 --> 01:57:58.620
手套準備好了
All right, the glove's ready.

1788
01:57:59.412 --> 01:58:01.998
問題是誰來彈指？
Question is, who's gonna snap their freakin' fingers?

1789
01:58:02.165 --> 01:58:04.250
-我來 -什麼？
- I'll do it. - Excuse me?

1790
01:58:04.417 --> 01:58:05.377
沒關係
It's okay.

1791
01:58:05.543 --> 01:58:06.461
別急
Stop, stop. Slow down.

1792
01:58:06.628 --> 01:58:08.129
索爾，等一下
Thor. Just wait.

1793
01:58:08.296 --> 01:58:10.131
我們還沒決定誰戴手套
We haven't decided who's gonna put that on yet.

1794
01:58:10.507 --> 01:58:13.426
抱歉，我們還要坐等適當時機嗎？
I'm sorry. What, we're all just sitting around waiting for the right opportunity?

1795
01:58:13.593 --> 01:58:14.719
至少應該討論一下
We should at least discuss it.

1796
01:58:14.886 --> 01:58:18.723
盯著那東西看不能救所有人回來
Look, sitting here staring at the thing is not gonna bring everybody back.

1797
01:58:19.766 --> 01:58:22.686
我是最強的復仇者，就該擔起責任
I'm the strongest Avenger, okay? So, this responsibility falls upon me.

1798
01:58:22.852 --> 01:58:24.062
-平常是那樣沒錯 -我的責任
- Normally, you're right. - It's my duty.

1799
01:58:24.229 --> 01:58:26.022
-重點不在那 -不是那樣
- It's not about that. - It's not that.

1800
01:58:26.189 --> 01:58:27.982
-兄弟 -閉嘴！讓我來
- Hey, buddy... - Stop it! Just let me.

1801
01:58:30.985 --> 01:58:32.487
讓我來
Just let me do it.

1802
01:58:32.654 --> 01:58:35.156
讓我做件好事，對的事
Just let me do something good. Something right.

1803
01:58:35.323 --> 01:58:36.324
這手套發出的能量
Look, it's not just the fact...

1804
01:58:36.491 --> 01:58:38.618
不僅足以供電給整座大陸
that that glove is channeling enough energy to light up a continent.

1805
01:58:38.785 --> 01:58:40.787
你的狀況也不理想
I'm telling you. You're in no condition.

1806
01:58:40.954 --> 01:58:43.998
你想我血管裡現在流著什麼？
What do you think is coursing through my veins right now?

1807
01:58:44.165 --> 01:58:45.208
起司醬？
Cheez Whiz?

1808
01:58:47.752 --> 01:58:48.753
閃電
Lightning.

1809
01:58:48.920 --> 01:58:50.046
-對 -閃電
Yeah. Lightning.

1810
01:58:50.213 --> 01:58:51.589
閃電幫不了你，兄弟
Lightning won't help you, pal.

1811
01:58:51.756 --> 01:58:53.591
應該是我
It's gotta be me.

1812
01:58:54.926 --> 01:58:57.095
你們看到哪些寶石對薩諾斯的影響
You saw what those stones did to Thanos.

1813
01:58:57.262 --> 01:58:58.805
它們差點殺死他
They almost killed him.

1814
01:59:00.223 --> 01:59:02.100
你們都無法存活
None of you could survive.

1815
01:59:02.809 --> 01:59:04.436
我們怎麼知道你可以？
How do we know you will?

1816
01:59:04.602 --> 01:59:05.645
不知道
We don't.

1817
01:59:05.937 --> 01:59:08.481
但那輻射主要是伽瑪
But the radiation's mostly gamma.

1818
01:59:11.985 --> 01:59:13.570
看來…
It's like...

1819
01:59:15.447 --> 01:59:17.365
我就是最佳人選
I was made for this.

1820
01:59:36.301 --> 01:59:37.802
可以了嗎？
Good to go, yeah?

1821
01:59:39.929 --> 01:59:40.930
動手吧
Let's do it.

1822
01:59:41.097 --> 01:59:44.142
記住，薩諾斯五年前殺害的所有人
Okay, remember, everyone Thanos snapped away five years ago...

1823
01:59:44.309 --> 01:59:46.770
你只能將他們帶回到今天
you're just bringing them back to now, today.

1824
01:59:46.936 --> 01:59:48.355
別改變過去五年的任何事
Don't change anything from the last five years.

1825
01:59:49.773 --> 01:59:50.940
瞭解
Got it.

1826
02:00:07.332 --> 02:00:10.126
星期五，幫我啟動穀倉門協定
Friday, do me a favour and activate Barn Door Protocol, will ya?

1827
02:00:10.293 --> 02:00:11.586
是，老闆
Yes, boss.

1828
02:00:20.178 --> 02:00:22.013
大家回來吧
Everybody comes home.

1829
02:00:45.412 --> 02:00:46.830
脫掉…
Take it off! Take it off!

1830
02:00:46.996 --> 02:00:48.123
等等，布魯斯，你還好嗎？
No, wait. Bruce, are you okay?

1831
02:00:49.290 --> 02:00:50.500
說話，班納
Talk to me, Banner.

1832
02:00:53.670 --> 02:00:54.671
我沒事
I'm okay.

1833
02:00:55.171 --> 02:00:56.464
我沒事
I'm okay.

1834
02:01:01.261 --> 02:01:02.303
（入口開啟，原點2014年）

1835
02:01:27.912 --> 02:01:29.039
布魯斯
Bruce!

1836
02:01:30.790 --> 02:01:32.375
別動他
Don't move him.

1837
02:01:39.257 --> 02:01:41.259
-成功了嗎？ -不確定，沒關係
- Did it work? - We're not sure. It's okay.

1838
02:02:15.585 --> 02:02:19.839
（蘿拉）

1839
02:02:27.764 --> 02:02:28.640
親愛的

1840
02:02:28.807 --> 02:02:29.766
克林特？
Honey. Clint?

1841
02:02:29.933 --> 02:02:31.184
親愛的
Honey.

1842
02:02:32.018 --> 02:02:33.353
大夥
Guys...

1843
02:02:35.814 --> 02:02:37.190
我想成功了
I think it worked.

1844
02:03:19.816 --> 02:03:21.693
我不能呼吸…
I can't breathe! I can't breathe!

1845
02:03:22.944 --> 02:03:24.738
頭罩…
Canopy, canopy, canopy.

1846
02:03:31.369 --> 02:03:33.163
羅德、火箭，快離開
Rhodey, Rocket, get out of here.

1847
02:03:34.330 --> 02:03:35.874
讓我上去…
Let me up! Let me up!

1848
02:03:36.624 --> 02:03:37.375
快啊！
Come on!

1849
02:03:47.510 --> 02:03:48.345
羅德
Rhodey!

1850
02:03:50.605 --> 02:03:51.905
Huh?

1851
02:03:56.895 --> 02:03:59.939
求救…有人收到嗎？我們在下層，淹水了
Mayday, Mayday! Does anybody copy? We're on the lower level. It's flooding!

1852
02:04:00.106 --> 02:04:01.816
什麼？
What? What?

1853
02:04:01.983 --> 02:04:04.152
我們溺水了，有人收到嗎？求救
We are drowning! Does anybody copy? Mayday!

1854
02:04:04.319 --> 02:04:06.488
等等，我在
Wait! I'm here!

1855
02:04:06.654 --> 02:04:08.156
我在，聽到了嗎？
I'm here. Can you hear me?

1856
02:04:27.801 --> 02:04:29.010
隊長？
Cap?

1857
02:04:52.992 --> 02:04:54.119
好
Okay.

1858
02:05:13.388 --> 02:05:14.514
女兒
Daughter.

1859
02:05:14.681 --> 02:05:15.849
是，父親
Yes, Father.

1860
02:05:17.726 --> 02:05:19.436
所以這就是未來
So, this is the future.

1861
02:05:20.103 --> 02:05:20.937
幹得好
Well done.

1862
02:05:21.855 --> 02:05:23.356
謝謝父親
Thank you, Father.

1863
02:05:23.523 --> 02:05:24.899
他們完全沒起疑
They suspected nothing.

1864
02:05:27.235 --> 02:05:28.695
傲慢者從不起疑
The arrogant never do.

1865
02:05:31.656 --> 02:05:32.782
去吧
Go.

1866
02:05:33.742 --> 02:05:36.161
去找寶石，拿來給我
Find the stones, bring them to me.

1867
02:05:36.327 --> 02:05:38.038
你會怎麼做？
What will you do?

1868
02:05:39.372 --> 02:05:41.041
等待
Wait.

1869
02:06:06.274 --> 02:06:07.942
告訴我一件事
Tell me something.

1870
02:06:09.069 --> 02:06:11.488
在未來…
In the future...

1871
02:06:11.654 --> 02:06:13.531
妳和我會怎麼樣？
what happens to you and me?

1872
02:06:15.825 --> 02:06:17.452
我企圖殺妳
I try to kill you.

1873
02:06:19.162 --> 02:06:20.663
好幾次
Several times.

1874
02:06:21.748 --> 02:06:23.708
但最後…
But eventually...

1875
02:06:23.875 --> 02:06:25.835
我們成為朋友
we become friends.

1876
02:06:27.337 --> 02:06:29.047
成為姊妹
We become sisters.

1877
02:06:36.721 --> 02:06:37.931
走吧
Come on.

1878
02:06:39.974 --> 02:06:41.768
我們能阻止他
We can stop him.

1879
02:06:49.859 --> 02:06:51.194
快醒醒
Come on, buddy, wake up!

1880
02:06:51.736 --> 02:06:53.196
這才對
That's my man.

1881
02:06:54.114 --> 02:06:56.157
你又弄丟了這個，我留著
You lose this again, I'm keeping it.

1882
02:06:59.703 --> 02:07:00.870
怎麼回事？
What happened?

1883
02:07:01.037 --> 02:07:03.164
改變時間往往會造成問題
You mess with time, it tends to mess back.

1884
02:07:03.331 --> 02:07:04.207
等會就知道
You'll see.

1885
02:07:26.312 --> 02:07:27.689
他在做什麼？
What's he been doing?

1886
02:07:29.607 --> 02:07:31.026
什麼都沒做
Absolutely nothing.

1887
02:07:32.777 --> 02:07:34.654
無限寶石呢？
Where are the stones?

1888
02:07:35.030 --> 02:07:36.865
在這片瓦礫堆底下
Somewhere under all this.

1889
02:07:38.241 --> 02:07:40.452
我只知道不在他手中
All I know is he doesn't have 'em.

1890
02:07:40.618 --> 02:07:42.370
那就保持下去
So, we keep it that way.

1891
02:07:42.537 --> 02:07:43.913
你們知道這是陷阱吧？
You know it's a trap, right?

1892
02:07:44.080 --> 02:07:45.415
是啊
Yeah.

1893
02:07:45.582 --> 02:07:46.916
管不了那麼多
I don't much care.

1894
02:07:47.667 --> 02:07:48.668
很好
Good.

1895
02:07:49.627 --> 02:07:52.130
只要我們有共識就好
Just as long as we're all in agreement.

1896
02:08:01.890 --> 02:08:03.892
這次讓他死得痛快
Let's kill him properly this time.

1897
02:08:13.276 --> 02:08:16.196
你們無法受失敗
You could not live with your own failure.

1898
02:08:17.697 --> 02:08:19.532
結果是什麼？
Where did that bring you?

1899
02:08:22.494 --> 02:08:24.371
再和我決一死戰
Back to me.

1900
02:08:27.791 --> 02:08:30.627
我以為殲滅半數生命
I thought by eliminating half of life...

1901
02:08:31.378 --> 02:08:33.755
另一半會成長茁壯
the other half would thrive.

1902
02:08:33.922 --> 02:08:35.256
但你們讓我看到…
But you've shown me...

1903
02:08:36.424 --> 02:08:38.176
那是不可能的
that's impossible.

1904
02:08:40.095 --> 02:08:43.390
只要有人記得昔日的榮景
And as long as there are those that remember what was...

1905
02:08:43.556 --> 02:08:48.770
就必定有人無法接受現實
there will always be those that are unable to accept what can be.

1906
02:08:49.521 --> 02:08:50.772
他們會反抗
They will resist.

1907
02:08:51.272 --> 02:08:53.191
對，我們就是那麼頑強
Yep, we're all kinds of stubborn.

1908
02:08:54.109 --> 02:08:55.694
我很感恩
I'm thankful.

1909
02:08:57.862 --> 02:08:59.614
因為現在…
Because now...

1910
02:08:59.781 --> 02:09:01.908
我知道自己該怎麼做
I know what I must do.

1911
02:09:02.367 --> 02:09:05.328
我將瓦解這宇宙
I will shred this universe...

1912
02:09:05.495 --> 02:09:07.539
消滅到最後一個原子不剩
down to its last atom.

1913
02:09:08.331 --> 02:09:10.000
然後
And then...

1914
02:09:10.166 --> 02:09:12.502
靠你們幫我蒐集來的寶石
with the stones you've collected for me...

1915
02:09:13.294 --> 02:09:15.422
創造一個新宇宙
create a new one...

1916
02:09:15.588 --> 02:09:17.799
充滿生命
teeming with life...

1917
02:09:17.966 --> 02:09:19.843
它知道的不是失去什麼
that knows not what it has lost...

1918
02:09:20.010 --> 02:09:22.387
而是獲得什麼
but only what it has been given.

1919
02:09:25.473 --> 02:09:26.891
一個懂得感恩的宇宙
A grateful universe.

1920
02:09:27.434 --> 02:09:28.852
從鮮血中誕生
Born out of blood.

1921
02:09:29.019 --> 02:09:30.687
他們永遠不會知道
They'll never know it.

1922
02:09:31.896 --> 02:09:34.816
因為你們不會活著告訴他們
Because you won't be alive to tell them.

1923
02:09:49.414 --> 02:09:50.707
另一個世界見了
See you on the other side, man.

1924
02:09:53.043 --> 02:09:55.045
等等，我來了
Hang on! I'm coming!

1925
02:10:25.325 --> 02:10:26.326
耶！
Yeah!

1926
02:10:41.216 --> 02:10:42.759
嗨
Oh, hey.

1927
02:10:42.926 --> 02:10:44.636
我認識妳
I know you.

1928
02:10:47.555 --> 02:10:48.556
父親
Father...

1929
02:10:49.307 --> 02:10:50.725
寶石到手了
I have the stones.

1930
02:10:50.892 --> 02:10:51.810
什麼？
What?

1931
02:10:53.186 --> 02:10:54.104
住手
Stop.

1932
02:10:59.317 --> 02:11:00.735
妳背叛我們？
You're betraying us?

1933
02:11:06.741 --> 02:11:08.034
妳不必這麼做
You don't have to do this.

1934
02:11:10.870 --> 02:11:13.373
這是我的天命
I am this.

1935
02:11:13.540 --> 02:11:15.458
不，並不是
No, you're not.

1936
02:11:15.917 --> 02:11:17.794
妳見過我們未來的下場
You've seen what we become.

1937
02:11:23.883 --> 02:11:26.094
涅布拉，聽她的話
Nebula, listen to her.

1938
02:11:27.554 --> 02:11:28.430
妳能改變
You can change.

1939
02:11:35.103 --> 02:11:36.604
他不會讓我改變的
He won't let me.

1940
02:11:38.231 --> 02:11:38.982
不！
No!

1941
02:11:58.626 --> 02:12:00.003
索爾，打我
Okay, Thor. Hit me.

1942
02:12:16.644 --> 02:12:17.937
老闆，醒醒！
Boss, wake up!

1943
02:13:09.239 --> 02:13:10.532
我就知道
I knew it!

1944
02:14:32.906 --> 02:14:35.742
我多年來的征戰
In all my years of conquest...

1945
02:14:37.035 --> 02:14:38.787
暴力
violence...

1946
02:14:39.829 --> 02:14:41.790
屠殺
slaughter...

1947
02:14:42.916 --> 02:14:45.335
向來不為一己之私
it was never personal.

1948
02:14:47.921 --> 02:14:50.006
但我現在告訴你
But I'll tell you now...

1949
02:14:52.008 --> 02:14:58.264
當對付你那頑固惱人的小星球時
what I'm about to do to your stubborn, annoying little planet...

1950
02:15:00.016 --> 02:15:02.227
我會非常非常…
I'm gonna enjoy it...

1951
02:15:03.144 --> 02:15:05.730
樂在其中
very, very much.

1952
02:16:09.002 --> 02:16:10.545
隊長，聽到了嗎？
Hey, Cap, you read me?

1953
02:16:16.551 --> 02:16:18.845
隊長，我山姆，聽到了嗎？
Cap, it's Sam. Can you hear me?

1954
02:16:22.849 --> 02:16:24.267
在你左邊
On your left.

1955
02:17:49.936 --> 02:17:51.229
大家都到了嗎？
Is that everyone?

1956
02:17:51.396 --> 02:17:53.606
你還嫌不夠嗎？
What? You wanted more?

1957
02:18:20.133 --> 02:18:22.093
復仇者聯盟…
Avengers...

1958
02:18:27.223 --> 02:18:28.308
集結
assemble.

1959
02:19:03.510 --> 02:19:04.761
去死吧！
Die!

1960
02:19:25.407 --> 02:19:28.159
不，給我，你拿小的
No, no, give me that. You have the little one.

1961
02:19:41.840 --> 02:19:42.674
喂！
Hey!

1962
02:19:43.675 --> 02:19:44.676
哇靠
Holy cow!

1963
02:19:44.843 --> 02:19:46.219
你不會相信發生了什麼事
You will not believe what's been going on.

1964
02:19:46.302 --> 02:19:47.512
記得我們在太空中嗎？
Do you remember when we were in space?

1965
02:19:47.679 --> 02:19:49.055
我變成灰燼？
And I got all dusty?

1966
02:19:49.222 --> 02:19:51.891
我一定昏倒了，醒來後你就不見了
And I must've passed out, because I woke up and you were gone.

1967
02:19:52.058 --> 02:19:53.685
奇異博士在那邊，他說…
But Doctor Strange was there, right? And he was like...

1968
02:19:53.852 --> 02:19:55.353
"五年了，快，他們需要我們"
"It's been five years. Come on, they need us."

1969
02:19:55.520 --> 02:19:57.188
然後開始像平常那樣畫火圈
And then he started doing the yellow sparkly thing that he does all the time.

1970
02:19:57.355 --> 02:19:58.189
是嗎？不
He did? Oh, no.

1971
02:19:58.356 --> 02:19:59.649
你幹嘛？
What are you doing? - Oh.

1972
02:20:04.696 --> 02:20:06.197
感覺好溫馨
Oh, this is nice.

1973
02:20:27.969 --> 02:20:28.970
葛摩菈？
Gamora?

1974
02:20:38.396 --> 02:20:40.065
我以為我失去妳了
I thought I lost you.

1975
02:20:44.652 --> 02:20:47.572
不要…碰…我
Ow. Don't touch me!

1976
02:20:50.575 --> 02:20:52.410
妳第一次沒踢中
You missed the first time.

1977
02:20:52.577 --> 02:20:54.579
第二次兩顆都中
Then you got 'em both the second time.

1978
02:20:56.581 --> 02:20:57.665
就是這個？
This is the one?

1979
02:20:57.832 --> 02:20:58.833
真假？
Seriously?

1980
02:20:59.000 --> 02:21:01.002
妳只能挑他或一棵樹
Your choices were him or a tree.

1981
02:21:11.805 --> 02:21:12.806
隊長
Cap!

1982
02:21:12.972 --> 02:21:14.724
你要我拿這玩意做什麼？
What do you want me to do with this damn thing?

1983
02:21:17.435 --> 02:21:19.479
把寶石拿得越遠越好
Get those stones as far away as possible!

1984
02:21:19.646 --> 02:21:20.689
不！
No!

1985
02:21:21.856 --> 02:21:23.817
我們得將它們送回原處
We need to get 'em back where they came from.

1986
02:21:23.983 --> 02:21:26.569
沒辦法，薩諾斯摧毀了量子隧道
No way to get 'em back. Thanos destroyed the quantum tunnel.

1987
02:21:26.736 --> 02:21:27.570
等一下
Hold on!

1988
02:21:29.447 --> 02:21:31.574
那不是我們唯一的時間機器
That wasn't our only time machine.

1989
02:21:37.580 --> 02:21:39.499
有人看到很醜的棕色廂型車嗎？
Anyone see an ugly brown van out there?

1990
02:21:40.041 --> 02:21:43.128
有！你不會喜歡它停的地方
Yes! But you're not gonna like where it's parked!

1991
02:21:43.294 --> 02:21:45.422
史考特，讓那玩意發揮作用要多久？
Scott, how long you need to get that thing working?

1992
02:21:46.798 --> 02:21:47.799
大約十分鐘
Uh, maybe 10 minutes.

1993
02:21:47.966 --> 02:21:49.467
開始發動，我們拿寶石給你
Get it started. We'll get the stones to you.

1994
02:21:49.634 --> 02:21:51.177
馬上辦，隊長
We're on it, Cap.

1995
02:22:00.937 --> 02:22:02.063
嘿
Hey.

1996
02:22:02.230 --> 02:22:05.233
你說我們勝率一千四百萬分之一？
You said one out of 14 million, we win, yeah?

1997
02:22:06.151 --> 02:22:07.152
告訴我就是這次
Tell me this is it.

1998
02:22:07.569 --> 02:22:09.446
如果我告訴你會發生什麼事
If I tell you what happens...

1999
02:22:09.612 --> 02:22:10.780
它就不會發生
it won't happen.

2000
02:22:14.367 --> 02:22:15.368
你最好是對的
You better be right.

2001
02:22:23.793 --> 02:22:25.170
這裡好混亂
It's a mess back here.

2002
02:22:26.171 --> 02:22:27.172
車子掛了
It's dead.

2003
02:22:28.465 --> 02:22:29.966
-什麼？ -拋錨
- What? - It's dead.

2004
02:22:30.133 --> 02:22:31.551
我得接電熱線發動
I have to hot-wire it.

2005
02:22:34.637 --> 02:22:35.847
涅布拉呢？
Where's Nebula?

2006
02:22:36.973 --> 02:22:38.308
她沒回應
She's not responding.

2007
02:22:38.683 --> 02:22:40.018
老大
Sire...

2008
02:22:49.778 --> 02:22:51.029
克林特
Clint!

2009
02:22:53.073 --> 02:22:54.199
交給我
Give it to me.

2010
02:23:16.471 --> 02:23:19.849
你奪走了我的一切
You took everything from me.

2011
02:23:20.225 --> 02:23:22.560
我根本不知道妳是哪根蔥
I don't even know who you are.

2012
02:23:22.727 --> 02:23:24.354
你會知道的
You will.

2013
02:23:46.793 --> 02:23:47.752
交給我
I got it!

2014
02:23:50.296 --> 02:23:51.381
啟動速殺模式
Activate Instant Kill.

2015
02:24:14.821 --> 02:24:16.156
空中掃射！
Rain fire!

2016
02:24:16.865 --> 02:24:18.783
但老大，我們的部隊
But, sire, our troops!

2017
02:24:18.950 --> 02:24:20.702
快點！
Just do it!

2018
02:24:40.847 --> 02:24:43.224
有人看到這個嗎？
Uh, is anyone else seeing this?

2019
02:24:57.155 --> 02:24:58.281
讓我來
I got this!

2020
02:24:58.531 --> 02:25:00.325
我來…我不行
I got this. Okay, I don't got this.

2021
02:25:00.658 --> 02:25:01.826
救命啊，快救命啊
Help, somebody help!

2022
02:25:01.993 --> 02:25:03.870
皇后區小子，注意
Hey, Queens, heads up!

2023
02:25:13.922 --> 02:25:14.964
等一下，我來救你
Hang on. I got you, kid.

2024
02:25:18.593 --> 02:25:19.761
很高興認識妳
Hey! Nice to meet you...

2025
02:25:19.928 --> 02:25:21.763
歐買尬！
Oh, my God!

2026
02:25:58.008 --> 02:25:59.467
這是甚麼啊？
What the hell is this?

2027
02:26:00.260 --> 02:26:01.344
星期五，他們在射什麼？
Friday, what are they firing at?

2028
02:26:01.511 --> 02:26:03.388
有東西進入高層大氣
Something just entered the upper atmosphere.

2029
02:26:16.651 --> 02:26:18.820
帥啦！
Oh, yeah!

2030
02:26:38.715 --> 02:26:41.134
丹佛斯，這裡需要協助
Danvers, we need an assist here.

2031
02:26:49.893 --> 02:26:52.479
妳好，我是彼得帕克
Hi, I'm Peter Parker.

2032
02:26:53.104 --> 02:26:54.522
嗨，彼得帕克
Hey, Peter Parker.

2033
02:26:54.689 --> 02:26:55.857
有東西要給我嗎？
You got something for me?

2034
02:27:01.988 --> 02:27:04.074
我不知道妳要如何對付他們
I don't know how you're gonna get it through all of that.

2035
02:27:05.742 --> 02:27:07.160
別擔心
Don't worry.

2036
02:27:08.036 --> 02:27:09.621
她有幫手
She's got help.

2037
02:29:57.455 --> 02:30:00.959
我是無可匹敵的
I am inevitable.

2038
02:30:21.062 --> 02:30:22.605
我…
And I...

2039
02:30:24.274 --> 02:30:25.442
是…
am...

2040
02:30:29.154 --> 02:30:30.655
鋼鐵人
Iron Man.

2041
02:32:29.357 --> 02:32:31.067
史塔克先生
Mr. Stark?

2042
02:32:31.484 --> 02:32:32.736
嘿
Hey!

2043
02:32:33.737 --> 02:32:36.698
史塔克先生，聽得見嗎？
Mr. Stark. Can you hear me?

2044
02:32:36.865 --> 02:32:38.408
我是彼得
It's Peter.

2045
02:32:39.701 --> 02:32:41.327
嗨
Hey.

2046
02:32:42.370 --> 02:32:45.415
我們贏了，史塔克先生
We won, Mr. Stark.

2047
02:32:47.250 --> 02:32:49.419
我們贏了，史塔克先生
We won, Mr. Stark.

2048
02:32:51.046 --> 02:32:53.882
我們贏了，你成功了…
We won! You did it, sir, you did it.

2049
02:32:54.799 --> 02:32:56.092
對不起
I'm sorry.

2050
02:32:56.259 --> 02:32:57.260
東尼
Tony.

2051
02:33:10.940 --> 02:33:11.983
嗨
Hey.

2052
02:33:12.150 --> 02:33:13.985
小辣椒
Hey, Pep.

2053
02:33:18.281 --> 02:33:19.366
星期五？
Friday?

2054
02:33:19.532 --> 02:33:22.285
生命功能危急
Life functions critical.

2055
02:33:30.877 --> 02:33:31.878
東尼
Tony?

2056
02:33:33.129 --> 02:33:34.214
看著我
Look at me.

2057
02:33:36.883 --> 02:33:38.802
我們會好好的
We're gonna be okay.

2058
02:33:43.515 --> 02:33:45.392
你可以休息了
You can rest now.

2059
02:35:30.914 --> 02:35:33.708
大家都要快樂結局，對吧？
Everybody wants a happy ending, right?

2060
02:35:33.875 --> 02:35:36.086
但不見得總能如願
But it doesn't always roll that way.

2061
02:35:38.171 --> 02:35:39.839
或許這次可以
Maybe this time.

2062
02:35:41.424 --> 02:35:44.094
我希望如果妳播放這影片
I'm hoping if you play this back...

2063
02:35:45.762 --> 02:35:47.097
是為了慶祝
it's in celebration.

2064
02:35:48.348 --> 02:35:52.018
我希望家人團聚，我們恢復生機
I hope families are reunited. I hope we get it back.

2065
02:35:52.185 --> 02:35:56.106
地球已經回復正常了
And something like a normal version of the planet has been restored.

2066
02:35:56.272 --> 02:35:58.233
如果真有所謂正常的地球
If there ever was such a thing.

2067
02:35:58.817 --> 02:36:01.820
天啊，我們的世界已是整個宇宙了
God, what a world. Universe, now.

2068
02:36:02.779 --> 02:36:04.781
如果十年前妳說人類並不孤單
If you told me 10 years ago that we weren't alone...

2069
02:36:04.948 --> 02:36:08.618
更別說到這程度，我並不會驚訝
let alone to this extent, I mean, I wouldn't have been surprised...

2070
02:36:08.785 --> 02:36:10.412
但拜託，誰曉得是這樣？
but come on, who knew?

2071
02:36:10.578 --> 02:36:15.208
光明與黑暗的驚人力量已發揮作用
The epic forces of darkness and light that have come into play.

2072
02:36:15.375 --> 02:36:17.085
無論如何
And for better or worse...

2073
02:36:17.252 --> 02:36:21.423
那是摩根在成長時必須面對的現實
that's the reality Morgan's gonna have to find a way to grow up in.

2074
02:36:24.676 --> 02:36:26.469
所以我想最好錄一小段祝福
So, I thought I'd probably better record a little greeting...

2075
02:36:26.636 --> 02:36:30.265
以防萬一我提早掛掉
in the case of an untimely death. On my part.

2076
02:36:30.432 --> 02:36:33.685
雖然任何時候掛掉都不是好時機
Not that death at any time isn't untimely.

2077
02:36:34.894 --> 02:36:37.939
我們明天想嘗試的時間旅行
This time travel thing that we're gonna try and pull off tomorrow...

2078
02:36:38.106 --> 02:36:40.316
能否存活下來仍在未定之天
it's got me scratching my head about the survivability of it all.

2079
02:36:40.483 --> 02:36:41.943
就是這事
That's the thing.

2080
02:36:43.903 --> 02:36:45.822
話說回來，這是超級英雄的職責
Then again, that's the hero gig, right?

2081
02:36:45.989 --> 02:36:47.073
終點是旅程的一部分
Part of the journey is the end.

2082
02:36:49.075 --> 02:36:50.076
我何必緊張？
What am I even tripping for?

2083
02:36:50.243 --> 02:36:54.330
一切都會照計畫進行
Everything is gonna work out exactly the way it's supposed to.

2084
02:36:57.834 --> 02:36:59.502
我愛妳三千次
I love you 3,000.

2085
02:37:19.606 --> 02:37:24.611
（東尼史塔克有心臟的證據）

2086
02:39:14.429 --> 02:39:18.183
真希望我有辦法讓她知道
You know, I wish there was a way that I could let her know.

2087
02:39:20.685 --> 02:39:22.812
我們贏了
That we won.

2088
02:39:24.189 --> 02:39:25.899
我們成功了
We did it.

2089
02:39:29.486 --> 02:39:31.279
她知道
She knows.

2090
02:39:36.159 --> 02:39:38.244
他們倆都知道
They both do.

2091
02:39:47.212 --> 02:39:48.296
妳還好嗎，小可愛？
How you doing, squirt?

2092
02:39:48.463 --> 02:39:49.464
很好
Good.

2093
02:39:49.631 --> 02:39:50.965
-很好？ -嗯
- You good? - Mm-hmm.

2094
02:39:51.132 --> 02:39:53.843
-肚子餓嗎？ -嗯
- Good. You hungry? - Mm-hmm.

2095
02:39:54.260 --> 02:39:55.261
想吃什麼？
What do you want?

2096
02:39:55.970 --> 02:39:57.389
起司漢堡
Cheeseburgers.

2097
02:40:02.185 --> 02:40:04.437
妳爸也愛吃起司漢堡
You know, your dad liked cheeseburgers.

2098
02:40:04.604 --> 02:40:06.022
喔
Okay.

2099
02:40:08.608 --> 02:40:10.860
想吃多少起司漢堡我都買給妳
I'm gonna get you all the cheeseburgers you want.

2100
02:40:11.027 --> 02:40:12.028
好
Okay.

2101
02:40:28.795 --> 02:40:30.213
那麼…
So...

2102
02:40:30.463 --> 02:40:32.632
你何時要回來？
when can we expect you back?

2103
02:40:34.718 --> 02:40:36.052
關於這一點…
Um, about that...

2104
02:40:36.302 --> 02:40:38.471
索爾，你的人民需要國王
Thor, your people need a king.

2105
02:40:38.638 --> 02:40:40.515
不，他們已經有一個了
No, they already have one.

2106
02:40:42.642 --> 02:40:43.643
真好笑
That's funny.

2107
02:40:49.232 --> 02:40:51.067
你是認真的嗎？
Are you being serious?

2108
02:40:54.738 --> 02:40:56.990
我該做真正的自己了
It's time for me to be who I am...

2109
02:40:57.574 --> 02:41:00.160
而非做我該做的那個人
rather than who I'm supposed to be.

2110
02:41:01.453 --> 02:41:03.204
但妳是領袖
But you, you're a leader.

2111
02:41:03.830 --> 02:41:05.540
優秀而稱職
That's who you are.

2112
02:41:08.043 --> 02:41:10.003
我會讓這裡改頭換面
You know, I'd make a lot of changes around here.

2113
02:41:10.170 --> 02:41:11.671
我滿心期待
I'm counting on it...

2114
02:41:11.838 --> 02:41:13.340
陛下
Your Majesty.

2115
02:41:23.475 --> 02:41:24.684
你有什麼打算？
What will you do?

2116
02:41:25.435 --> 02:41:26.853
還不確定
I'm not sure.

2117
02:41:27.020 --> 02:41:30.565
千年來我第一次沒有方向
For the first time in a thousand years,

2118
02:41:30.732 --> 02:41:32.150
不過我能搭便車
I have no path. I do have a ride though.

2119
02:41:32.317 --> 02:41:34.277
動作快，乞幫幫主
Move it or lose it, hairbag.

2120
02:41:35.862 --> 02:41:38.615
（搜尋中）

2121
02:41:38.782 --> 02:41:40.325
到了
Oh, here we are!

2122
02:41:40.784 --> 02:41:42.327
樹仔，真高興見到你
Tree, good to see you.

2123
02:41:46.915 --> 02:41:50.210
阿斯嘉星際異攻隊再度合體
The Asgardians of the Galaxy back together again.

2124
02:41:50.627 --> 02:41:52.504
先去哪裡？
Where to first?

2125
02:41:53.630 --> 02:41:54.673
嘿
Hey.

2126
02:41:55.298 --> 02:41:57.258
別忘了，這還是我的船
Just so you know, this is my ship still.

2127
02:41:57.425 --> 02:41:58.426
我是老大
I'm in charge.

2128
02:41:58.968 --> 02:42:01.513
我知道，當然
I know. I know. Of course you are.

2129
02:42:01.680 --> 02:42:03.223
當然
Of course.

2130
02:42:05.850 --> 02:42:08.395
你說當然，卻又觸摸地圖
See, you say, "Of course," but then you touch the map.

2131
02:42:08.561 --> 02:42:11.064
讓我覺得你不明白我是老大
It makes you think that maybe you didn't realize I was in charge.

2132
02:42:11.690 --> 02:42:13.024
鬼爾，是你沒有安全感
Quail, that's your own insecurities in there.

2133
02:42:13.191 --> 02:42:14.192
鬼爾？
Quail?

2134
02:42:14.359 --> 02:42:16.611
我只是想出一分力幫忙
Okay? I am merely trying to be of service and assisting.

2135
02:42:16.778 --> 02:42:17.987
是奎爾
Quill.

2136
02:42:18.154 --> 02:42:19.030
我是這麼說啊
That's what I said.

2137
02:42:19.197 --> 02:42:21.574
你們該幹一架，看誰是老大
You should fight one another for the honour of leadership.

2138
02:42:21.741 --> 02:42:23.118
聽起來很公平
Sounds fair.

2139
02:42:25.870 --> 02:42:28.248
-沒必要啦 -不必
- It's not necessary, okay? - It's not.

2140
02:42:28.415 --> 02:42:30.792
我有爆能槍，除非你們想用刀子
I got some blasters, unless you guys wanna use knives.

2141
02:42:30.959 --> 02:42:33.169
對！拜託用刀子
Oh, yes! Please, use knives.

2142
02:42:33.336 --> 02:42:34.421
對，刀子
Yeah. Knives.

2143
02:42:34.587 --> 02:42:36.131
我是格魯特
I am Groot.

2144
02:42:41.886 --> 02:42:43.263
沒必要
Not necessary.

2145
02:42:43.430 --> 02:42:44.889
我們不會拿刀捅來捅去
There shall be no knifing one another.

2146
02:42:45.056 --> 02:42:48.059
大家都知道誰是老大
Everybody knows who's in charge.

2147
02:42:51.646 --> 02:42:52.856
我
Me.

2148
02:42:53.940 --> 02:42:54.774
對吧？
Right?

2149
02:42:55.692 --> 02:42:57.902
對，是你
Yes, you.

2150
02:42:58.153 --> 02:43:00.572
當然…
Of course! Of course.

2151
02:43:00.739 --> 02:43:02.407
當然
Of course.

2152
02:43:04.159 --> 02:43:05.702
記住…
Remember...

2153
02:43:06.536 --> 02:43:08.830
必須將寶石放回取得的時間
you have to return the stones to the exact moment you got 'em...

2154
02:43:08.997 --> 02:43:12.208
否則會引發許多麻煩的替代現實
or you're gonna open up a bunch of nasty alternative realities.

2155
02:43:12.375 --> 02:43:13.376
放心，布魯斯
Don't worry, Bruce.

2156
02:43:13.918 --> 02:43:15.795
我不會節外生枝
Clip all the branches.

2157
02:43:16.338 --> 02:43:18.089
我試過
You know, I tried.

2158
02:43:19.382 --> 02:43:24.202
我拿到手套和寶石時，試過救她回來
When I had the gauntlet, the stones, I really tried to bring her back.

2159
02:43:26.890 --> 02:43:28.516
我好想她
I miss her, man.

2160
02:43:28.892 --> 02:43:29.893
我也是
Me too.

2161
02:43:33.980 --> 02:43:36.399
你要的話，我能陪你去
You know, if you want, I could come with you.

2162
02:43:38.985 --> 02:43:40.445
你是好人，山姆
You're a good man, Sam.

2163
02:43:40.987 --> 02:43:42.530
但這是我的責任
This one's on me, though.

2164
02:43:46.993 --> 02:43:48.912
我回來之前別幹蠢事
Don't do anything stupid till I get back.

2165
02:43:50.747 --> 02:43:51.998
我怎麼能？
How can I?

2166
02:43:52.165 --> 02:43:53.958
愚蠢都被你帶走了
You're taking all the stupid with you.

2167
02:44:01.549 --> 02:44:03.343
我會想你的，兄弟
Gonna miss you, buddy.

2168
02:44:03.718 --> 02:44:05.220
不會有事的，巴奇
It's gonna be okay, Buck.

2169
02:44:12.602 --> 02:44:14.396
這需要多久？
How long is this gonna take?

2170
02:44:14.646 --> 02:44:17.399
他需要多久都行，對我們只有五秒鐘
For him, as long as he needs. For us, five seconds.

2171
02:44:22.487 --> 02:44:23.738
準備好了嗎，隊長？
You ready, Cap?

2172
02:44:23.905 --> 02:44:26.324
回到這裡見，好嗎？
All right, we'll meet you back here, okay?

2173
02:44:26.991 --> 02:44:28.118
沒問題
You bet.

2174
02:44:29.619 --> 02:44:31.204
進入量子領域，三…
Going quantum. Three...

2175
02:44:31.788 --> 02:44:32.622
二…
two...

2176
02:44:33.289 --> 02:44:34.499
一
one.

2177
02:44:36.376 --> 02:44:38.420
返回現場，五…
And returning in five...

2178
02:44:38.586 --> 02:44:39.546
四…
four...

2179
02:44:39.713 --> 02:44:41.548
三，二…
three, two...

2180
02:44:41.715 --> 02:44:43.049
一
one.

2181
02:44:50.306 --> 02:44:51.307
他在哪？
Where is he?

2182
02:44:51.474 --> 02:44:53.226
不知道，他迅速經過時間戳記
I don't know. He blew right by his time stamp.

2183
02:44:53.393 --> 02:44:54.853
應該回來這裡的
He should be here.

2184
02:45:00.358 --> 02:45:01.276
讓他回來
Get him back.

2185
02:45:01.443 --> 02:45:02.569
-我在試 -快讓他回來
- I'm trying. - Get him the hell back.

2186
02:45:02.736 --> 02:45:04.612
-我說我在試 -山姆
- Hey, I said I'm trying. - Sam.

2187
02:45:28.595 --> 02:45:30.180
去吧
Go ahead.

2188
02:45:48.156 --> 02:45:48.907
隊長？
Cap?

2189
02:45:51.242 --> 02:45:52.994
嗨，山姆
Hi, Sam.

2190
02:45:55.997 --> 02:45:59.042
是出了狀況還是進行順利？
So, did something go wrong or did something go right?

2191
02:46:01.169 --> 02:46:05.006
把寶石放回去之後，我想…
Well, after I put the stones back, I thought...

2192
02:46:06.132 --> 02:46:07.467
或許…
maybe...

2193
02:46:07.967 --> 02:46:12.764
我聽東尼的話，好好過日子
I'll try some of that life Tony was telling me to get.

2194
02:46:14.766 --> 02:46:16.893
結果如何？
How'd that work out for ya?

2195
02:46:19.396 --> 02:46:20.814
很棒
It was beautiful.

2196
02:46:22.148 --> 02:46:23.858
我為你高興
Good. I'm happy for you.

2197
02:46:24.025 --> 02:46:25.068
真心的
Truly.

2198
02:46:25.819 --> 02:46:27.112
謝謝
Thank you.

2199
02:46:28.446 --> 02:46:29.698
唯一讓我難過的是
Only thing bumming me out...

2200
02:46:29.864 --> 02:46:33.451
我得活在一個沒有美國隊長的世界
is the fact I have to live in a world without Captain America.

2201
02:46:34.388 --> 02:46:35.723
Oh.

2202
02:46:37.247 --> 02:46:40.041
這讓我想到
That reminds me.

2203
02:46:48.550 --> 02:46:49.759
拿拿看
Try it on.

2204
02:47:15.285 --> 02:47:16.786
感覺如何？
How does it feel?

2205
02:47:19.372 --> 02:47:21.082
好像是別人的
Like it's someone else's.

2206
02:47:24.127 --> 02:47:25.295
並不是
It isn't.

2207
02:47:38.641 --> 02:47:40.226
謝謝
Thank you.

2208
02:47:41.936 --> 02:47:43.229
我會盡力
I'll do my best.

2209
02:47:48.610 --> 02:47:50.528
因此它是你的
That's why it's yours.

2210
02:47:52.238 --> 02:47:53.615
想跟我聊聊她嗎？
You wanna tell me about her?

2211
02:48:00.205 --> 02:48:01.706
不
No.

2212
02:48:02.123 --> 02:48:04.250
我想不了
No, I don't think I will.

2213
02:48:05.305 --> 02:48:11.354
